	 ('Distracted-Boyfriend','This meme template, commonly known as "Distracted Boyfriend," depicts a street scene with three main characters engaged in a visually comedic situation. The image is set on a busy urban sidewalk with buildings and other pedestrians visible in the background, creating a sense of everyday life.

In the foreground, three young adults are the focus. A man in a blue plaid shirt is walking with a woman in a light blue top, presumably his partner. However, the man''s head is turned sharply to look back at another woman walking by in a bright red sleeveless top. His expression is one of obvious interest or attraction.

The woman in red is positioned in the left foreground, slightly out of focus, walking confidently and seemingly unaware of the attention she''s receiving. Meanwhile, the man''s presumed partner, to his right, is looking at him with an expression of shock, displeasure, or disbelief at his blatant interest in the other woman.

The image is perfectly timed to capture this moment of social faux pas, with the man caught in the act of admiring someone other than his companion. The composition creates a clear narrative and emotional tension between the three figures.

This meme template has become incredibly popular for its versatility in representing situations of temptation, distraction, or sudden shifts in attention or preference. It''s often used to humorously illustrate choices between options in various contexts, from personal decisions to broader social or political commentary.

The clear expressions and body language of the characters, combined with the relatable scenario, make this image highly effective as a meme format. It allows for easy adaptation by adding text labels to each character to represent different concepts or choices in countless situations.','/memes/Distracted-Boyfriend.jpg',2,'{}','{"distracted bf","guy checking out another girl","man looking at other woman","jealous girlfriend","guy looking back","cheater temptation","wandering eyes","disloyal boyfriend","unfaithful guy","guy holding hand with girl and looks back"}',0.0,'[0.0075340336,-0.035766818,0.0066913823,0.0050954684,-0.00800752,-0.046172895,-0.03804237,0.0017266829,0.013979176,0.016669413,-0.019497456,-0.00916818,0.060629103,0.0037764607,-0.01319304,-0.008740523,-0.023627833,-0.027178632,-0.0233341,0.03318619,-0.018933784,0.0011916263,-0.05631096,-0.013309471,-0.031372942,0.076281644,0.009226322,0.013577892,0.084971964,0.018756088,0.030182501,-0.02020217,-0.0018273315,-0.026026804,0.010904053,-0.0030819813,0.040551636,-0.02327464,-0.005848217,-0.0023895092,0.039224286,-0.030487897,-0.016862288,-0.019584382,-0.044574477,-0.04361993,0.015037483,-0.036895975,-0.004488759,-0.029490633,0.0004557872,-0.035816263,-0.0023664914,-0.0034549073,-0.004457974,-0.028774323,-0.04219398,-0.003396101,0.03534557,0.036178328,0.027056053,0.027555384,0.0023339116,-0.03789389,-0.013178724,0.0025262397,-0.0021516716,0.00385084,-0.017589716,-0.009942175,-0.025172507,-0.00079857104,-0.0064582042,-0.026624363,-0.036379777,0.024259211,-0.016502693,-0.026338425,0.01924508,-0.011022213,0.039802477,0.03435764,-0.011505282,0.0053527215,0.0008067465,-0.005655175,0.015937502,0.028864559,-0.011086802,-0.0069821677,-0.014123363,0.02405788,0.008187428,0.033123143,0.012411065,0.03452714,-0.0038792666,0.008617714,0.015369237,0.0139327375,-0.006555336,0.07185603,-0.02884426,0.04802229,-0.05244453,0.053148776,0.02216357,0.0015670569,-0.041346606,-0.03970094,-0.028700363,-0.014949168,0.009682987,0.02890