	 ('Change-My-Mind','This meme template features a man seated at a small folding table outdoors, seemingly on a college campus or public square. The scene has a casual, impromptu feel, with brick pathways, trees, and buildings visible in the background.

The central figure is wearing a bright blue sweater or jacket and appears to be gesturing with one hand, as if in mid-conversation or making a point. His posture and expression suggest confidence and a readiness to engage in discussion.

On the table in front of him are a few items: some papers or documents, what looks like a drink, and possibly other small objects. The most prominent feature is a sign attached to the front of the table that reads "CHANGE MY MIND" in bold, capital letters.

This setup mimics the style of public debates or opinion stands often seen on college campuses, where individuals invite others to challenge their views on various topics. The "Change My Mind" sign has become iconic in meme culture, often used to present controversial or stubborn opinions in a somewhat provocative manner.

The composition of the image places the man and his table in the foreground, drawing immediate attention to the sign and setting up the premise for the meme. The outdoor setting provides context and adds to the feeling of a public forum or open debate scenario.

This template is frequently used online by adding text above the image to state an opinion or belief, inviting humorous or serious responses in the spirit of the "change my mind" challenge. It has become a popular format for expressing strongly held views or satirizing dogmatic positions on various subjects.','/memes/Change-My-Mind.jpg',2,'{}','{"Steven Crowder''s sign","prove me wrong","convince me"}',0.0,'[-0.010875512,-0.060084816,0.054516986,-0.006046414,0.01990721,-0.026912756,-0.009015102,0.02860957,-0.028291324,0.045455627,0.063891925,0.0007914242,0.033816133,-0.008563239,-0.015540585,-0.011771271,-0.015592086,-0.026317133,-0.05255687,0.038763802,-0.017158108,-0.0008122406,-0.055512566,-0.03773279,-0.006038723,0.033171225,-0.022309639,-0.008068881,0.057250943,0.03760455,0.013817563,-0.04443689,-0.014192982,-0.016181888,-0.006639366,-0.02226872,0.002528353,-0.033672772,-0.017305244,-0.0037680143,0.039499994,-0.019092614,0.010805672,-0.016432084,-0.021543669,-0.013521162,-0.046930578,-0.031239888,0.0044361725,0.020282457,0.01861001,-0.0036603047,0.0066159572,-0.014634853,-0.030730136,-0.02952451,-0.0466543,-0.017144471,-0.0044093104,0.031448573,0.012624238,0.005319888,-0.0068055894,-0.034083672,0.009153232,0.011508251,-0.012286881,-0.025365176,-0.037032872,-0.018771842,-0.022769086,0.012582115,0.030845756,-0.01744628,-0.016222775,-0.00241436,-0.019920595,-0.017541306,-0.032825697,-0.0034970725,0.010752883,0.05136455,-0.0024377995,-0.031168953,-0.06328503,-0.011330144,0.029350484,0.033320405,0.03133475,-0.018492563,0.00069353735,0.039740667,-0.0033761049,-0.009405454,0.020609362,0.023999056,0.025891598,0.020791741,0.038732685,-0.00854353,-0.0065473136,0.023118244,-0.024101283,0.032567807,-0.041034076,0.018446805,0.026360711,-0.00044915444,-0.054257985,-0.053313255,0.002261813,-0.028444972,0.017334316,0.019827079,-0.032240164,0.044257563,0.001085365,0.041121267,-0.02108224,0.0068772286,-0.02051999,-0.010773895,-0.03246942,0.0010130957,-0.015110468,-0.01783788,0.0