	 ('Woman-Yelling-At-Cat','This meme template combines two distinct images to create a humorous juxtaposition. On the left side, we see two women in what appears to be a dramatic scene from a reality TV show or similar program. One woman, with blonde hair, is shouting and pointing aggressively off-screen, her face contorted in an expression of anger or outrage. Beside her, a brunette woman looks on with a concerned and slightly shocked expression.

On the right side of the image, we see a dining table setting with a white cat sitting at the table. The cat has a distinct, almost grumpy or unimpressed expression, with slightly narrowed eyes. In front of the cat is a plate with what looks like a salad. A human hand is visible at the top of the frame, suggesting someone is either serving the cat or interacting with it at the table.

The humor in this meme template comes from the contrast between the intense, emotional reaction of the women on the left and the seemingly unbothered, somewhat annoyed-looking cat on the right. It''s as if the cat is the target of the women''s outburst, but remains completely unfazed by their dramatics.

This template is often used to humorously depict situations where someone is overreacting or being dramatic about something, while the subject of their outburst (represented by the cat) remains calm, indifferent, or unimpressed. The formal dining setting for the cat adds an extra layer of absurdity to the scene.

The composition of the meme invites viewers to imagine a connection between these two unrelated images, creating a narrative that can be adapted to various humorous scenarios depending on the text added to the meme.','/memes/Woman-Yelling-At-Cat.jpg',2,'{}','{"Women yelling","confused cat","girl screaming at cat","angry woman yelling at cat at dinner table","lady screams at cat","woman pointing at cat","smudge the cat","woman yelling at a cat","crying woman","fury lady cat eating salad","cat table","cat no","me dijiste que","chica gritando a gato","girl screaming cat"}',0.0,'[-0.010352141,-0.0113178585,0.005063083,-0.0032342772,-0.007699559,-0.06746725,-0.033872418,0.020110385,-0.02188922,0.049550302,0.0074928226,0.011193376,0.026014755,-0.007358356,-0.005184633,0.00026910138,0.0001497857,-0.0330977,-0.036607094,0.022290435,0.005714451,0.005815682,-0.07751306,-0.01931403,-0.0029725544,0.084677875,0.009602102,0.009900384,0.07442584,0.010519304,0.0031281237,-0.014454373,-0.003841078,-0.041311,0.007802444,-0.017997177,0.03566506,-0.016371919,-0.048537675,-0.017902004,0.026943302,-0.03107539,0.034096465,-0.035255607,-0.011486661,-0.013740904,0.00481396,0.010208923,0.0307712,-0.019037811,0.011100117,-0.03330954,0.014216501,-0.013508705,-0.04996067,-0.030264815,-0.031102635,-0.0149835395,0.015204791,0.0024271577,0.040247645,0.0042361123,-0.014522399,-0.041797776,-0.011885608,0.0016509304,0.004217705,-0.02486876,-0.037735794,-0.033688206,0.013472936,0.0012472504,-0.014021896,-0.006850641,-0.07395139,-0.034290455,-0.01971212,-0.01569706,0.016795903,0.006464118,0.023414223,0.033295598,-0.022543063,-0.012112322,-0.026399417,-0.006468007,0.01804098,0.037054546,0.004013403,-0.013632164,-0.009646839,0.04118097,-0.0239681,0.032772012,0.010689917,0.049328502,-0.00031524806,0.025814557,0.014686796,0.01034437,-0.019926747,0.04269028,-0.020307684,0.043923855,-0.06598039,0.015496727,0.06439711,-0.010620051,-0.031597428,-0.032856114,-0.031148866,-0.014263874,0.012439725,-0.008568128,-0