	 ('Surprised-Pikachu','This meme template features a close-up image of Pikachu, the iconic yellow electric-type Pokémon character. The image is cropped to focus solely on Pikachu''s face, which dominates the frame. Pikachu''s expression is one of surprise or shock, with its mouth open in a small, rounded "O" shape.

The image has a distinctly low-resolution, pixelated quality, which adds to its memetic nature. This blurriness gives it a somewhat comical and exaggerated appearance, enhancing the surprised expression. The colors are vivid but slightly washed out due to the image quality, with Pikachu''s signature bright yellow fur being the dominant color.

Pikachu''s eyes are wide and alert, depicted as large brown circles that convey a sense of astonishment or disbelief. The red circular cheeks, a defining feature of Pikachu, are clearly visible on either side of its face. The pointed ears characteristic of Pikachu can be seen at the top of the frame, though they''re partially cut off.

The background of the image shows hints of green and brown, suggesting a natural setting, though it''s out of focus and indistinct due to the close-up nature of the shot and the overall low resolution.

This particular image of Pikachu has become a widely recognized meme template, often used to express surprise, shock, or confusion in reaction to unexpected information or situations. Its popularity stems from the combination of Pikachu''s beloved status in pop culture and the exaggerated, almost comically surprised expression captured in this particular frame.

The low quality of the image adds to its charm and meme potential, as it embodies the often rough, quickly-shared nature of internet memes. This "Surprised Pikachu" meme has become a staple in online culture, used across various social media platforms to humorously depict reactions to obvious or predictable outcomes.','/memes/Surprised-Pikachu.jpg',2,'{}','{"shocked pikachu","surprised picachu"}',0.0,'[0.0047533223,-0.0024431543,0.00078279315,0.00029511013,-0.012302233,-0.052592844,0.03014106,-0.029788952,0.03554015,0.06348515,0.024853632,-0.017477402,0.0376465,0.010356378,-0.02293714,-0.00858912,-0.009762295,-0.03636232,-0.0018352533,0.02665503,-0.0042160624,-0.010213818,-0.035677556,-0.026868997,0.0030877404,0.037854012,0.0050241835,-0.031267345,0.020365711,0.0041015116,-0.013543877,0.027456846,0.004683824,-0.032116927,-0.0038995317,-0.014948129,0.024496077,-0.033659462,-0.056955528,-0.02979432,0.07495197,-0.025084406,0.01750099,-0.016465599,-0.052248716,-0.03499609,-0.033935588,-0.0048474823,0.034042392,-0.045117307,0.024005242,0.02178622,0.0036810741,0.030816944,-0.030740147,-0.047786552,0.010484627,-0.038428087,0.009429067,0.0412971,0.008526088,-0.003547084,-0.0009532019,-0.03369965,-0.029638894,-0.00783466,-0.039028242,-0.024802336,-0.016117396,-0.0014892918,0.008868905,0.0040743332,-0.0024932404,-0.012730405,-0.05752618,0.014861731,-0.014067541,-0.013164557,-0.016755516,0.014156733,0.027904725,0.011707183,-0.021622352,-0.04853757,-0.023817841,-0.03708458,0.0037981558,-0.015974663,-0.024739204,-0.011449706,-0.030461844,0.07587169,-0.015339459,0.03836597,0.03418575,0.011036303,0.00913151,0.02508543,-0.02288116,-0.012240682,0.011984735,0.026652299,0.028105475,0.03863547,-0.016161669,-0.010018032,0.009475834,-0.0038917873,-0.04633712,-0.025049584,0.014921297,-0.025822226,0.010795946,-0.022172654,-0.04105265,0.047678873,-0.013426094,0.062037375,-0.027110144,-0.025352756,-0.045380663,-0.013386189,-0.016816907,-0.016856926,0.015108819,-0.02221618,0.015705923,0.04020