	 ('Creepy-Condescending-Wonka','This meme template features a close-up shot of a character from the 1971 film "Willy Wonka & the Chocolate Factory." The image captures the eccentric and whimsical nature of the character, who is dressed in a flamboyant style reminiscent of a Victorian-era dandy or circus ringmaster.

The character wears a large, light brown top hat that sits atop his curly, strawberry blonde hair. His bright blue eyes have a mischievous twinkle, and he sports a knowing, slightly condescending smile. This expression is often interpreted as conveying a sense of sarcasm, superiority, or hidden knowledge.

His outfit is notably colorful and extravagant. He wears a deep purple velvet jacket, which contrasts sharply with a white shirt collar and a large, pale brown bow tie. Around his neck is a vibrant floral scarf or cravat with pink and purple tones, adding to the eccentric ensemble.

The character''s pose is distinctive, with one hand raised to his face in a gesture that suggests he''s leaning in to share a secret or make a wry observation. This pose, combined with the facial expression, gives the image a sense of conspiracy or inside joke with the viewer.

The background of the image is somewhat blurred but appears to be a colorful set, possibly from the movie, with hints of yellow and other bright colors visible.

This particular meme template is often used to express sarcasm, condescension, or to mock naive or foolish statements. The character''s expression and pose lend themselves well to captions that play on the idea of feigned or exaggerated surprise, or knowing better than the subject being discussed.','/memes/Creepy-Condescending-Wonka.jpg',2,'{}','{"willy wonka stare","sarcastic wonka","tell me more about X","tell me again","gene wilder"}',0.0,'[0.03250473,-0.046686824,0.0107278405,0.008780708,0.005569652,-0.031666417,0.002268296,0.011264034,-0.015912939,0.031745255,-0.012252747,0.012108429,0.046686858,-0.002279473,-0.02087399,-0.0009773421,0.0054528182,-0.0055422112,0.0007019612,0.04074448,0.021718526,-0.00096671155,-0.07228784,-0.015016571,0.009613685,0.07876012,-0.013998688,0.009412883,0.051695835,0.014265855,0.013048952,0.033822432,0.0028508466,-0.072777145,0.0063983086,0.00934589,0.031317074,-0.048849136,0.021511648,-0.04272581,-0.0071948646,-0.018645898,0.019414464,-0.035296503,0.0011138839,0.0077490625,-0.039253443,-0.015783364,0.02643271,-0.029889312,-0.005558583,-0.033782423,0.006093629,0.02562761,0.0009589788,-0.026497098,0.0016837567,-0.0065924036,0.00025056634,0.03253284,0.021632241,-0.004119421,-0.008911283,-0.04780338,-0.03084936,-0.008323818,-0.02259976,-0.0133298375,-0.019542508,-0.0412841,-0.00069885293,0.014889586,0.010136129,0.008352689,-0.049052436,-0.03993903,-0.0116999345,0.0022204027,-0.0039047077,0.012816228,0.04769876,-0.0035099627,0.0013314598,-0.020837622,-0.020790674,0.02383649,0.043570228,0.025453515,0.01444862,-0.036477566,0.0015664329,0.06610391,-0.011864521,0.03830902,0.031000383,0.02426796,-0.004095237,0.041508663,-0.00799565,0.025264638,-0.0068577738,0.024177814,-0.018994492,0.035050873,-0.012136951,0.0027428563,0.021094441,0.012925611,-0.047909066,-0.004795577,-0.012815336,-0.015871799,0.03575321,0.00449692,-0.03460571,0.025011698,0.019994361,0.045814727,-0.038847767,-0.023119826,0.00023346464,-0.030535538,0.005729589,-0.0033137626,0