	 ('Awkward-Moment-Sealion','This meme template features a close-up portrait of an adorable and expressive elephant seal pup, capturing the essence of what''s commonly known as the "Awkward Moment Seal" meme. The image focuses tightly on the seal''s face, which dominates the frame against a blurred, neutral background.

The seal has a distinctive, endearing appearance with large, dark eyes that seem to convey a mix of innocence and mild concern. Its eyes are wide and slightly glossy, giving it an almost cartoon-like quality of expressiveness. The seal''s snout is prominent, with a broad, flat nose covered in tiny whisker holes, giving it a spotted appearance.

One of the most striking features is the seal''s mouth, which appears to be drawn into a slight grimace or uncomfortable smile. This expression, combined with the folded skin around its neck creating what looks like multiple chins, gives the seal a comical, slightly uncomfortable look that resonates with the awkward or uneasy situations the meme typically represents.

The seal''s fur is a soft gray color, lighter around the face and darkening slightly towards the edges of the frame. The whiskers are clearly visible, protruding from the sides of its face and adding to the seal''s charismatic appearance.

The image is crisp and clear, allowing viewers to see fine details like the texture of the seal''s skin and the reflection in its eyes. The lighting is soft and even, highlighting the seal''s features without harsh shadows.

This meme template has become iconic for its versatility in expressing discomfort, awkwardness, or that moment of realization when one has said or done something embarrassing. The seal''s expression perfectly encapsulates that universal feeling of wanting to disappear in uncomfortable social situations, making it a highly relatable and widely used image in meme culture.','/memes/Awkward-Moment-Sealion.jpg',2,'{}','{"awkward seal","uncomfortable situation sealion","heavy breathing sealion"}',0.0,'[0.031495113,0.0166691,-0.0056461594,0.011973206,0.017508259,-0.03702357,-0.031793427,0.0031955582,0.009147703,0.048066456,0.0045229434,0.013121063,0.031581894,0.003973841,-0.010730446,0.0125763435,0.030125065,-0.045946203,-0.06292299,0.0019050692,-0.0059656487,-0.015221937,-0.06311602,-0.037340816,0.022568308,0.061847057,0.018508015,0.0069155465,0.06623126,-0.0050533595,-0.027357372,0.018003982,0.019228961,-0.066791035,0.016629491,0.0052604955,0.01685854,-0.028479114,0.0016210036,-0.035436723,0.046164416,-0.02521364,0.057087757,-0.00017222899,-0.023951134,0.0024069361,-0.01635213,0.032586545,0.009368244,-0.009032175,0.018070841,-0.030284155,0.013830485,0.022074446,-0.019628154,-0.041953642,-0.009649406,-0.027853325,0.0123482635,0.023106782,0.04531297,-0.018727178,0.0169921,-0.023428075,-0.026190482,-0.0033570114,-0.045449574,-0.0057836203,-0.026154818,-0.0007587422,0.013982005,0.019235265,-0.02170896,-0.03101501,-0.05751061,-0.039246265,-0.016441612,-0.014774519,0.019444577,0.016622866,0.013588732,0.02883726,3.536671e-05,-0.0283446,0.0009839751,-0.036605667,-0.006736569,0.054214634,0.031753495,-0.035500035,-0.01816394,0.06810907,-0.014193611,0.022080494,-0.013577767,0.029681008,-0.019251974,0.012730086,-0.0033069619,0.0003229802,-0.021754988,0.018200513,0.0047411146,0.050854772,-0.026680807,0.0021452396,-0.027256716,0.004566498,-0.024086578,-0.01230137,-0.018346842,-0.019912152,0.0009292795,-0.016634556,-0.019096958,0.017575597,-0.012230057,0.0686072,-0.050962918,-0.0009045