	 ('Too-Damn-High','This meme template features a close-up shot of an older African American man with a distinctive appearance and animated expression. He has a full white beard and mustache that contrast sharply with his dark skin. The man is wearing glasses, a dark suit jacket, white shirt, and a patterned tie, giving him a formal, professional appearance.

The most striking aspect of the image is the man''s energetic pose and expression. His right arm is raised high, with his fist clenched in a gesture that suggests enthusiasm, triumph, or emphatic agreement. His facial expression matches this energy, with his eyes seemingly closed or narrowed behind his glasses and his mouth open wide in what appears to be a joyful or excited exclamation.

The background of the image is a solid blue color, which could indicate he''s on a stage or at a podium, possibly giving a speech or presentation. The lighting focuses on the man, making him stand out vividly against the background.

This image is often used as a reaction meme to express great excitement, agreement, or a sense of victory. The man''s animated gesture and expression make it a versatile template for conveying strong positive emotions or reactions in a variety of contexts.

The composition of the image, focusing tightly on the upper body and face of the subject, emphasizes the emotional impact and makes the gesture and expression the central focus. This framing is ideal for meme usage, as it allows for easy recognition and interpretation of the emotion being conveyed.','/memes/Too-Damn-High.jpg',2,'{}','{"The rent is too damn high","bar to damn high"}',0.0,'[0.029596364,-0.020652048,0.011502505,0.0333606,-0.006732498,-0.023897653,-0.032771256,0.0024746766,-0.0038477834,0.041737836,-0.01935596,-0.025598086,0.035188504,-0.0027611412,0.012239776,-0.0018579538,-0.009695006,-0.019150835,-0.020551087,0.028400406,0.017807769,-0.010315125,-0.07162995,-0.053522464,0.020836947,0.056231316,-0.0265972,0.010604204,0.051081643,0.022302078,0.01484181,0.0042725815,-0.0076966197,-0.049852785,-0.012709319,-0.0050814543,0.017184878,-0.059698947,-0.02282015,-0.030093351,0.041691355,-0.030730784,0.007061149,-0.016032653,-0.074467964,-0.045717783,-0.02901928,-0.014388391,0.024505131,0.011261566,0.009083377,-0.023634402,0.028652625,0.02610648,-0.017932983,-0.033871174,-0.012280723,-0.019354083,-0.013588676,0.012690794,0.0404518,0.02011983,-0.019413082,-0.035039917,-0.022344258,0.009279748,-0.030703288,0.0047687273,-0.029685251,-0.025501104,-0.008370306,-0.008677555,0.04238445,-0.008135496,-0.05299552,-0.017236514,-0.047237128,-0.028916733,0.015579055,-0.025257232,0.0035137252,0.034880865,-0.009107739,-0.014116611,-0.031126156,-0.0066713206,0.018544452,0.0005009351,0.02690321,-0.025782201,-0.0043580737,0.042999327,0.0005675381,-0.0024484443,0.0039988477,0.045655154,-0.0036849428,0.056405794,0.0020197441,0.037957963,-0.033065043,0.033073623,-0.055144116,0.037931573,-0.030207131,0.028014315,0.016319616,0.005957651,-0.032829348,-0.036271345,0.022826035,-0.029342111,0.006227451,-0.0007745254,-0.051560678,0.028059702,0.007668244,0.0561753,-0.037280567,0.006700014,-0.052375983,-0.007132274,-0.018263215,-0.034511704,-0.011626585,0.0025513205,0.0006655021,0.03374547,