	 ('Conspiracy-Keanu','This meme template features a close-up shot of a young man with a distinctive, bewildered expression. The image appears to be a still from a movie or TV show, captured at a moment of confusion or surprise.

The man has shaggy, dark hair that falls just above his shoulders in a somewhat messy style typical of the 1990s or early 2000s. His eyebrows are slightly raised, adding to his look of confusion. His mouth is slightly open, as if he''s about to speak or has just been caught off-guard by something.

He''s wearing a white dress shirt with a black suit jacket, suggesting a formal or semi-formal setting. The background is blurry but appears to be outdoors, with muted green tones visible.

The image quality and style are reminiscent of films from the late 20th or early 21st century. The slightly grainy texture and color palette contribute to this vintage feel.

This particular expression has become iconic in meme culture, often used to convey confusion, disbelief, or a moment of realization. The exaggerated facial features and the timing of the capture make it particularly effective for humorous contexts.

The image is cropped closely around the man''s face, emphasizing his reaction and making it easy to focus on the expression. This tight framing is common in reaction memes, allowing the image to be easily inserted into various contexts for comedic effect.

Overall, this meme template capitalizes on a perfectly timed moment of genuine-looking confusion, making it versatile for a wide range of humorous situations where someone might be portrayed as baffled or caught off-guard.','/memes/Conspiracy-Keanu.jpg',2,'{}','{"what if","keanu reeves",whoa}',0.0,'[0.028855385,-0.031129612,0.0058637676,0.019345608,-0.0013934833,-0.03725236,-0.01227892,-0.021059101,-0.0025185053,0.045950633,5.978909e-05,-0.023276268,0.053277057,0.0009774307,-0.017495792,0.02546292,0.009875368,-0.05166026,-0.02433212,0.04155004,0.026042955,-0.007899246,-0.0667488,-0.05039498,0.0042238305,0.03141391,-0.01282492,-0.0015169426,0.04964181,0.014041983,0.023188137,0.017976355,-0.03939068,-0.048291616,0.0046109655,0.017340627,0.02887582,-0.05994344,-0.027720716,-0.019494792,0.0141236065,-0.009484299,0.020223906,-0.0135569805,-0.032117944,-0.027487138,-0.012071761,-0.026210042,0.0075357673,-0.00031027832,0.015566393,-0.054505844,0.0149272075,0.032908756,0.00087489176,-0.048327003,-0.015706094,-0.00097514543,0.0073530255,0.005323744,0.034205273,0.03834728,0.006834075,-0.011680883,-0.022298934,0.027765855,-0.03343625,-0.01687899,-0.013716708,-0.024817325,-0.000287537,0.0069877747,0.0069955476,0.024069376,-0.062360805,0.010632074,-0.051439174,-0.0013584553,0.050357535,-0.015642185,0.024979185,0.030379958,-0.018325742,-0.042353354,-0.011899433,-0.042008452,0.035041597,0.027835345,0.022693207,-0.006271253,-0.0026048685,0.061793443,-0.006146354,0.015088331,0.002707115,0.039099596,0.011970353,0.03306698,-0.0017610956,0.029484019,-0.020635987,0.05641309,-0.018133301,0.035753544,-0.027907973,-0.01207786,0.0098293545,0.007239607,-0.0524174,-0.009298174,0.013333138,-0.041599836,-0.01841896,-0.019515587,-0.042768754,0.038099773,0.0142382085,0.033966083,-0.039003465,-0.015719466,-0.046429038,-0.007711841,-0.017103203,-0.0028976048,-0.010129219,-0.016692335,0.029212099,0.04095937,-0.045440413,0.012986728,-0.005253295,0.003578946,0.013353364,0.04279582,-0.031426426,0.02790