	 ('Blank-Nut-Button','This meme template image presents a striking visual contrast between two central elements: a large, bright blue button and a human hand in a dismissive gesture.

The button dominates the left side of the frame. It''s a vivid, royal blue color that stands out sharply against the darker background. The button appears to be part of some kind of control panel or device, suggested by the glimpse of a gray or white surface surrounding it. The button''s smooth, glossy surface gives it an almost tempting quality, as if inviting interaction.

On the right side of the image, we see a human hand entering the frame. The hand is positioned palm-out towards the viewer, fingers extended upwards. This gesture is universally recognized as a "stop" or "no thanks" signal. The hand appears to be moving, as there''s a slight blur to its edges, enhancing the sense of an active, dismissive motion.

The background of the image is predominantly dark, which makes both the blue button and the lighter-toned hand stand out dramatically. This high-contrast composition draws the viewer''s attention immediately to these two key elements.

The juxtaposition of the inviting button and the rejecting hand creates a clear narrative tension. It suggests a moment of decision or temptation, where an obvious or easy choice (represented by the button) is being actively refused or avoided.

This template is often used in memes to humorously portray situations where someone is resisting an tempting but unwise or unwanted option. The simplicity and clarity of the visual metaphor make it highly versatile for a wide range of comedic scenarios involving choice, temptation, or willpower.

The slightly blurred, low-resolution quality of the image adds to its meme aesthetic, giving it a raw, relatable feel that''s characteristic of many popular internet memes. This imperfect quality often adds to the humor and shareability of memes created with this template.','/memes/Blank-Nut-Button.jpg',2,'{}','{"blank blue button","smash button","press button","button slam","button meme","panic button",botton,"nut button (crystalbot)"}',0.0,'[-0.015065704,-0.030960413,0.018526556,0.03678335,0.0017082113,-0.052550856,-0.027339252,0.026256265,-0.017017419,0.07228277,-0.008745217,-0.0053179828,0.01418185,0.006224814,-0.0054456373,-0.009656647,0.015374411,-0.014730137,-0.023487255,0.016708797,-0.0011308506,-0.0018453622,-0.07717812,-0.073952,-0.020434687,0.046845842,-0.008132963,0.00035669826,0.05157957,0.029926645,-0.000516867,-0.00989997,0.02081618,-0.04704753,0.0022519235,-0.015363293,0.027833795,-0.055728838,-0.0093734665,-0.027734146,0.027380599,-0.040235084,0.03056767,-0.032471944,-0.013429235,-0.02714425,-0.040885724,-0.013516552,-0.0042953724,-0.0053008567,0.0003769608,0.0070280926,0.0026306133,0.0025353667,-0.03800196,-0.0048176916,-0.042781975,-0.018141901,0.013338533,0.020226957,0.014205819,-0.01838792,-0.0024964127,-0.06302272,-0.017887596,0.012342256,-0.015164282,-0.010364353,-0.049466778,-0.038020924,-0.009645093,0.027633198,0.005126912,-0.040597595,-0.019375095,0.009260797,-0.029506,-0.016307896,-0.0023025249,0.004556697,0.024550302,0.04194177,-0.005655911,-0.015467307,-0.02667187,0.023784626,0.029321935,0.043214634,0.011328623,-0.035636846,0.00057000795,0.061280154,-0.010759161,0.0025141079,0.021213096,0.020785052,0.013369606,0.044295453,-0.008053132,-0.016712112,0.002373218,0.017336361,-0.050534617,0.0076004574,-0.004638192,0.007946246,0.04660084,0.024263678,-0.058019657,-0.057236176,-0.012429532,-0.026010165,0.0049641905,-0.016587337,-0.010317548,0.07024261,-0.024772575,0.048133895,-0.029687995,0.0025137959,-0.0291311,0.021904362,-0.03608872,0.0006733