	 ('X-X-Everywhere','This meme template is a classic scene from the beloved Pixar animated film "Toy Story." It features two of the main characters: a cowboy doll and a space ranger action figure, standing side by side on what appears to be a wooden surface, likely a table or desk.

The cowboy is on the left, wearing his iconic yellow plaid shirt with a cow-print vest, blue jeans, and a belt with a large round buckle. He has a holster on his hip and his expression is one of slight concern or skepticism, with raised eyebrows and a slight frown.

To the right is the space ranger, clad in his signature white, green, and purple spacesuit. His chest bears the "Space Ranger" logo, and he has various colored buttons on his suit. The space ranger''s pose is dynamic and expressive, with one arm outstretched as if he''s presenting or explaining something. His face shows excitement and enthusiasm, with a wide-eyed expression and open-mouthed smile.

The contrast between the two characters is striking - the cowboy''s more reserved and doubtful demeanor juxtaposed against the space ranger''s exuberance and confidence. This setup is perfect for memes that play on themes of skepticism versus enthusiasm, traditional versus modern, or simply two contrasting viewpoints on a situation.

The background of the image shows a hint of a room setting, with a door frame visible and some small star decorations on the wall, emphasizing the toy''s perspective and scale within their environment.

This image is frequently used in meme culture to represent situations where one person is excitedly explaining or promoting an idea while another looks on with doubt or confusion, making it versatile for a wide range of humorous or relatable scenarios.','/memes/X-X-Everywhere.jpg',2,'{}','{"woody and buzz lightyear pointing","toy story","dicks everywhere","toystory everywhere"}',0.0,'[0.035498004,0.008793994,0.030495888,0.029185655,0.02787848,-0.06446291,-0.01124906,-0.0072601084,0.007567848,0.04971938,0.0070738187,0.017429149,0.012024596,0.012697466,0.024337864,0.022626996,0.01265957,-0.041122735,-0.036061734,-0.016855633,-0.041716386,-0.01282732,-0.09888703,-0.0026822218,-0.005644173,0.053987417,0.00893803,0.024195544,0.062070377,0.022330232,0.015959179,-0.0072655785,0.03870067,-0.021575147,-0.0033782832,-0.01192145,0.024838505,-0.042549487,0.0015631799,-0.014998739,0.028740715,-0.008436775,0.052098133,-0.051280808,-0.027272794,-0.013570027,0.036025748,-0.010210676,0.026608886,-0.039772797,0.01368113,-0.0049912077,-0.017858118,0.02520348,-0.025328005,-0.023705205,0.022992551,-0.03953442,0.02565837,0.013302713,0.04705632,0.0112747485,-0.0077193878,-0.04743887,-0.024311058,-0.016643094,-0.029027632,-0.012481967,-0.028708776,0.013296144,0.034908373,0.039636254,0.011272822,0.0005278943,-0.019810386,0.0065310393,-0.031198954,-0.02194925,-0.004963369,0.011855819,0.03949094,0.03275998,0.004839119,-0.029573264,-0.039641514,-0.030634731,0.032830235,0.047722828,0.0062527223,-0.06699852,-0.029665317,0.09126593,-0.01786367,0.017140225,0.032998566,0.008462141,-0.015450537,0.0075732768,-0.0131725995,-0.0073204054,0.004001651,0.037847824,-0.03788296,0.040462587,-0.053276807,-0.011740288,0.024582343,-0.013872969,0.00066017284,-0.028401863,0.008881839,-0.036951676,0.025543261,0.0054688016,-0.048270334,0.0053020036,-0.0007452901,0.0659727,-0.030366663,-0.01816282,-0.024494633,-0.012764476,-0.00037449188,-0.002413935,-0.00046829905,0.0007990887,0.02678775,0.028875034,0.011510015,0.0