	 ('But-Thats-None-Of-My-Business','This meme template features the iconic Muppet character Kermit the Frog in a humorous and slightly mischievous pose. The image captures Kermit from the chest up, his distinctive bright green felt body and round white eyes with black pupils clearly visible. His mouth is closed in a slight smirk, giving him a knowing or sly expression.

The focal point of the image is a large glass of tea that Kermit is holding up to his mouth, as if about to take a sip. The glass contains a reddish-brown liquid, presumably iced tea, and a Lipton tea bag tag is visible hanging over the rim of the glass. The liquid in the glass has a warm, amber glow, suggesting it''s backlit or catching the light in an appealing way.

Kermit''s arm is extended, holding the glass close to his face in a casual, almost nonchalant manner. This pose, combined with his expression, gives the impression of someone about to make a wry comment or observation – the classic "But that''s none of my business" setup that this meme is known for.

The background is softly out of focus, hinting at an indoor setting, possibly a kitchen or living room. The lighting is warm and natural, adding to the casual, everyday feel of the scene.

This image has become a popular meme template, often used to make sarcastic or pointed observations about others'' behavior, followed by the phrase "But that''s none of my business." The juxtaposition of Kermit''s innocent puppet appearance with the implication of judgmental or gossipy commentary creates a humorous contrast that has made this meme enduringly popular across social media platforms.','/memes/But-Thats-None-Of-My-Business.jpg',2,'{}','{"Kermit the frog","kermit drinking lipton iced tea","kermit frog tea","kermit lipton","kermit drinking tea"}',0.0,'[0.00461291,-0.04768256,0.018677238,0.03184532,-0.012729328,-0.06253641,-0.032308172,0.010314466,-0.033979323,0.014935326,-0.0071735354,-0.0044816867,0.042454995,-0.007933535,-0.045260753,0.006756828,0.007188907,-0.012446521,-0.011722397,-0.017882962,0.008245361,0.013769784,-0.02583349,0.019259717,0.006755973,0.028527232,-0.031567656,0.019359555,0.054301295,-0.0014871332,-0.007873613,0.027004106,0.015014867,-0.050679896,-0.00014216604,0.00077902613,0.030226229,0.015879607,0.0029643162,-0.021725155,0.0052851425,0.0096713975,0.040263735,-0.0130571565,0.004857338,0.018553143,-0.016595239,0.008671463,0.061643794,-0.0039239167,0.0039128913,0.017184276,-0.003843942,-0.01042624,-0.025383653,-0.039721094,-0.0062266905,-0.051114935,0.0054377145,0.046218883,0.006486051,-0.012447908,-0.0044867457,-0.058139212,-0.01886743,-0.017498571,-0.019658817,-0.019105481,0.004219538,-0.033589564,0.0019623805,0.014992244,-0.017556982,0.01627794,-0.044506993,-0.02226663,0.007996872,0.035688322,0.04056349,0.026642716,0.014475706,0.021751208,-0.023323363,-0.024278449,-0.019369217,-0.01853271,-0.0021308083,0.03725378,-0.008628796,-0.030575437,-0.0089568915,0.07711088,-0.0392376,-0.00093537464,0.013431141,0.020429239,-0.021553466,0.04513992,-0.003952214,0.0061411844,-0.009616104,-0.014793823,-0.009056284,0.04161375,0.00047629507,-0.006481317,0.04741544,-0.0013653754,-0.040437568,-0.023150396,-0.0147873415,-0.01964499,0.009436548,-0.02545