	 ('That-Would-Be-Great','This meme template features a scene from what appears to be a typical American office environment, likely from the late 1990s or early 2000s. The focal point is a middle-aged man standing in the foreground, captured in a moment of apparent exasperation or frustration.

The man is dressed in stereotypical office attire of the era: a light blue button-up shirt with the sleeves rolled up, a yellowish tie with a repeating pattern, and prominent red suspenders. He''s wearing large, square-framed glasses that were popular during that time period. His hair is styled in a somewhat messy, medium-length cut.

The expression on the man''s face is particularly notable. His mouth is slightly open, as if he''s in the middle of speaking, and his eyes convey a sense of disbelief or annoyance. It''s the kind of look one might give when dealing with an absurd situation or explaining something for the umpteenth time.

In his right hand, the man is holding a white coffee mug, suggesting he might have been in the middle of a coffee break when whatever prompted his reaction occurred.

The background of the image shows a typical open-plan office space. Fluorescent lighting illuminates the area, and glimpses of cubicle walls and office equipment can be seen. There''s a hint of other office workers in the background, but they''re out of focus.

