	 ('Ancient-Aliens','This meme template features a close-up shot of a man with a distinctively eccentric appearance. He has wild, unkempt dark hair that sticks up in all directions, giving him a somewhat frazzled look. The man is wearing a brown suit jacket and a patterned tie, suggesting a professional setting despite his disheveled hair.

The man''s facial expression is particularly notable. He has a wide, enthusiastic grin and his eyes are slightly squinted, as if he''s in the middle of an animated explanation or reaction. His hands are raised and visible in the frame, with his fingers splayed out in an expressive gesture. This body language, combined with his facial expression, conveys a sense of excitement or passionate emphasis about whatever he''s discussing.

The background appears to be an indoor setting, likely a studio or interview room, with warm, golden lighting that gives the image a slightly vintage feel. In the bottom right corner, there''s a watermark for "HISTORY.com" in yellow text, indicating this image is a screenshot from a History Channel program.

This meme template is often used to express passionate agreement, wild theories, or over-the-top explanations. The man''s appearance and gestures make it perfect for conveying enthusiasm, especially about unconventional or outlandish ideas. The contrast between his professional attire and his wild hair adds to the humorous effect, making it a versatile template for various comedic contexts online.','/memes/Ancient-Aliens.jpg',2,'{}','{"Giorgio Tsoukalos","History Channel Guy","science guy","aliens guy"}',0.0,'[0.030196894,-0.030323848,0.00727272,0.012334493,0.016903263,-0.019826973,-0.03367739,-0.0065203165,0.009790094,0.025680251,0.007309296,-0.01924322,0.03754077,-0.023859674,0.0035789122,0.020800943,-0.0014568503,-0.05148372,-0.02024572,0.028060094,0.04225662,-0.03141912,-0.055991597,-0.05884394,0.0016931662,0.04697008,-0.030797439,0.005125991,0.05035633,0.017566962,0.034314353,0.010962855,-0.052531037,-0.064146966,0.00033463465,0.023372715,-0.0033497699,-0.052044373,-0.023414398,-0.054683786,-0.0043395427,-0.025412034,-0.0031069396,-0.02434513,-0.021071002,0.0020004308,-0.028358076,-0.007386935,0.023700085,0.0070194663,0.018985288,-0.02936694,0.018700551,0.0468554,-0.007137285,-0.043707818,-0.032402698,0.014575792,-0.0033639986,0.018018935,0.03755474,0.014222379,-0.016580816,-0.04209349,-0.013934729,0.02267032,-0.023739122,-0.01707395,-0.026712554,-0.020087287,-0.0119557325,0.02070053,0.026921485,0.02667056,-0.05096571,-0.020191379,-0.018157315,-0.0123162195,0.0073071406,0.0039124195,0.03434109,0.033930298,-0.014876095,-0.024725633,-0.00836852,-0.004374486,0.04379287,0.04723465,0.032668497,-0.019404098,0.011481735,0.046962168,0.0012529134,-0.0016885108,0.016046893,0.04070471,0.015970947,0.054044556,-0.0034503166,0.03275367,-0.022787627,0.05153815,-0.04355138,0.022290217,-0.027839372,0.029084621,0.028227901,-0.0076249116,-0.028080385,-0.04337688,0.028627703,-0.033275463,-0.0018105919,-0.013153918,-0.050881892,0.008433209,0.023957143,0.0424092,-0.038400356,-0.0183