	 ('Brace-Yourselves-X-is-Coming','This meme template features a striking image of a man in medieval or fantasy-style attire, likely from a popular television series or film set in a historical or fictional medieval world. The man is shown in profile, facing to the right of the frame, with a serious and somewhat stern expression on his face.

He has shoulder-length dark hair that appears slightly windswept, and a full beard. His attire is notable for its rugged, northern aesthetic: he wears a thick, dark cloak or coat with a prominent fur collar. The fur is mottled in shades of brown, black, and white, giving it a wild and authentic appearance.

The man is gripping the hilt of a sword with both hands, though only the top of the hilt is visible in the frame. This posture, combined with his serious expression, conveys a sense of impending action or grave importance.

The background is a plain white, which makes the figure stand out dramatically and allows for easy addition of text in meme formats. This isolation of the character against a blank backdrop is common in meme templates, as it focuses attention solely on the subject and their expression or pose.

The image''s composition, with the character positioned to the left side of the frame and facing right, leaves space on the right side that is often used for text in meme adaptations. The character''s intense gaze and the implied weight of the moment he seems to be experiencing make this image particularly suited for memes about preparing for challenging situations, making dramatic declarations, or facing daunting tasks.

Overall, the image evokes themes of duty, honor, and facing adversity, which contribute to its versatility as a meme template for a wide range of topics, from mundane daily struggles to more serious commentary on life''s challenges.','/memes/Brace-Yourselves-X-is-Coming.jpg',2,'{}','{"imminent ned from game of thrones","brace yourselves winter is coming","brace yourself"}',0.0,'[0.020670896,-0.03595313,0.035963327,-0.0037189894,0.011246046,-0.025975486,-0.01725601,-0.0220502,-0.02578279,0.037345517,0.010427365,-0.017110849,0.048634823,0.014399111,0.019101517,0.0045868293,-0.013924984,-0.030263282,-0.028289592,0.0299318,0.0093311425,-0.003302004,-0.08465347,-0.032833997,-0.013631084,0.034128062,0.0039340626,0.022293275,0.06280839,0.038881145,0.024749357,0.025400357,-0.0120362,-0.04700501,-0.021576287,0.001645278,1.1554821e-05,-0.07794085,-0.021276949,-0.02501035,0.049460247,-0.01693029,0.040170014,-0.02936704,-0.0028929098,-0.017958954,-0.023035824,-0.029020129,-0.0019533772,-0.029750492,0.02365159,-0.023723355,0.0188537,0.015420127,-0.014062725,-0.0013841392,-0.020395111,0.030901155,0.0071620266,0.02000405,0.042219363,-0.008366037,-0.026111042,-0.01591599,-0.025797851,0.0031304662,-0.00089745625,0.015431006,-0.013989882,-0.00080011494,-0.007889787,0.026640292,0.024842352,0.009224725,-0.050489236,-0.010808975,-0.030721392,-0.0089288205,0.04515694,0.0030968215,0.041265745,0.04869353,-0.029220626,-0.00834641,-0.03985558,0.0029273215,-0.0031255858,0.04110028,0.006715797,-0.026631657,0.003981607,0.0638143,0.0014517677,0.013638248,0.004831276,0.049360983,-0.0026816614,0.054854736,-0.027181642,-0.0076942528,-0.01865881,0.07256977,-0.017732998,0.030437974,-0.041123785,-0.0077961884,0.0072847093,-0.017212238,-0.044547014,-0.031061936,0.04378349,-0.020088244,-0.0045876186,-0.025176624,-0.01603524,0.0061724316,-0.02394316,0.034511466,-0.0032881428,0.01918132,-0.025918543,0.0067960112,-0.026071213,-0.028402591,-0.01760867,-0.014635121,0.004723675,0.028607287,-0.0389627,0.007423