	 ('Unsettled-Tom','This meme template features a striking close-up of a cartoon character''s face, split dramatically down the middle. The left side depicts a gray, somewhat menacing-looking creature with large, intense yellow eyes rimmed with black. These eyes have an almost feline quality, with oval-shaped green pupils that give an eerie, otherworldly feel. The gray skin has a rough, textured appearance, suggesting fur or perhaps scales.

In stark contrast, the right side of the face is pure white, resembling a cute, innocent cartoon animal. This side has a single visible eye - a simple black dot that conveys a friendlier, more approachable demeanor. A small red triangle below suggests a tiny mouth or nose.

The juxtaposition of these two halves creates a powerful visual metaphor, often used in memes to represent duality, internal conflict, or drastic changes in mood or personality. The harsh line dividing the face emphasizes this contrast, making it seem as though two entirely different beings have been fused together.

The background is a muted, nondescript color, focusing all attention on the face itself. At the edges of the image, we can see hints of other features - perhaps an ear on the left side and some wisps of hair or fur at the top.

This template''s power lies in its ability to convey complex emotions or situations through a simple, visually arresting image. It''s particularly effective for expressing ideas about hidden natures, sudden transformations, or the coexistence of opposing forces within a single entity.','/memes/Unsettled-Tom.jpg',2,'{}','{"tom face","concerned tom","tom and jerry","disgusted tom","surprised tom","tom staring down",unsettled/shocking}',0.0,'[0.015619566,-0.016364837,0.004615182,0.0088514825,-0.017965516,-0.057485454,-0.015951393,-0.015631706,-0.04125673,0.063617244,-0.0093930615,0.008813892,0.022002313,0.0035656004,0.007538991,-0.006491253,0.0026517615,-0.020616062,-0.024655247,0.0125705935,-0.00485845,0.029559288,-0.07198482,-0.040663302,-0.0015496445,0.057487275,0.0014695569,0.0022766525,0.04435358,0.008404912,-0.006565414,0.01327283,0.0082400385,-0.05852097,0.011198644,-0.0025573168,0.037987188,-0.05099257,0.0034847683,-0.014384641,0.06581434,-0.008532361,0.013304349,-0.037795395,-0.030850582,-0.022952667,-0.028612949,0.01615591,-0.008540774,-0.015061981,0.006205818,-0.030877264,0.030823639,0.018083245,-0.048722524,-0.029891001,0.0016183874,-0.020869922,-0.008264898,0.020249791,0.042426117,0.016835604,0.026349828,-0.060129207,-0.0336272,0.01609669,-0.049441185,-0.023406329,-0.029113332,-0.011999135,0.013579958,0.013897705,-0.012981023,0.0029401039,-0.046167605,-0.03189645,-0.024425386,-0.050130174,0.04050222,0.009178075,0.02458688,0.020247974,-0.013386439,-0.039760724,-0.009300598,0.0006543994,0.0025907105,0.034760293,0.028275955,-0.022263374,-0.014310589,0.058809128,0.0042950967,0.038220994,0.03569206,0.037345473,0.01788553,0.026280826,-0.009964073,-0.0045776432,-0.014512516,0.056254197,-0.003000085,0.05725827,-0.043202158,-0.009172476,0.03408599,0.010515891,-0.029434545,-0.03206681,0.028987607,-0.032823786,-0.001335846,0.0024076472,-0.009802361,0.030584382,-0.0183416,0.055229567,-0.06650375,-0.014691346,-0.04931449,-0.01290896,-0.0498342,0.009265629,-0.0010528034