	 ('Sparta-Leonidas','This meme template features a dramatic scene from the movie "300," depicting a fierce warrior in the midst of battle. The image is characterized by its intense, gritty atmosphere and muted color palette dominated by sepia tones.

In the foreground, a muscular, bare-chested man with a thick beard is captured mid-shout, his face contorted in a powerful expression of rage or battle cry. His mouth is wide open, revealing his teeth, and his eyes are intense and focused. He has short, dark hair and appears to be wearing some kind of red cape or cloak draped over one shoulder.

The warrior is wielding a long, dark sword or spear in his right hand, raised and ready for combat. His pose suggests he is in the middle of an aggressive action, possibly charging or rallying troops.

Behind him, the background is filled with a chaotic battle scene. Numerous bodies and fallen warriors can be seen strewn across what appears to be a dusty, sun-baked plain or battlefield. The lighting is dramatic, with a hazy, golden quality that adds to the epic and cinematic feel of the image.

This template is often used in memes to represent moments of intense determination, defiance, or rallying against overwhelming odds. The warrior''s passionate cry and the backdrop of battle make it a powerful image for conveying strength, courage, and the spirit of fighting against adversity.

The composition draws the viewer''s eye directly to the warrior''s face, making his expression the focal point of the image and allowing for easy adaptation into various meme contexts where his shout can be reinterpreted or captioned for humorous or inspirational effect.','/memes/Sparta-Leonidas.jpg',2,'{}','{"Leonidas from the movie 300","tonight we dine"}',0.0,'[0.017930558,-0.03709818,0.026474446,0.026591642,0.006741284,-0.029037474,-0.03708247,-0.011517611,-0.016701728,0.037820242,0.025017433,0.0058603375,0.010468075,0.00538759,0.030598665,0.014486381,-0.033239864,-0.04516355,-0.04921098,-0.004834101,-0.0080020195,-0.012465278,-0.052982636,-0.03551501,0.012602255,0.061245,-0.009445823,0.017343996,0.053867854,0.03778216,0.007667334,0.014586885,0.00370694,-0.04885488,-0.0042325375,-0.023919813,0.0042557023,-0.09819625,-0.050286938,-0.021406079,0.045565378,-0.035133123,0.023200262,-0.0068318904,-0.022522388,-0.011813054,-0.029342312,-0.019682001,0.01362272,-0.009613632,0.0026454336,-0.024327992,0.0028498378,0.019278737,-0.023002613,-0.013880418,-0.0061028954,-0.004638021,0.011293003,0.029704332,0.03785078,0.01861796,-0.023653938,-0.01761379,-0.022460217,-0.012076432,0.016214307,0.0015077841,-0.018594716,-0.0026882158,-0.024718277,-0.0030823932,0.027573375,-0.007014812,-0.037429214,-0.017473828,-0.046688702,-0.023738248,0.030667182,0.002217817,0.029057397,0.04457475,-0.03308741,-0.021529403,-0.022205612,0.009249893,-0.0009969107,0.031783782,0.005934288,-0.031490065,0.022138434,0.040736377,0.009035593,0.0141744185,0.008635993,0.028634889,-0.0034394132,0.039866045,-0.027651323,0.01023542,-0.0069069862,0.05665667,-0.026626164,0.030728621,-0.05034236,0.01732651,0.014935908,-0.008950903,-0.016025035,-0.04255859,0.02978164,-0.040903464,0.005107975,0.0020943196,0.0046747043,0.021229248,-0.031054515,0.021749403,-0.036218032,0.010644055,-0.00037092587,0.02605097,-0.013779927,0.0019189391,-0.024030883,0.0009809326,0.017401977,0.007120567,-0.027802482,0.024245132,-0.0053931517