	 ('Picard-Wtf','This meme template is a screenshot from the popular science fiction TV series Star Trek: The Next Generation. The image features a central figure in the foreground, a bald man wearing a distinctive red Starfleet uniform with captain''s pips, indicating his high rank. He is captured in a moment of animated speech or exclamation, with his mouth open and his right hand extended forward, palm up, in a gesticulating manner that suggests he is emphasizing a point or reacting to something with surprise or exasperation.

The background depicts the bridge of the starship Enterprise, with its characteristic curved design and control panels visible. In the background, slightly out of focus, another crew member can be seen wearing a gold uniform, typical of the engineering or security divisions in the Star Trek universe.

The lighting in the image has a somewhat muted, cinematic quality typical of the show''s production era, with a slight green tint that was common in the series'' visual aesthetic. This particular frame has become iconic in internet culture, often used to express frustration, disbelief, or to humorously overexplain something obvious.

The facial expression of the main character is particularly noteworthy - a mix of exasperation and intensity that has made this image highly versatile for meme creators. It''s frequently used to convey reactions to absurd situations or to represent someone passionately trying to make a point.

This image encapsulates a moment of heightened emotion within the typically calm and rational environment of a futuristic starship bridge, creating a contrast that adds to its comedic potential as a meme template.','/memes/Picard-Wtf.jpg',2,'{}','{"captain jean-luc picard star trek","annoyed picard","why the fuck would you",startrek}',0.0,'[0.02745957,-0.035282914,-0.0055125505,0.034034975,0.03741045,-0.060201142,-0.0369219,-0.039940763,-0.006961733,0.044637863,-0.00056344096,-0.0120274415,0.03974439,-0.003975434,0.017968914,-0.035957076,0.008751846,-0.029430678,-0.055203643,0.0005314679,-0.0063336445,0.010150206,-0.08350349,-0.0717782,-0.0264932,0.058625232,-0.014196888,0.036158454,0.053126074,0.019578412,0.0038152183,-0.01937763,-0.028277636,-0.04142379,0.012316412,-0.0056100856,0.024097688,-0.04730533,-0.045652952,-0.045189887,0.032808486,-0.010550724,0.011859574,0.00857572,-0.017582394,-0.019179521,0.020839524,-0.0050672484,0.009167167,0.011874901,0.001921726,0.0025164746,0.009113233,0.029499564,-0.047275838,-0.018710421,-0.00024093164,-0.0071427627,-0.0054671844,0.026841847,0.046623055,-0.023220625,-0.022321545,-0.03629429,-0.047101516,0.0124512715,-0.008704227,0.03360686,-0.039167926,-0.0013693053,-0.0072866036,0.035870895,0.0061302446,-0.009826462,-0.04346508,-0.023787148,-0.0072398353,-0.03069319,0.031085016,-0.027770346,0.017738592,0.05811455,-0.030345729,-0.037355334,0.0088240495,0.005156573,0.017937945,0.030088263,0.018015342,-0.030719003,-0.013061379,0.044088956,-0.0047434717,0.009309983,-0.02823799,0.0440537,-0.019685848,0.052236415,-0.009821704,-0.0025691658,-0.00023994723,0.096514,-0.063826494,0.03101904,-0.018963777,0.008377093,0.04388261,0.00091597205,-0.018023822,-0.043079626,0.03204205,0.02322586,0.031356424,-0.0051046563,-0.016598836,0.039567057,-0.016405102,0.031311892,-0.02580427,0.0151122855,-0.037723742,-0.012391528,0.0010674379,-0.019375253,-0.004112599,-0.024437401,0.04619255,0.026868712,-0.025267418,0.014038522,0.03184955,-0.06681497,0.006