	 ('Hide-the-Pain-Harold','This meme template consists of two vertically stacked images featuring an older man with white hair and a beard, sitting at a white desk or table in a bright, minimalist interior setting.

In the top image, the man is looking at a laptop screen with an expression of mild discomfort or confusion. He''s wearing a light gray button-up shirt and holding a pink coffee mug in his right hand. The desk has a few minimalist decorative items, including two small potted plants and a circular object, possibly a clock or art piece.

The bottom image shows the same scene, but the man''s expression has changed dramatically. He now displays a wide, beaming smile, still looking at the laptop screen and holding the mug. This sudden shift in emotion is the key element of the meme, often used to represent a quick change in mood or realization.

The background of both images is clean and bright, with what appears to be a window letting in natural light. The overall aesthetic is modern and uncluttered, focusing attention on the man''s reactions.

This template is commonly used to humorously depict sudden mood swings, realizations, or reactions to information found online. The contrast between the initial puzzled look and the subsequent joyful expression makes it versatile for various comedic scenarios in meme culture.','/memes/Hide-the-Pain-Harold.jpg',2,'{}','{"sad life harold",maurice,"hide pain climate change",herold}',0.0,'[0.02602895,-0.04453325,0.023820741,0.033425048,0.005865215,-0.061629333,-0.015646407,0.012260171,-0.011373134,0.050008893,0.004600443,-0.0057149413,0.03623881,0.008141625,-0.011336278,-0.028114138,0.0018864765,-0.02073903,-0.040754374,0.036069006,0.024014726,0.033295147,-0.05018282,-0.043719616,-0.010705684,0.055368785,-0.019324137,0.015038492,0.06297107,0.010233214,-0.012828749,0.0021602707,-0.005570994,-0.033175103,-0.020498948,-0.002036931,0.017747583,-0.03870913,-0.01186211,-0.04760473,0.054424666,-0.002103535,0.0248031,-0.017274275,-0.029730022,-0.02517712,-0.033578448,0.0013174509,0.047660735,-0.0036946354,0.018282764,-0.036022764,-0.0047438955,0.0099861305,0.006049241,-0.0314695,-0.02512509,-0.002744887,0.005240344,0.015994057,0.039893214,0.041948125,-0.0065440335,-0.028879358,0.008349386,0.003052025,-0.009258577,-0.017951757,-0.02920047,-0.0038075927,-0.012290111,0.014885841,-0.008953479,-0.015017213,-0.055324186,0.00023532327,-0.017475754,0.005870096,0.003264443,0.0026508432,0.034310088,0.047018684,-0.018900182,-0.012699993,-0.04013639,-0.026512794,0.04695146,0.043096155,0.0185918,-0.04291901,-0.002056803,0.03345371,-0.0024485441,0.009566765,0.0017968802,0.05544842,-0.017662516,0.051372964,0.0022296137,0.015864778,-0.023330405,0.032185614,-0.054580946,0.024681685,-0.044615485,-0.008371343,0.053714182,0.00051358645,-0.058115575,-0.034487147,0.019971542,-0.018169262,0.0038137396,0.031069499,-0.015943594,0.025535293,0.014816494,0.04687395,-0.018789368,0.008858499,-0.044041354,-0.017882964,-0.02787136,-0.012944099,-0.009720636,-0.0016147852,0.0021303091,0.03885541,-0.03375321,0.0