	 ('The-Most-Interesting-Man-In-The-World','This meme template features a distinguished-looking older gentleman seated at what appears to be a bar or table. He has a full head of gray hair and a well-groomed salt-and-pepper beard. His expression is one of confident amusement, with a slight smirk and a twinkle in his eye that suggests he''s about to impart some wisdom or make a witty observation.

The man is dressed in a dark pinstriped suit jacket over a light-colored shirt, giving him an air of casual elegance. His posture is relaxed yet engaging, with one arm resting on the table and his body angled slightly towards the viewer.

In front of him on the table is a green bottle of Dos Equis beer, a detail that has become iconic in this meme template. The presence of the beer bottle is significant, as it ties the image to a well-known advertising campaign.

The background of the image is warm and rich, with dark, patterned wallpaper visible behind the man. This setting evokes a sense of a upscale, perhaps exclusive venue, reinforcing the sophisticated persona of the central figure.

The lighting in the image is soft and flattering, highlighting the man''s features and creating a mood of intimacy, as if the viewer is engaged in a personal conversation with him.

This template is widely recognized as "The Most Interesting Man in the World" meme, derived from a series of Dos Equis beer advertisements. It''s often used to make humorous claims about incredible, improbable, or ironically mundane achievements, playing off the character''s suave and worldly persona.','/memes/The-Most-Interesting-Man-In-The-World.jpg',2,'{}','{"I dont always... but when I do","Dos Equis Man","I don''t always","dos xx","don''t usually guy","i don’t always"}',0.0,'[0.029719668,-0.023358112,0.04359658,0.021877004,-0.0024056113,-0.022739843,-0.032992642,0.013703556,-0.010528814,0.018950485,0.046151523,-0.011551217,0.022412296,0.0045284447,0.019936556,0.011040789,-0.005957358,-0.026390824,-0.025318176,0.023475321,0.020601392,0.013141781,-0.08035191,-0.03501592,0.0061278716,0.04498462,-0.028140964,0.031080553,0.0707526,0.013590485,0.019680157,0.020960242,-0.020332664,-0.050905976,-0.007903522,0.0137846535,0.014579283,-0.056042988,0.0009881163,-0.026525844,0.031842593,-0.012377146,0.03039816,0.0066645076,-0.034321226,-0.022925528,-0.01889895,-0.041471723,0.011771354,-0.021099722,0.021148702,-0.039321076,0.04222382,0.031721883,-0.016429842,-0.014440607,-0.04230439,0.0031598664,0.020830132,0.014481054,0.029840166,0.0080659,0.0019477376,-0.02928366,0.0023570224,-0.0023352066,-0.015797665,0.0058678864,0.004662116,-0.02913516,0.010474132,-0.01294409,-0.013160652,0.0090324795,-0.073545754,-0.004413797,-0.019202612,-0.001929127,0.010845073,-0.0040445356,0.021930104,0.03465993,0.012257429,-0.0028466072,-0.0504312,0.008603176,0.052923232,0.06759262,0.03129211,-0.0064678495,0.011075006,0.04496144,0.0059390105,-0.009260771,0.0017453404,0.033134818,-0.0073695322,0.06289887,-0.01256582,0.020739978,-0.035118315,0.053196914,-0.05443366,0.015648397,-0.010124417,0.017856453,0.048231177,0.0074244426,-0.041995842,-0.053946495,0.028238293,-0.0140101295,0.016643345,0.013491441,-0.040875107,0.021895735,-0.026688186,0.028427703,-0.04944175,0.009943219,-0.04195738,-0.013184605,0