	 ('Marked-Safe-From','This meme template features a minimalist design centered on a simple icon and text. The focal point of the image is a small, stylized flag icon positioned at the top. The flag is represented by a blue triangular shape attached to a thin vertical line, resembling a simplified version of a location marker or pin often seen in digital maps or social media check-ins.

Below the flag icon, the text is arranged in three lines, each in a different font size. The first line, in the largest font, reads "Marked Safe From". This text style is bold and attention-grabbing, suggesting it''s the primary message of the meme. Below that, in a much smaller font size, is the word "Today", creating a pause or break in the reading flow.

The overall layout is stark and uncluttered, with plenty of white space surrounding the icon and text. This clean, minimalist approach allows for easy modification of the bottom text to fit various scenarios or jokes.

The meme format parodies the Facebook feature that allows users to mark themselves as "safe" during disasters or emergencies. By using this format for mundane or humorous situations, the meme subverts the seriousness of the original feature, often for comedic effect.

The simplicity of the design makes it highly versatile and easy to adapt for different contexts, allowing users to insert various phrases or situations in place of "Today" to create humor or commentary on current events, personal experiences, or pop culture phenomena. This adaptability contributes to its popularity as a meme template across social media platforms.','/memes/Marked-Safe-From.jpg',2,'{}','{"facebook marked safe","marked safe flag","marked safe today","facebook safe from"}',0.0,'[-0.012765704,-0.026087143,0.006924272,0.006877187,0.011718105,-0.016684074,0.00033666735,0.0035096654,0.010527889,0.046263143,0.0056881327,0.01526467,0.012805119,0.0007388545,-0.041898523,-0.02963575,-0.02858237,-0.011345116,-0.01723685,0.023818769,-0.022659289,-0.006718691,-0.09247101,-0.041291438,-0.0523714,0.05691417,-0.01632607,0.002903317,0.087951556,0.059842113,0.005952984,-0.014202335,-0.00794946,-0.07150239,-0.010166304,-0.00090476807,0.039080504,-0.0382245,-0.006771093,0.0074880198,0.02193314,-0.04115922,0.078018844,-0.010296544,-0.041562222,-0.018697988,-0.031411484,0.0135416305,-0.00023238765,-0.014964802,0.0059368745,0.0043726414,0.03609279,-0.018803515,-0.022039678,-0.017814673,-0.038820323,-0.03348891,0.0016150469,0.04092585,0.028882558,0.003172027,0.035990685,-0.047188148,-0.059332456,-0.008557389,0.0030250838,-0.016069412,-0.033591904,-0.051126756,0.0065560257,0.028493607,-0.041061237,-0.025754036,-0.037505295,0.0027779585,-0.014858454,-0.01446933,-0.019412521,0.010271096,0.018716654,0.05443998,-0.0016583933,-0.04128131,-0.015269353,-0.026106557,0.020592755,0.022821134,0.018190091,-0.028665738,-0.006444663,0.02809308,0.0030981586,-0.025759827,-0.0018346471,0.007199576,-0.023614416,0.054420102,-0.014369081,0.029644782,0.019233761,0.03158127,-0.029369812,0.041871835,-0.050806306,0.025069257,0.025647232,-0.018505402,-0.04344366,-0.020009559,-0.01677587,-0.016631978,0.007575357,-0.015914796,-0.021086156,-0.0019430894,0.013853065,0.058505397,-0.036131248,0.03787029,-