	 ('Archer','This meme template features a stylized cartoon portrait of a man in a professional office setting. The art style is reminiscent of the animated series "Archer," known for its distinctive visual aesthetic that blends retro and modern elements.

The central figure is a handsome, square-jawed man with jet-black hair neatly combed back. He has piercing blue eyes and a stern, focused expression. His features are sharp and angular, giving him a classically masculine appearance. The man is wearing a crisp white shirt with a dark tie and a gray suit jacket, indicating a professional or business setting.

The background of the image shows an office interior. There are fluorescent lights visible on the ceiling, and behind the man, we can see part of a wooden door frame or cabinet. To the right, there''s a glimpse of what appears to be a yellow or orange piece of furniture, possibly a couch or chair, suggesting a mid-century modern design aesthetic.

The overall color palette is muted, with shades of gray, white, and brown dominating, punctuated by the man''s striking blue eyes and the touch of yellow in the background. This color scheme contributes to the retro-modern feel of the image.

The composition is tightly focused on the man''s face and upper body, making him the clear focal point of the template. This close-up view allows for emphasis on facial expressions and reactions, which is likely why this image is popular as a meme template. It can be used to convey a range of emotions or reactions, from confidence to skepticism, depending on the context and captions added.

The clean lines and bold style make this image highly recognizable and versatile for various meme applications, particularly those involving workplace humor, masculinity, or situations requiring a deadpan or sardonic reaction.','/memes/Archer.jpg',2,'{}','{"Do you want X? Because that''s how you get X. Do you want ants? Because that''s how you get ants.","sterling archer","do you want ants archer","archer ants"}',0.0,'[0.043358773,-0.014692164,0.012162167,-0.010371458,-0.0004652655,-0.036667105,-0.026513796,-0.0005152036,0.008364568,0.03640408,0.005709076,-0.0071577397,0.035400283,0.014944026,0.015544081,0.0008250144,-0.00055867725,0.005221464,-0.019043313,0.031790573,0.005094196,-0.0049663023,-0.0758255,-0.041506995,-0.01658683,0.057414375,-0.015575522,0.009549746,0.03760829,0.017936815,0.012454845,0.012400027,-0.03054382,-0.053282425,-0.010330386,0.010347873,0.036137924,-0.050541326,-0.021997433,-0.02884209,0.020814145,-0.020247526,0.00822809,-0.024145426,-0.0204973,-0.046451148,0.0017512013,0.0064681647,0.007809816,0.010753715,0.03044157,0.0038706767,0.019820292,0.00827497,0.0031233288,-0.050657805,0.010996745,8.8080924e-05,0.0050780764,0.028983017,0.020984415,0.015455799,-0.01199024,-0.0201072,0.0027470298,0.011894646,-0.010506055,0.009577873,-0.014386003,-0.0009841835,-0.016370079,0.020668477,0.0019777822,0.007649038,-0.037488375,-0.004660854,-0.025245065,-0.024645904,0.010434527,0.0056043044,0.02520493,0.036135845,-0.027308526,-0.022489136,-0.02730952,0.0006502857,0.017202469,0.048026316,0.008467774,-0.027776701,-0.008933225,0.059463933,0.005235228,0.006081152,0.0014825874,0.048111815,-0.015835382,0.041884553,0.016262652,0.018548451,-0.03393733,0.057763405,-0.03452828,0.0121972,-0.033985734,0.015206736,0.034367476,-0.006327322,-0.03645226,-0.013927777,0.023578746,-0.021315971,-0.0074019213,0.015078184,-0.030444158,0.01987246,0.01411412,0.06348705,-0.03649679,0.012395983,-0.021777043,-0.0041502556,-0.006088684,-0.0019721354,-0.00068190816,-0.03045934,0.00211843