	 ('Aint-Nobody-Got-Time-For-That','This meme template features a close-up shot of a woman with a very expressive face. She appears to be an African American woman with short dark hair, wearing a light-colored headband or scarf. Her facial expression is notably animated and emphatic, with her eyes wide open and her mouth forming an "O" shape as if she''s in the middle of speaking or exclaiming something with great emotion or surprise.

The woman is wearing a brightly colored top, possibly a tank top or sleeveless shirt with yellow and purple visible. The background behind her is nondescript, showing what looks like a light green or blue-tinted brick wall, suggesting an urban or city setting.

The image quality and style are reminiscent of a screenshot from a video interview or impromptu street interview, giving it an authentic, candid feel. This particular frame seems to capture a moment of realization, shock, or passionate declaration from the subject.

This meme template is often used to convey reactions of disbelief, sudden understanding, or exaggerated surprise in response to various situations or statements. The woman''s vivid expression makes it a versatile template for expressing strong emotional reactions in a humorous or relatable way across many contexts in internet culture.

