	 ('Aaaaand-Its-Gone','This meme template features a scene from the animated TV show South Park, known for its distinctive paper cut-out style animation. The image depicts a character sitting at a desk in what appears to be an office setting.

The character is a middle-aged man with a round face, short dark hair, and a serious expression. He''s wearing a dark suit with a blue tie, typical office attire. His eyes are wide and somewhat blank, giving him a slightly confused or perplexed look, which is characteristic of South Park''s animation style.

The man is seated behind a large wooden desk, with his hands resting on a keyboard in front of a computer monitor. The desk is neat and organized, with a few office supplies visible, including what looks like a yellow desk lamp to the left.

Behind the character, we can see a large window that takes up most of the back wall. Through the window, there''s a view of a bright blue sky with a few small clouds and some green hills or mountains in the distance, suggesting a pleasant outdoor environment contrasting with the indoor office setting.

The room itself has wood-paneled walls and what appear to be green-tinted skylights or ceiling panels visible at the top of the frame, adding to the office atmosphere.

This template is often used in memes to represent moments of confusion, realization, or deadpan reactions in professional or bureaucratic contexts. The character''s blank stare and office setting make it versatile for commenting on work-related situations or general moments of bewilderment in formal settings.','/memes/Aaaaand-Its-Gone.jpg',2,'{}','{"and it''s gone","south park banker guy"}',0.0,'[0.04909992,-0.025509486,0.0063643144,0.022941004,0.015762938,-0.018219907,-0.007580986,0.0072455998,0.012547564,0.051161002,0.019298442,-0.0011140414,0.027223326,0.031924456,-0.013037294,-0.0072126933,-0.016778853,0.0053955256,-0.04306828,0.02513864,0.0059277117,-0.0024201695,-0.054928325,-0.01716001,-0.030033793,0.0578984,-0.021669695,0.023819167,0.063169956,-0.002208606,-0.005401629,-0.0026645572,-0.03846058,-0.05723989,0.013549317,0.0009314701,0.05018279,-0.049577408,-0.022704436,-0.035818648,0.018157542,-0.019524228,0.034533072,-0.01878314,-0.030103656,-0.027998123,-0.024564218,-0.0009063701,0.019525783,0.021467412,0.058519956,-0.0001836109,-0.009829253,0.018309059,-0.0049081845,-0.018324055,-0.018856956,0.024226928,-0.014986167,0.012323871,0.03755594,0.015808517,-0.019990956,-0.031700302,0.0039787614,0.014214472,-0.0059819864,-0.028401908,-0.022502707,0.018518575,0.024333049,0.05401173,0.0129556665,0.013386501,-0.026497427,0.014367751,-0.01146416,-0.013915569,0.014993353,0.036411807,0.029102212,0.032447353,-0.033285767,-0.024987178,-0.01992198,-0.022385746,0.042548366,0.06524442,0.028409043,-0.031071043,-0.03265256,0.047580786,-0.0032308889,0.00042460297,-0.016735023,0.04437005,-0.02037404,0.044580907,0.0042300266,0.020823363,-0.0258431,0.056937702,-0.034056105,0.031178644,-0.012636335,0.0028238012,0.064196534,-0.0042051887,-0.05624017,-0.019759037,0.01723269,-0.015457536,0.003138451,0.013675231,-0.02595326,0.034559395,0.041169714,0.06297714,-0.04440153,0.011214458,-0.034247037,-0.020393122,-0.0025210397,-0.011762525,-0.010992301,-0.00071313453,-0.0028883459,0.04248491