	 ('The-Rock-Driving','This meme template consists of three vertically stacked panels, each showing a scene from inside a car. The images appear to be screenshots from a movie or TV show.

In the top panel, we see a muscular man with short dark hair and a stubbled face. He''s wearing a dark jacket and appears to be in the driver''s seat, looking back over his shoulder with a concerned or questioning expression. His mouth is slightly open as if he''s speaking. A speech bubble to his right is left blank for meme text to be added.

The middle panel shows a young woman with long blonde hair sitting in the back seat of the car. She has a worried or apprehensive look on her face, with her eyebrows slightly raised. The interior of the car is visible around her. Again, there''s a blank speech bubble to her right for customizable text.

The bottom panel returns to the man from the first image. This time we see him from a different angle, facing forward in the driver''s seat. His eyes are wide and his expression has changed to one of shock or realization. The car''s interior is more visible in this shot, including the rearview mirror and part of the windshield.

This template is set up for a comedic exchange between the two characters, with the man''s changing expression in the final panel typically serving as the punchline. The blank speech bubbles allow meme creators to insert their own dialogue, making this a versatile format for various jokes or commentary. The cinematic quality of the images and the expressive performances of the actors contribute to the meme''s effectiveness in conveying a range of scenarios and reactions.','/memes/The-Rock-Driving.jpg',2,'{}','{"race to witch mountain blank"}',0.0,'[0.030556351,-0.014188259,0.013216327,0.0066794707,0.021895312,-0.06273203,-0.033545088,-0.015071779,-0.02381838,0.037673287,0.020553166,-0.0014189183,0.029071031,-0.022396168,-0.015238959,0.009965211,0.012238647,-0.024097692,-0.03916746,-0.01707127,-0.027072787,-0.025084106,-0.06751839,-0.028946932,-0.02454971,0.04455624,0.014688588,0.034365274,0.04679402,0.014736948,0.01809917,-0.006767018,0.018955523,-0.056464173,0.016133001,-0.004878622,0.023161165,-0.02123586,-0.030057676,-0.00082271424,0.022993201,-0.0074491343,0.017096024,-0.02004236,-0.018793942,-0.034389824,-0.0015028086,-0.00041486436,0.011956076,-0.004203446,0.014151559,-0.028978858,0.020467192,-0.011536185,-0.01365465,-0.02748923,-0.02130758,0.0064118626,-0.01765108,0.027987016,0.03932141,0.018987585,0.0019002085,-0.02683809,-0.026111873,0.013177943,-0.0011705655,0.016592097,-0.033495508,0.008004523,-0.02103033,0.028797437,-0.0063239536,0.0043764506,-0.05339593,-0.010631571,-0.02312936,-0.0035341275,0.033958863,0.0008769476,0.023832688,0.05085175,0.0178874,-0.023220496,-0.013659324,-0.03743453,0.012616941,0.022646101,-0.004524844,-0.03670031,-0.01651826,0.043431636,-0.0022328852,0.01043119,0.029838076,0.051769443,-0.03512237,0.015834246,0.01217334,-0.001914793,-0.024227072,0.0554157,-0.038943972,0.050041895,-0.023277337,0.013943743,0.03734181,-0.0034832,-0.037137657,-0.031469624,-0.01533917,-0.016858285,0.014612161,-0.015025498,-0.015635345,0.038400352,0.013948