	 ('Left-Exit-12-Off-Ramp','This meme template consists of two stacked images that create a humorous juxtaposition between a road sign and a driver''s actual behavior.

The top image shows a standard green highway sign suspended above a road. The sign indicates two possible directions: a straight arrow pointing upward for continuing straight, and a right turn arrow branching off from the straight arrow. Above this sign is a smaller yellow sign reading "LEFT" and below it, another small green sign displaying "EXIT 12". The sky visible behind the sign is blue with some puffy white clouds, giving a sense of a clear day. Part of the highway''s metal structure is visible at the top of the frame.

The bottom image depicts a real-life driving scenario that directly contradicts the sign''s instructions. We see a section of highway with a right-curving exit ramp. However, instead of following either the straight path or taking the right exit as the sign suggests, a dark-colored classic car (possibly from the 1960s or 1970s) is shown drifting sideways across multiple lanes. The car is kicking up a cloud of tire smoke, indicating it''s performing a dramatic left turn or drift maneuver across the exit lanes. This action is clearly dangerous and illegal.

The humor in this meme template comes from the stark contrast between the clear, official directions provided by the road sign and the reckless, rebellious action of the driver who chooses to go left instead. It plays on the idea of ignoring obvious instructions or taking an unexpected third option when presented with a seemingly binary choice.

This template can be used to comment on situations where someone deliberately chooses to do the opposite of what''s expected or advised, often in a risky or absurd manner. It taps into themes of defiance, poor decision-making, or humorously subverting expectations.','/memes/Left-Exit-12-Off-Ramp.jpg',2,'{}','{"car drifts off highway","sharp turn on road","car drift meme","left exit ramp 12","swerve meme","swerving car","road meme","no u car skid","car exiting"}',0.0,'[-0.011723753,-0.018823396,0.0007034748,0.016014948,-0.0064698844,-0.07541418,-0.0043323413,0.023131529,-0.008150154,0.084270924,0.015684212,0.033283032,0.04514039,-0.026361287,-0.014147162,0.0053585363,0.008033079,-0.01506701,-0.053665936,0.03362776,-0.019481925,-0.027922485,-0.029524952,-0.040339764,0.006228203,0.032587,0.026706612,0.0010811832,0.056176346,0.040329807,0.027655186,0.007151966,-0.017088922,-0.049464315,-0.010860039,0.0017230136,0.026884852,-0.03181328,0.013727883,0.00675431,-0.0019679226,-0.025084822,0.013360926,-0.04431649,-0.015163919,-0.06496945,-0.0441612,-0.020985764,0.025627384,0.00057607336,-0.009294691,0.0051298495,0.031148817,-0.025677012,-0.026233334,0.0030844605,-0.023228157,0.0056015444,-0.0077969385,0.035007834,0.0494964,-0.019866638,0.0125453,-0.051721044,-0.04477484,0.0024038784,0.00034465623,0.014506765,-0.04827974,-0.007642184,-0.056061707,0.025567912,0.015078632,-0.0061398298,-0.025234299,0.017917715,-0.0125519065,0.005622673,-0.018599106,0.007779831,0.0072384453,0.039052512,-0.00602908,-0.019109767,0.008875253,0.01871567,0.017622823,0.04239086,0.026170524,-0.030445755,0.016844267,0.03431118,0.005472101,-0.008303322,0.032293484,0.049724262,-0.033451974,0.037713338,0.0029378247,-0.007747121,-0.012013724,0.04689188,-0.010021972,0.03402954,-0.029464535,0.007995862,0.033446882,-0.0017299625,-0.06223867,-0.027672643,-0.016992725,-0.022661962,0.030553285,-0.011413682,-0.017532503,0.0235566,0.0082773715,0.052609473,-0.020193705,0.016375793,-0.01928828,-0.043786764,-0.02740167