	 ('Dont-You-Squidward','This meme template features a close-up shot of SpongeBob SquarePants, the iconic yellow sea sponge character from the eponymous animated series. In this image, SpongeBob is sporting a particularly smug, self-satisfied expression. His eyes are half-lidded and slightly squinted, with his characteristic buck teeth prominently displayed in a sly grin.

SpongeBob is wearing his usual attire: a white collar shirt, red tie, and brown square pants. However, his posture and facial expression are far from his typically innocent and cheerful demeanor. Instead, he exudes an air of cockiness or mischievous confidence.

The background of the image shows the recognizable teal-colored interior of SpongeBob''s pineapple house. A curved doorway or porthole is visible behind him, along with some indistinct household items on what appears to be a countertop or shelf to the right.

This particular facial expression of SpongeBob has become a popular meme template, often used to convey a sense of smug superiority, sarcasm, or a "told-you-so" attitude. The exaggerated features and the contrast between SpongeBob''s usually cheerful character and this devious look make it a versatile and humorous image for a wide range of meme applications.

The image quality suggests it''s a screenshot from the actual cartoon, preserving the characteristic animation style of the show with its bold colors and simple, expressive designs. This template captures a moment that''s both instantly recognizable to fans of the show and broadly relatable as a human expression, contributing to its popularity in meme culture.','/memes/Dont-You-Squidward.jpg',2,'{}','{"spongebob grinning","spongebob smirk face","smug spongebob"}',0.0,'[0.03241351,-0.025537398,-0.008857048,-0.008754367,0.015687414,-0.018116698,-0.01763603,-0.016184835,0.014323957,0.005623559,0.013531366,-0.0023918643,0.0350262,-0.00046007455,0.0034671403,-0.045544732,-0.01584633,-0.028015742,-0.049408935,0.026960272,0.0034698597,0.0025972186,-0.028391566,-0.02183746,-0.008159891,0.056468263,0.009546577,0.01397637,0.04824258,-0.001671218,0.014004656,0.020016389,-0.017055737,-0.03389574,0.021656668,0.003893361,0.023674456,-0.035113312,0.0030172467,-0.047969967,0.04693203,-0.028589532,0.0045048506,-0.02476231,-0.01688016,-0.01807036,-0.025749506,0.011409503,0.02600406,-0.00054946134,0.018516857,0.005463743,0.022705434,0.027295994,-0.020199502,-0.032525785,-0.008283008,0.008242626,0.018958122,0.01593732,0.031416968,0.0018884058,-0.039045718,-0.06891134,-0.031444725,-0.007109449,0.0006030888,-0.037833188,-0.017853297,0.008933057,0.0055386093,0.009627695,0.00737984,-0.019662635,-0.049976334,-0.007151668,-0.03952,-0.0065413085,0.017067395,0.022305414,0.051178396,0.04974616,0.0333822,-0.034098804,-0.030760454,-0.0011174323,0.051794063,0.04182311,0.010407501,-0.051313974,-0.047517207,0.09112814,0.001935133,0.021870425,0.017541979,0.042919755,0.019227047,0.059397094,0.022404078,0.016905893,-0.004299119,0.06218457,-0.004090288,0.03200576,-0.0148570575,0.02459369,0.03489681,0.00082050083,-0.065727994,-0.009407935,0.040439617,-0.0002512235,0.025820388,-0.015721278,-0.025679572,0.017348694,-0.005318391,0.068283685,-0.047993895,-0.01838226,-0.034806114,-4.4100307e-05,0.0014831339,-