	 ('Waiting-Skeleton','This meme template features a comical and slightly eerie scene of a plastic or resin skeleton posed in a casual, waiting position on what appears to be a wooden bench or deck. The skeleton is positioned as if it were a person lounging outdoors, creating a humorous juxtaposition between death and leisure.

The skeleton is seated with its bony arms resting on the back of the bench, giving it a relaxed, almost contemplative pose. Its skull is tilted slightly upward, as if gazing into the distance or perhaps enjoying the sunshine. The jaw of the skull is slightly agape, which adds to the comical effect, almost suggesting a bemused expression.

The setting around the skeleton contributes to the meme''s humor and relatability. Behind the bench is a grassy slope, indicating an outdoor environment like a park or backyard. This ordinary backdrop contrasts sharply with the extraordinary presence of the skeleton, enhancing the surreal quality of the image.

The skeleton''s posture and setting evoke a sense of patient waiting or prolonged anticipation, which is often used in memes to humorously represent long waits, procrastination, or the feeling of time dragging on. The image''s composition, with the skeleton centered and facing slightly to the side, makes it easy to add text overlays for various meme contexts.

The weathered appearance of the wooden bench and the natural background give the scene an authentic, everyday feel, which makes the presence of the skeleton all the more absurd and amusing. This contrast between the mundane setting and the macabre subject is key to the template''s versatility for creating humorous or ironic memes about life, death, waiting, or the passage of time.','/memes/Waiting-Skeleton.jpg',2,'{}','{"skeleton waiting on bench in the park","still waiting","waiting for love","waiting skelton","skeleton on bench","the waiting skeleton","me waiting for"}',0.0,'[0.0149226915,-0.028145857,0.011148806,-0.0024783234,0.031669743,-0.038935754,-0.008696485,-0.012571219,-0.003532423,0.04101789,0.025564618,-0.023693098,0.021943014,-0.019685773,-0.0030891963,0.011228278,-0.0026421489,-0.016039345,-0.05108892,0.012414196,-0.013117927,0.0013028365,-0.062038846,-0.033655252,-0.03608248,0.033438016,-0.017555153,0.035324536,0.07693087,0.04372709,0.02073338,0.0034668408,0.02696894,-0.06453025,0.021206154,-0.0010181324,0.023543516,-0.04497128,0.01578499,0.019522496,0.020524405,-0.0023922352,0.012401507,0.012391484,-0.009039663,-0.034560118,-0.009330956,-0.013268969,0.02024605,-0.0200326,0.034142565,-0.014552928,0.0039340737,-0.019926155,-0.029255472,-0.031878866,-0.032492414,-0.028656945,0.0076206466,0.018116718,0.052584104,-0.029276393,-0.016626323,-0.06417604,-0.01516036,0.009136124,0.017921744,0.032102663,-0.01723387,-0.011600692,0.01309865,0.0059551597,0.0034486435,0.0037206758,-0.014504244,0.04240595,-0.021397466,-0.015764365,0.032656576,0.0289807,0.046891037,0.032939885,-0.011115065,-0.03476827,-0.04640292,-0.031883862,-0.024942158,0.023969064,0.033701845,-0.039964333,-0.0062876493,0.046399523,0.008813195,0.016141037,0.005328169,0.050392848,-0.006625436,0.05007738,0.0008356015,0.011166485,0.009399686,0.05278835,-0.035744697,0.019858206,-0.040131826,-0.012582312,0.010366831,-0.007615528,-0.039516225,-0.04038395,0.016713697,-0.028374756,0.0045988066,0.005164911,