	 ('Dr-Evil-Laser','This meme template features a scene that appears to be from a movie or TV show, likely a parody of a classic villain character. The image shows a bald man in a gray high-collared suit, reminiscent of the iconic Dr. Evil character from the Austin Powers film series.

The man is seated behind what looks like a large, spherical object - possibly meant to represent a moon or planet. His hands are raised on either side of his head, with his fingers curled in a dramatic gesture. His facial expression is one of exaggerated surprise or excitement, with his mouth open wide as if he''s exclaiming something.

The background of the image is split diagonally. On the left side is a deep red color, while the right side is a lighter gray or white. The corner where these two colors meet is adorned with a series of rivets or bolts, giving the setting a mechanical or high-tech appearance.

The lighting in the scene is dramatic, with the red background providing a stark contrast to the man''s pale skin and gray outfit. This lighting, combined with the futuristic set design, contributes to the over-the-top, theatrical nature of the scene.

This image is often used as a reaction meme to express mock villainy, dramatic reveals, or exaggerated excitement about plans or schemes. The character''s theatrical pose and expression make it a versatile template for adding humorous captions or for representing moments of comically evil glee.','/memes/Dr-Evil-Laser.jpg',2,'{}','{"Dr. Evil quotation marks","Dr Evil Air Quotes","doctor evil","austin powers quotemarks","austin powers guy with fingers to the side"}',0.0,'[0.03059217,-0.018531332,0.01148816,0.005329795,0.009352615,-0.074872114,-0.018019719,-0.029641967,-0.029521972,0.047992248,0.056417175,0.014355618,0.04342895,-0.012468668,-0.008368784,0.0014549482,-0.0005635619,-0.0288784,-0.014387233,0.02134114,0.001280048,0.017459089,-0.06658716,-0.043764587,0.0031403624,0.026741182,-0.00059792935,0.017788094,0.025510246,0.026377993,0.012124794,-0.014988663,0.0046688085,-0.04391083,0.010042756,0.002727575,0.05756251,-0.063916616,0.021203142,-0.034354024,0.038035385,0.007236476,0.023820125,-0.021624286,-0.03306743,-0.039356537,-0.004899087,0.0026895152,0.0052130837,-0.00682105,-0.004750191,0.005243069,0.0063336333,0.036384817,-0.038224947,-0.045801606,6.5880435e-05,-0.014006343,-0.005596187,-0.00023722141,0.030363498,-0.009395624,0.008304345,-0.030383686,-0.033563353,0.020081095,-0.02388138,-0.022945793,-0.013208365,0.013371093,0.017376984,0.014054353,0.015135087,0.018874442,-0.042431638,-0.0059254356,-0.0050686575,-0.031179696,0.033063557,-0.016533524,0.030599475,0.04601503,-0.021102576,-0.035999425,0.0038068942,-0.018416123,0.045064535,0.040474467,0.005645894,-0.0339563,-0.0011320243,0.032258105,-0.01984639,-0.0018455198,0.015700571,0.03041974,-0.019360775,0.026337823,-0.025545938,0.007912596,-0.015728295,0.06753226,-0.07527265,0.027948612,-0.0036155249,0.014069656,0.0600451,-0.008286811,-0.016758565,-0.048233617,0.027023444,-0.025705243,0.033628203,-0.0053269,-0.05387646,0.027441537,0.011691071,0.03773439,-0.024039194,-0.008714928,-0.030031972,-0.045548208,0.0172