	 ('Maury-Lie-Detector','This meme template features a middle-aged man with short gray hair and glasses, sitting in a chair against a backdrop of exposed brick walls. He''s wearing a dark suit jacket over a black shirt, giving him a formal yet casual appearance. The man''s expression is one of curiosity and slight skepticism, with his eyebrows raised and his mouth slightly open as if he''s about to speak.

In his hands, he''s holding a white envelope or card with the word "Maury" printed on it in bold black letters. This is a clear reference to the "Maury" talk show, known for its dramatic reveals and paternity test results.

The setting appears to be a television studio set, with a warm-toned column visible to the left, suggesting a professional broadcast environment. The lighting is even and flattering, typical of TV studio lighting.

This image is frequently used as a reaction meme, often in contexts where someone is about to reveal surprising or dramatic information. The "Maury" envelope, combined with the host''s expectant expression, creates a sense of anticipation and imminent revelation.

The composition of the image focuses tightly on the man and the envelope, drawing the viewer''s attention to his reaction and the potential news he''s about to share. This close-up shot enhances the dramatic tension inherent in the meme''s typical usage.

Overall, this meme template capitalizes on the cultural recognition of the "Maury" show format and the associated expectations of shocking revelations or plot twists, making it a versatile image for expressing moments of surprise, disbelief, or dramatic unveiling in various online contexts.','/memes/Maury-Lie-Detector.jpg',2,'{}','{"The lie detector determined that was a lie. The fact that you X determined that was a lie. Maury Povich.",muary,"you are the father"}',0.0,'[0.046095416,-0.01435612,0.031042608,0.033237178,-0.011562111,-0.04314555,-0.04840017,0.015172846,-0.035295893,0.033910196,0.020974979,-0.012548226,0.021600973,0.037790857,-0.03919842,0.0011120277,0.013838175,-0.014958582,0.0014555766,0.022702703,0.034021933,0.020437222,-0.07427148,-0.048765272,-0.00776868,0.03889225,-0.027374525,0.019378673,0.043737594,0.007178253,-0.010813923,-0.00825759,0.0042105224,-0.04465106,-0.023556653,0.0019546521,0.027441408,-0.02643216,-0.034010746,-0.031508744,0.020453643,-0.015781429,0.015109012,-0.008118196,-0.052743185,-0.047721144,0.0024393997,-0.008725145,0.030722786,0.013131336,0.013429366,-0.014728492,0.017321728,-0.010268459,-0.016679123,-0.03314894,-0.030740349,-0.01055727,0.012652272,0.0016174498,0.017941805,0.002765637,-0.0041218265,-0.04606081,-0.0014567012,0.04470059,-0.013901604,-0.013265225,-0.0001725812,-0.031357076,0.027823875,0.01329547,0.0046743536,-0.004431481,-0.045076814,-0.021476517,-0.0063893073,-0.011486613,0.009619597,-0.012145097,0.006498984,0.026098257,0.01409114,-0.03610133,-0.03202241,-0.033295028,0.007410498,0.031985875,0.029356899,-0.020093793,-0.015379945,0.041927334,0.01831239,-0.01625612,0.018966578,0.046416648,-0.002477161,0.02848216,0.01376607,0.043749467,-0.0009405352,0.0402583,-0.05848867,0.0037155498,0.0115162255,0.032996353,0.08477838,-0.013273173,-0.04215108,-0.017848117,0.013520164,-0.05210787,-0.003090402,-0.012434651,-0.07220975,0.05919014,-0.0016551806,0.059205834,-0.028877648,-0.0007726981,-0.038830172,-0.0096137775,-0.017664