	 ('Put-It-Somewhere-Else-Patrick','This meme template features two vertically stacked panels from the animated TV show SpongeBob SquarePants, focusing on Patrick Star, the pink starfish character, in a crowded, chaotic scene.

In the top panel, Patrick is prominently displayed in the center, his pink form taking up much of the frame. His expression is one of alarm or distress, with wide eyes and a gaping mouth showing his prominent teeth. Patrick''s arms are outstretched, adding to the sense of panic or excitement. Surrounding Patrick are several other colorful sea creatures, each with exaggerated expressions of surprise, shock, or concern. These include characters like a blue fish with bulging eyes, a yellow fish looking worried, and a pink creature with a startled look.

The bottom panel shows a continuation or slight variation of the scene. Patrick is still central, but his expression has changed slightly, appearing more confused or questioning. His mouth is still open, but less dramatically so. The surrounding characters have shifted positions slightly, maintaining their exaggerated expressions but in slightly different poses or angles.

The overall composition is busy and vibrant, with a multitude of bright colors – pinks, yellows, blues, and greens – creating a visually striking and chaotic atmosphere. The close-up nature of the shots emphasizes the characters'' exaggerated facial expressions and reactions, making it perfect for meme usage where extreme emotions or overreactions are being portrayed.

