	 ('Bernie-I-Am-Once-Again-Asking-For-Your-Support','This meme template features an elderly man with white hair and glasses standing outdoors in a wintry setting. He''s wearing a heavy, beige-colored coat with a hood, suggesting cold weather. His expression is serious and somewhat exasperated, with his mouth slightly open as if he''s speaking emphatically.

The background shows bare trees and a street, indicating a suburban or small-town environment. There''s a hint of snow on the ground, further emphasizing the winter season. The sky appears overcast, adding to the cold, stark atmosphere of the image.

The man''s posture and facial expression convey a sense of frustration or insistence, as if he''s repeating something he''s said before. This ties into the text overlay "I am once again asking," which has become a popular phrase associated with this meme format.

The image quality suggests it''s a screenshot from a video, likely a campaign ad or public address. The word "Bernie" appears in the top right corner, identifying the subject of the image.

This meme template is widely recognized and often used to express situations where someone needs to repeatedly request or state something, playing on the exasperated look of the man in the image. It''s become a versatile format in internet culture, adaptable to many different contexts where persistence or repetition is the theme.

The composition of the image, with the man centered and facing the camera directly, makes it particularly effective as a meme template. It allows for easy addition of text above or below the image, making it highly customizable for various humorous or satirical purposes.','/memes/Bernie-I-Am-Once-Again-Asking-For-Your-Support.jpg',2,'{}','{"bernie sanders commercial","bernie sanders 2020 campaign","asking for your financial support","once again bernie"}',0.0,'[0.021177046,-0.001012358,0.009998724,0.02012775,0.0077340803,-0.019695146,-0.013863815,0.033767752,-0.010142656,0.061945036,0.0071018287,-0.031252436,0.05076675,0.0054909876,0.007867658,-0.02753548,-0.0048300764,-0.020869035,-0.01657832,0.032477714,-0.009473365,-0.013306874,-0.05237485,-0.05451981,9.8637865e-05,0.027780024,-0.023461372,0.02966014,0.052864835,0.025520423,0.036044642,-0.019662574,-0.029956354,-0.05592284,-0.012451939,-0.010697511,0.022963589,-0.050330706,-0.003955693,-0.016734574,0.016080923,-0.044457756,0.017637055,-0.019104283,-0.027365906,-0.053554587,-0.0559467,0.009086039,0.024611667,-0.019641733,0.01513919,-0.018391356,0.02279861,0.0071768095,0.023855498,-0.003904418,-0.020204592,0.01815203,-0.017754037,-0.0013893548,0.031888463,0.005103348,0.011158338,-0.01854294,-0.0051297895,-0.009987345,-0.006332916,0.018385038,-0.009388204,0.002573912,-0.022588199,0.018222291,0.025408477,-0.016001105,-0.013368924,0.0061331205,-0.038218282,-0.023284538,-0.013758548,0.0415816,0.0008619149,0.029162815,-0.008068819,-0.015130265,-0.02079026,-0.03278223,0.00849792,0.023479566,0.025641493,-0.016609354,-0.018621054,0.045405205,-0.0076998626,0.043577455,0.0120067075,0.04597723,0.0061442056,0.023263719,0.005531772,0.007326081,-0.0020833232,0.08505511,-0.0026159568,0.05464986,-0.055774927,0.0069037327,0.025156176,0.010143803,-0.07664492,-0.009423618,-0.0044429535,-0.008663107,0.021003488,-0.0097559085,-0.041408107,0.0068861437,0.026674101,0.019246368,-0.0021975478,-0.0001388449,-0.036137573,-0.021136174,-0.03112