	 ('Boardroom-Meeting-Suggestion','This meme template is a comic-style sequence consisting of three panels, depicting a scenario that typically unfolds in a corporate or office setting.

In the first panel, we see a meeting room scene. A long table dominates the frame, with four characters seated or standing around it. The character at the head of the table, likely a boss or team leader, is standing and leaning forward with both hands on the table, appearing to address the others. Three other characters are seated: one on the left side of the table (seen from behind) and two on the right side facing the viewer. The background is a soft pink color, giving a slightly warm tone to the scene.

The second panel shows a closer view of just the two characters seated on the right side of the table, plus a new character who has appeared on the far right. All three are now speaking, indicated by speech bubbles above their heads. Their facial expressions are more animated, with the first two looking enthusiastic while the third (new) character appears contemplative or concerned.

The third panel dramatically shifts the scene. It''s split into four sub-sections, creating a more dynamic and emotionally charged composition. The top-left section shows a close-up of the original boss character, now with an angry or frustrated expression. Below this is a dejected-looking version of the third character from the previous panel. The right side of this panel opens up to show a view of a multi-story office building, with a figure being flung out of one of the windows, implying that someone (likely the dejected character) has been fired or forcefully removed from the premises.

This template is often used to humorously illustrate scenarios where someone offers an unpopular opinion or suggestion in a group setting, leading to their metaphorical "ejection" from the situation. The exaggerated expressions and the sudden shift to the exterior view of the building create a stark contrast that emphasizes the comedic punch of the meme.','/memes/Boardroom-Meeting-Suggestion.jpg',2,'{}','{"throw a guy out the boardroom window","board room meeting","boss throwing employee","company meem template","any ideas?","man getting thrown out window"}',0.0,'[0.031922657,-0.04864613,0.02455394,0.025742078,0.04690023,-0.07510273,-0.04416314,-0.006443136,-0.017446602,0.035349462,0.010998332,0.033860616,0.025824362,0.0011389635,-0.0058149365,-0.008719459,-0.0069903885,-0.012116024,-0.023684632,0.018960284,-0.025535624,-0.02067296,-0.095317975,-0.031842384,-0.020166466,0.062045343,-0.0046730572,0.009591044,0.064317346,0.016159907,-0.021781124,-0.038916998,-0.012056379,-0.040393364,0.0056654564,-0.01264871,0.02116069,-0.0277725,-0.041678812,-0.017811587,0.017121037,-0.0062970407,0.03177224,-0.03477355,-0.0122357225,-0.027073627,-0.008195166,0.021171413,0.01960891,0.00054265844,0.020742808,-0.0006609916,-0.0141356625,0.012941148,-0.027478391,-0.041757274,-0.032311372,-0.013251739,0.01355413,0.0411618,0.01991316,0.011705064,0.014036927,-0.02202098,-0.02411332,0.003986606,-0.028550243,-0.023503976,-0.028364928,0.0030956373,-0.023398563,0.040053107,0.013543399,0.0011788162,-0.044972643,-0.020932768,-0.019981671,-0.020822246,-0.004139152,0.0062320107,0.038832884,0.053545874,-0.015067311,-0.006823,-0.0131878825,-0.033112694,0.043432556,0.046248402,0.013969211,-0.020872813,-0.012276303,0.042205557,-0.010262749,-0.0006511034,0.009914075,0.039756827,-0.02542662,0.058323756,-0.008521479,0.0010997057,-0.04559741,0.044840444,-0.06351447,0.018338338,-0.048342846,-0.00087656564,0.088179804,0.006291543,-0.025676703,-0.040023502,-0.007804611,-0.023135375,0.026649602,0.007643051,-0.