	 ('Roll-Safe-Think-About-It','This meme template features a close-up shot of a man with a thoughtful and slightly mischievous expression. The man is African American, with short dark hair and a well-groomed beard. He''s wearing a black leather jacket and a gold watch, giving him a stylish, urban appearance.

The focal point of the image is the man''s facial expression and gesture. He''s tapping his temple with his index finger, a gesture often associated with indicating intelligence, having an idea, or implying that someone should think carefully about something. His eyes are slightly narrowed, and there''s a hint of a knowing smile on his face, suggesting he''s sharing some sort of insight or clever thought.

The background is slightly out of focus but appears to be an urban setting. There''s a reflective surface behind him, possibly a shop window, and you can faintly see some text that looks like opening hours written on glass.

This image has become a popular meme template often used to convey sarcastic wisdom, pointing out obvious solutions to problems, or highlighting ironically clever (but often impractical or unethical) ideas. The gesture and expression perfectly encapsulate a "think about it" moment, which makes it versatile for a wide range of humorous or satirical captions.

The lighting and color grading of the image give it a cinematic quality, suggesting it may be a still from a movie or TV show. The warm tones and the subject''s charismatic expression make the image engaging and memorable, contributing to its popularity as a meme template.','/memes/Roll-Safe-Think-About-It.jpg',2,'{}','{"thinking black guy","black guy pointing at his head","can''t blank if you don''t blank","smart black dude","guy tapping head","wimsical black guy",kayode,"british rapper","terrible genius advice","you can;t","it''s not ____ if ____","if you dont","terribly genious advice","you don''t have to","black man thinking","terribly genius advice","you don''t need","negro pensante","you dont need","genius black-guy"}',0.0,'[0.028485136,-0.008902677,0.014654763,0.0024949904,-0.016340308,-0.040191583,-0.03941296,-0.0017682406,-0.0043747644,0.042756174,-0.0064720656,-0.0022457077,0.028413335,-0.0052230326,0.0035493178,0.012802033,0.017076237,-0.0352354,0.0017602755,0.012072664,0.0102979895,-0.006910919,-0.050347023,-0.052021157,0.012931275,0.0609985,-0.046400685,0.0249581,0.06755541,0.044016454,0.014980503,0.022774663,0.010913529,-0.052493654,-0.022190068,-0.015857318,0.038275618,-0.049446255,-0.022665683,-0.02269678,0.00015103427,0.011957022,0.02035689,-0.0045069125,-0.030012287,-0.005757676,-0.042593475,-0.015799379,0.02401374,-0.011432896,-0.002920582,-0.02077216,0.010659617,0.023141697,-0.020609917,-0.02702066,-0.020145526,-0.013591241,-0.008212529,0.015418671,0.030484745,-0.00010729128,-0.019580444,-0.03916407,-0.029436229,0.014438774,-0.024873182,0.0071284533,-0.031114297,-0.0308221,-0.01248485,-0.0043964735,0.045141827,0.006025485,-0.03554045,-0.011512048,-0.025416337,-0.015915817,0.016895663,-0.0022537368,0.013801884,0.05004671,-0.019979564,-0.034806363,0.0037818847,-0.022498267,0.03181296,0.027973272,0.019141657,-0.053805187,0.010072007,0.060249366,0.028165283,0.009213592,0.030855726,0.03415041,0.018929023,0.047342047,-0.012290256,0.038053162,-0.0456646