	 ('See-Nobody-Cares','This meme template consists of two stacked images from what appears to be a movie or TV show scene set in a tropical resort or beach location.

In the top image, we see an outdoor dining area with umbrellas and thatched-roof structures in the background. Two men are seated at a round table in the foreground. On the left is a man in a red polo shirt and a straw hat, appearing calm and reserved. On the right is a larger man wearing a vibrant floral Hawaiian shirt, who seems to be excitedly gesturing or explaining something with an animated expression.

The bottom image shows a closer view of these same two characters, now standing and facing each other. The man in the red polo is on the left, turned towards his companion and listening. The man in the Hawaiian shirt is on the right, still animated and appearing to be in the middle of an enthusiastic explanation or story. His body language suggests he''s fully engaged in whatever he''s communicating.

The setting behind them has changed slightly, showing more of the beach area with palm trees and possibly some structures or vehicles in the background.

This template is often used to represent scenarios where one person (represented by the animated character in the Hawaiian shirt) is excitedly explaining or sharing something to a more reserved or skeptical listener (the man in the red polo).

The contrast between the reserved demeanor of one character and the unbridled enthusiasm of the other creates a comedic dynamic that''s often exploited in memes to illustrate various social situations or conversations where one party is significantly more excited or invested than the other.','/memes/See-Nobody-Cares.jpg',2,'{}','{"Jurassic Park Dennis","see? no one cares","see? nobody cares"}',0.0,'[0.033050615,0.011674109,0.01714352,0.0020488661,0.02524728,-0.058733497,-0.04026083,-0.0049761254,0.008932634,0.016425392,0.039333563,0.029351432,0.018006148,0.006389807,-0.028023254,-0.0035603226,0.008118828,-0.036394976,-0.02354784,0.017328223,-0.014197642,0.004372083,-0.05827437,-0.018843181,-0.005716846,0.057574026,-0.01182075,0.031566173,0.08093187,0.00959032,0.019537022,0.0023528778,0.0057677636,-0.027635653,0.019570012,0.009603124,0.043542117,-0.05122703,-0.039513785,-0.06546038,0.019975077,-0.0055042454,0.018536786,-0.02063276,-0.0152439745,0.007714796,-0.002145278,-0.02485668,0.013923143,0.0027815718,0.017628696,-0.01392483,-5.0380124e-05,0.040908,-0.035303153,-0.023728665,-0.032930017,-0.01662206,0.034517467,0.019211525,-0.004896046,0.00982639,-0.017976057,-0.0585868,-0.026969176,0.005956556,-0.002951423,-0.008633416,-0.00031175357,-0.012824118,0.017035995,0.016978854,0.01566007,0.0046455036,-0.029314322,-0.005080463,-0.007334686,0.006981112,0.016497519,0.0022426613,0.052693713,0.074160516,0.0070699714,-0.017990006,-0.045317788,-0.01627085,0.05010694,0.022324072,0.03516503,-0.02590998,-0.023665149,0.0435124,-0.024828436,-0.0030673924,-0.008542296,0.036917035,0.0061843004,0.047839783,-0.023006491,0.032899525,0.009903189,0.061041884,-0.03907801,0.021998433,-0.051003247,0.029942391,0.03707753,0.0015027305,-0.03294253,-0.033053383,-0.0072298045,-0.006099146,0.018608188,-0.022483926,-0.009301726,0.032218795,0.018237252,0.013616066,-0.051127814,-0.023567477,-0.04045769,-0.00019041232,-0.01115581,0.030532066,0.014797664,-0.0006009,0.01626988,0.02261977,-0.059885237,0.