	 ('Confession-Bear','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a black bear, specifically an Asian black bear or moon bear, known for its distinctive white crescent marking on its chest (though not visible in this image). The bear is captured in a pensive, almost melancholic pose that has made it a popular template for expressing disappointment or contemplation in meme culture.

The bear''s face is the focal point of the image, showing remarkable detail and expression. Its small, round ears are just visible at the top of its head. The bear''s eyes are dark and reflective, conveying a sense of intelligence and emotional depth that resonates with viewers. Its snout is slightly wrinkled, with a glistening black nose, and its mouth is slightly downturned, giving the impression of a frown or pout.

The bear is resting its chin and paws on what appears to be a weathered log or branch. Its large, powerful claws are clearly visible, contrasting with the vulnerable and almost human-like expression on its face. The fur is a rich, dark color, appearing silky and dense.

The background is soft and out of focus, emphasizing the bear''s face and expression. The lighting is gentle, possibly natural daylight, which highlights the textures of the bear''s fur and brings out the nuances in its facial features.

This image has become iconic in meme culture due to the bear''s remarkably relatable expression. It''s often used to convey feelings of regret, disappointment, or resigned acceptance of an unpleasant situation. The contrast between the powerful predator and its seemingly vulnerable emotional state adds to the image''s appeal and versatility as a meme template.','/memes/Confession-Bear.jpg',2,'{}','{"sad bear","confession bear hd","unpopular opinion bear"}',0.0,'[0.01292889,-0.007987043,0.040432777,0.016194679,0.018932313,-0.048987947,-0.028805738,0.00046737844,-0.022129383,0.034764875,0.007412362,0.00013076377,0.024444785,-0.021220412,0.016550351,-0.020357292,0.015721243,-0.02376433,-0.031157568,-0.00699859,0.016750095,-0.001571552,-0.06012323,-0.029115275,0.016292373,0.06417272,-0.019627254,0.027421774,0.056016997,0.01712206,-0.015666315,0.018615905,0.008672295,-0.075635575,-0.004366624,-0.011791221,0.017607303,-0.041807786,0.017905898,0.018778233,0.03926285,-0.025898978,0.045233108,-0.009041542,-0.024597572,-0.03779804,-0.04329392,-0.012820661,0.031504158,-0.04322338,0.023601403,-0.036918916,0.019280361,0.010121985,-0.02523534,-0.032901727,-0.015599515,-0.019824179,0.029135112,0.014907873,0.037456494,0.006131241,0.0052472074,-0.033245742,-0.030589623,0.0017583058,-0.030359788,-0.031258356,-0.020453738,0.0050181844,0.0039186785,0.007590051,0.000101684855,-0.017701108,-0.043564368,-0.030974919,-0.04174119,-0.04640321,-0.0026044163,0.014871321,0.00043731218,0.026306268,0.018617248,0.0024727588,0.014801242,-0.026909992,0.008525433,0.027207384,0.034850687,-0.01809081,-0.023839781,0.07431726,-0.01587137,0.03775303,0.026535131,0.025258943,0.0067704674,0.003974568,-0.044018023,0.03267709,-0.0023426816,0.014287069,-0.017853592,0.020180555,-0.043041643,0.001561011,0.0037640852,-0.0033822951,-0.028648859,-0.046006344,0.016349198,-0.027708933,-0.02047069,-0.010185396,-0.022707716,0.0026875858,-0.020007951,0.058046672,-0.021376615,-0.011853055,-0.045433197,0.020337371,-0.01316