	 ('Hard-To-Swallow-Pills','This meme template consists of two vertically stacked images, both featuring hands in a soft, pastel-colored illustration style.

In the top image, a hand is shown holding a large white pill bottle. The bottle is cylindrical with a white cap and a label that reads "Hard to swallow pills". Another hand is pointing at the label with its index finger, drawing attention to the text.

The bottom image shows an open palm facing upwards, holding three small round pills. One pill is larger and appears to have a line across its middle, while the other two are smaller and one has "543" printed on it. A finger from another hand is seen touching or moving one of the smaller pills.

The background in both images is a soft gradient, transitioning from a light blue-green at the bottom to a pale peach or beige color at the top, giving the entire image a calm, almost dreamy atmosphere.

This template is commonly used to represent difficult truths or realities that people find challenging to accept or "swallow". The top image sets up the concept of hard-to-swallow pills as a metaphor, while the bottom image typically represents the specific "pill" or truth being presented in the meme.

The clean, simple style and pastel colors create a contrast with the often harsh or uncomfortable truths this meme format is used to convey, adding an element of irony to its usage. The detailed illustration of hands and pills gives the meme a sense of tangibility and relatability, making it effective for a wide range of topics and situations.','/memes/Hard-To-Swallow-Pills.jpg',2,'{}','{"hard pills to swallow"}',0.0,'[0.00074677134,-0.036638513,0.04015885,0.013922553,0.02731364,-0.05801287,-0.03482661,0.0089865755,-0.024069851,0.047113955,0.005255778,0.0010688858,0.04210729,0.019602891,-0.014904392,0.027909325,0.015227437,-0.020130783,0.0015698825,-0.0057212855,-0.01288531,0.02250823,-0.07833843,-0.04224566,-0.014717531,0.024407744,0.024284558,0.025192901,0.055770244,0.026716368,-0.024209436,0.002516255,0.027359672,-0.060825266,0.01369272,-0.011147768,0.028471889,-0.050063845,0.00077899627,-0.051560998,0.035165705,-0.012893336,0.030252615,-0.006045323,-0.018605817,-0.011033088,-0.017724099,-0.006224353,0.0040115933,-0.013099204,0.024662932,-0.0133661665,0.031197002,0.014842306,-0.039551623,0.01769875,-0.011643259,-0.05072301,0.0073697926,0.0061563943,0.017668702,-0.0020968528,-0.0021978323,-0.05211435,-0.035507705,0.009534089,-0.029316403,-0.011538477,-0.023562945,-0.049179863,-0.007610577,0.015249678,-0.013361314,-0.022168772,-0.038484376,-0.03101998,0.0035940313,0.009249606,0.011171966,0.016995687,0.018980226,0.05080996,-0.010783225,-0.017510934,-0.035957456,0.040305916,0.0038924108,0.023810297,0.030150997,-0.04412875,0.004107575,0.048642356,-0.033104885,-0.0067917006,-0.018004442,0.025741698,-0.032123815,0.022235885,-0.0067176167,0.004328065,0.004383433,0.03444872,-0.0056108893,0.04793329,-0.034634642,0.020220129,0.053063195,-0.000970197,-0.030672558,-0.01585254,0.00991648,-0.028713834,0.013422367,-0.010391672,-0.0039778524,0.013626589,0.004536381,0.031495176,-0.045139,0.042954903,-0.024618082,0.007862481,-0.009889703,0.005678891,-0.0030922587,0.03114209,0.00668