	 ('Mugatu-So-Hot-Right-Now','This meme template captures a memorable scene from what appears to be a movie or TV show, set in a crowded theater or cinema. The image focuses on a flamboyant couple in the foreground, surrounded by other audience members.

In the center, a man with bleached blonde, curly hair is wearing a striking red and blue outfit with silver fringe details, reminiscent of a Western-style performance costume. His expression is one of exaggerated surprise or excitement, with his mouth wide open. He''s holding a small white dog, also dressed in red, adding to the eccentric nature of his appearance.

Next to him sits a woman with jet-black hair in a blunt bob cut. She''s wearing a red outfit that appears to be made of leather or vinyl, with a dramatic neckline. Her makeup is bold, featuring dark lipstick and strong eyebrows. Her expression is serious, almost stern, contrasting sharply with her companion''s enthusiasm.

Behind them, other audience members are visible. A woman in a zebra-print top is smiling, while others seem focused on whatever is happening off-screen. The variety of expressions and the stark contrast between the main couple and the rest of the audience creates a sense of comedic juxtaposition.

This image is often used as a reaction meme to represent extreme enthusiasm (the blonde man) paired with indifference or disdain (the dark-haired woman), or to highlight the contrast between different types of people in the same situation. The theatrical nature of the main characters'' appearances adds to the meme''s versatility in expressing over-the-top reactions or stark differences in taste or opinion.','/memes/Mugatu-So-Hot-Right-Now.jpg',2,'{}','{"Mugatu from Zoolander","Will Farrell",mugato}',0.0,'[0.020904262,-0.032903302,0.0019756414,0.0016891591,0.007474776,-0.0620973,-0.01833596,-0.007811641,-0.02681919,0.04395721,0.011756375,-0.0029093614,0.025488498,0.0137159685,-0.0017942704,-0.005349601,-0.012460763,-0.05445044,-0.036125228,0.023332346,-0.035366688,0.016350655,-0.08269268,-0.0118983425,0.0029703283,0.077089235,0.027176335,-0.0029229084,0.05825896,0.0035524196,0.016945582,0.018653484,0.0031610557,-0.02135944,0.029564057,-0.027772667,0.01294825,-0.04453552,-0.047116328,-0.055795148,0.034484807,-0.03111209,0.018090928,-0.024236396,-0.03394169,0.006504548,0.034658995,0.0025706044,0.024424493,-0.01556774,-0.008326224,-0.030703835,-0.010146478,0.0330979,-0.012847016,-0.05105726,-0.015843263,-0.0056522274,0.017494528,0.026405392,0.04248922,0.0005717921,-0.014124233,-0.03422613,-0.00828736,0.0043906537,-0.004443696,-0.0018957983,-0.048882224,-0.022719767,0.056675643,-0.0023008382,-0.004452791,-0.020183701,-0.051227104,-0.013393897,-0.023681141,0.00046835945,0.01577269,0.0070777996,0.03277802,0.033214603,0.0034721007,-0.022430187,-0.00939051,-0.018699687,0.020024171,0.03707538,-0.009652043,-0.014912332,-0.022161888,0.03739414,-0.0252133,0.007598897,-0.0053647556,0.023507647,-0.0025002824,0.008480718,0.009175049,0.00088423426,-0.035186503,0.0676104,-0.05776056,0.05386137,-0.05676961,0.031645857,0.024129473,0.015794486,-0.05160337,-0.04574409,-0.025421768,-0.028878257,0.023942037,0.003285961,-0.0235268,0.052219912,0.02412212,0.0644674,-0.055688698,-0.01893026,-0