	 ('Success-Kid','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a young toddler with a distinctive, determined expression. The child is wearing a white and green raglan-style shirt, which stands out against the geometric background.

The toddler''s facial expression is the key element of this meme. Their brow is slightly furrowed, mouth set in a subtle but unmistakable expression of triumph or satisfaction. One hand is raised in a fist pump gesture, adding to the air of victory or determination.

The background is divided into several geometric sections, each a different shade of blue or purple. This creates a striking contrast with the child''s image and gives the meme a modern, graphic feel. The angular nature of the background further emphasizes the child''s rounded features and expressive pose.

This image is widely known as the "Success Kid" meme, often used to express feelings of accomplishment, determination, or overcoming challenges. The child''s expression and gesture perfectly encapsulate a sense of "nailing it" or achieving something against the odds, which has made this image a popular choice for sharing small victories or moments of pride online.

The composition of the image, with the child slightly off-center and the background creating a sort of spotlight effect, draws the viewer''s attention directly to the toddler''s face and gesture. This framing enhances the impact of the expression and makes the image highly effective as a reaction meme.

Overall, this template''s combination of an adorably determined child and a stylized background has made it one of the most recognizable and enduring memes in internet culture, capable of conveying a wide range of triumphant or satisfied sentiments.','/memes/Success-Kid.jpg',2,'{}','{"Motivation Baby","Motivation Kid","Success Baby"}',0.0,'[-0.0066416524,-0.010311282,0.014673402,0.011948304,0.015262815,-0.012199502,-0.01846381,-0.0062242,0.017485412,0.005009252,-0.04284349,0.010780152,0.035944324,0.008023291,0.019443981,0.007820394,0.0029973837,-0.018780304,-0.035993837,0.010414508,0.001926002,0.019640703,-0.0864402,-0.03792651,0.029015996,0.037481274,0.011292601,0.005722006,0.06993516,0.029368844,-0.015414086,0.013038578,-0.0077579096,-0.0090435045,-0.01552325,-0.006771148,0.016352825,-0.038252164,0.0103212,-0.03362282,0.040063836,-0.03742431,0.041750334,-6.711193e-05,-0.044715624,-0.020186447,-0.00749048,-0.027386349,0.045428403,-0.0024751471,0.012050577,0.0022007208,0.019145565,-0.006777579,-0.011423663,0.007939621,0.0082451925,-0.02118644,0.025020896,0.060582686,0.013427132,0.0034873711,0.009832428,-0.034788046,-0.020936215,-0.028475584,-0.00513395,-0.0070499405,-0.018979128,-0.0050019333,-0.016038608,0.008309779,-0.0042862706,-0.017523315,-0.029030474,0.01349498,-0.036679868,0.0062097223,0.0018728849,0.019490322,0.012112625,0.05542968,0.025336377,-0.042340014,-0.03365067,-0.024010392,0.008993632,0.052913506,0.009244796,-0.0345384,0.016772354,0.05353508,-0.038156938,0.0075593353,0.010157702,0.045474112,-0.015702128,0.029626844,-0.026578236,0.00798116,0.0037647707,0.024571372,-0.005348564,0.02859591,-0.09238341,0.014704476,0.03023608,-0.03559134,-0.03684272,-0.038198557,-0.00068159826,0.0014238223,0.025315339,-0.033694286,-0.024679061,0.050032046,0.011168835,0.063294105,-0.02330367,-0.027484607,-0.028034046,-0.0053941584,-0.019308241,-0.004261759,-0.00950513,0.014858688,-0.011013504,0.04125577,-0.04232103,0.012776007,-0.03060043,-0.038464446,-0.022552907,0.025438