	 ('Expanding-Brain','This meme template consists of four vertically stacked panels, each depicting a progressively more intense or "enlightened" representation of a human brain.

The first panel shows a basic X-ray-like image of a skull and brain in blue outlines against a black background. The brain is visible within the skull, but it''s a simple, non-detailed representation.

The second panel features a more detailed, blue-tinted image of a human head in profile. The brain is more prominently displayed, with purple and white areas indicating neural activity. This image suggests increased brain function or awareness.

In the third panel, the image becomes even more vibrant. The head silhouette is now pink-tinted, and the brain inside is glowing white with intense areas of light, implying a state of high mental activity or enlightenment.

The fourth and final panel takes the concept to an extreme. Here, the brain is depicted as a bright teal, highly detailed organ, surrounded by radiating beams of light that extend beyond the outline of the head. This suggests a state of transcendent knowledge or cosmic understanding.

Each successive image in the sequence implies a greater level of mental awakening, intelligence, or enlightenment. The progression from a simple X-ray to a glowing, energy-radiating brain creates a visual metaphor for expanding consciousness or increasing levels of realization.

This template is often used in memes to humorously represent levels of understanding or awareness about a particular topic, with the most "enlightened" state often being associated with an absurd or ironically simplistic idea. The format invites creators to fill in text beside each image, typically progressing from common knowledge to increasingly niche or outlandish concepts.','/memes/Expanding-Brain.jpg',2,'{}','{"levels of intelligence","expanding brain template","brain expanding","expanding brain meme","mind expansion",4-expanding-brain-meme,"enlightement meme","expanding mind","big brain"}',0.0,'[0.0031044127,-0.040673867,0.0040440066,-0.0047424817,0.0039908765,-0.04751984,-0.023063475,2.6703743e-05,-0.039258495,0.064128526,0.017974269,-0.00063257286,0.0421409,-0.004925312,-0.02195867,0.00048119226,-0.03894039,-0.03452894,-0.042974573,0.011194619,-0.02370748,0.023509553,-0.08565227,-0.0062385583,-0.020416843,0.048450105,0.01932164,0.020613825,0.059124075,0.033451937,0.0050356872,-0.018233966,0.042670876,-0.06777379,-0.005845629,0.010433837,0.021748953,-0.050170325,-0.00822968,-0.013001415,0.011305337,-0.0037191408,0.005895741,-0.0391313,-0.0464821,-0.022473356,-0.019104619,-0.01878242,0.01970322,-0.013991815,0.0021061853,-0.035217818,0.018865924,-0.0057876846,-0.0059446786,-0.03479197,0.001162308,-0.012484947,-0.020972036,0.02464002,0.052419595,0.027680803,0.027147556,-0.03563412,-0.018902134,0.024961099,-0.021129344,-0.034544416,-0.047219455,-0.022257905,-0.03166914,0.020102497,-0.02268872,-0.026980808,-0.019518662,-0.011959171,-0.0038753175,-0.0046471204,0.0050519607,-0.019152954,0.02481549,0.03190813,-0.015286531,0.0065840553,0.00395006,-0.013245603,0.0004731321,0.009318742,0.031536784,-0.058999002,0.004060715,0.030952182,0.016735319,0.00997971,0.017272191,0.029780399,-0.014465427,0.03966963,0.0019215473,0.01074141,-0.030258888,0.06111661,-0.03432908,0.04070215,-0.051599402,-0.01404393,0.01643791,0.04006773,-0.01596617,-0.06399767,0.020503376,-0.011275207,0.