	 ('Running-Away-Balloon','This meme template consists of two panels, both featuring simplistic cartoon-style drawings on a light blue background.

In the top panel, we see a white, stick figure-like character with a rounded body and head. The character has large, circular eyes and a wide, open mouth expressing excitement or enthusiasm. Its arms are outstretched, reaching eagerly towards a large, bright yellow circle on the right side of the frame. This yellow circle dominates almost half of the panel, suggesting it''s an object of great interest or desire for the character.

The bottom panel shows the same scene but with a significant addition. The white character is in the same pose, still reaching for the yellow circle. However, behind it now stands a much larger, pink blob-like figure. This pink figure has small, beady eyes and a slight smile. It has wrapped one of its appendages around the white character''s midsection, effectively holding it back or restraining it. The white character now has a single tear drop on its cheek, indicating distress or frustration at being held back from its goal.

This template is often used to represent situations where someone is enthusiastically pursuing something, only to be held back or prevented from reaching it by an unexpected obstacle or responsibility. The contrast between the character''s initial excitement and subsequent frustration, coupled with the comical appearance of the restraining pink blob, makes this a versatile format for expressing disappointment, thwarted plans, or the conflict between desires and obligations in a humorous way.

The simplistic art style and clear emotional shift between the panels contribute to the meme''s effectiveness in conveying complex ideas through a quick, visually striking format.','/memes/Running-Away-Balloon.jpg',2,'{}','{"big yellow ball and pink guy","me vs my hopes and dreams","good grades and success","cant reach"}',0.0,'[0.020243764,-0.029038493,0.007914082,0.018016038,0.017724479,-0.05536485,0.016991166,0.005546205,-0.0053402884,0.060757615,-0.009518428,0.010580791,0.021350877,0.007813614,-0.021521462,-0.004174367,0.01244471,-0.019827142,-0.021631531,0.02806294,-0.021899879,0.0023763347,-0.060277663,-0.014271106,-0.012817354,0.06904593,0.0075915754,0.004683487,0.051274903,0.01205576,-0.026939953,-0.001806343,0.0122748185,-0.052233305,-0.0069895335,-0.025113806,0.017756782,-0.04927129,0.015815156,-0.035163093,0.044164054,-0.015841076,0.031545,-0.029482745,-0.036817886,-0.026903547,-0.022132935,-0.006441381,0.030940596,-0.025596589,0.009253369,-0.022890212,0.0032547617,-8.1468555e-05,-0.020091124,-0.011941166,-0.0004566896,-0.039676607,9.388277e-05,0.025896654,0.02464347,0.015777985,0.008114765,-0.050360046,-0.040532913,-0.019270694,-0.042001408,-0.020852558,-0.015133501,-0.00051900244,-0.00053778937,0.025750881,-0.0013025837,-0.03956603,-0.05651164,0.012285708,-0.02250726,-0.010029665,0.015457677,0.010723676,0.05335187,0.066446744,-0.0064444956,-0.02267393,-0.0069292937,-0.009742885,0.027023274,0.016028918,0.008358494,-0.037555456,-0.011809075,0.04667997,-0.019956287,0.021155404,0.023355171,0.025918484,-0.020859499,0.036141153,-0.017137673,-0.001288045,-0.0256015,0.06544882,-0.02574555,0.02376854,-0.066837445,-0.0023259628,0.05000892,0.009331976,-0.038595255,-0.035000365,0.0075537083,-0.030131413,-0.006191378,-0.013882058,-0.02334064,0.031442486,0.0051349574,0.075329855,-0.052332595,-0.022492861,-0.025361603,0.0011493117,-0.05175159,0.0028551233,0.0071720784,0.01612931,0.0045642746,0.03894022,-0.038404875,0.024392065,0.007025323,-0.022530572,0.007133597,0.046