	 ('UNO-Draw-25-Cards','This meme template is a split image that humorously portrays a dilemma in the popular card game UNO. The left side of the image shows a close-up of a hand holding a large UNO card. This card is black with white text reading "or draw 25," indicating a special action card in the game that forces the next player to either play a specific card or draw 25 cards as a penalty.

On the right side of the image, we see a man sitting at a table, looking somewhat defeated or resigned. He''s holding a large fan of UNO cards in his hands, implying he chose to draw the 25 cards rather than play the required card. The man is wearing a dark shirt and appears to be in a casual indoor setting, possibly a home or community space. There''s also a can of soda on the table in front of him, adding to the casual game night atmosphere.

The juxtaposition of these two images creates the humorous situation: the tough choice presented by the action card on the left, and the consequence of choosing to draw cards on the right. The man''s expression and the sheer number of cards in his hand emphasize the comical outcome of his decision.

This meme template is often used to represent difficult choices or situations where all options seem undesirable, with the large handful of cards symbolizing an overwhelmingly negative outcome. The format invites creators to replace the "or draw 25" text with other choices, while the image of the man with many cards remains as the punchline, representing the reluctant acceptance of an unpleasant alternative.','/memes/UNO-Draw-25-Cards.jpg',2,'{}','{"do something you don’t like or draw 25 cards","uno dilemma","uno or draw 25","draw 25","do something you don''t like or draw 25","draw 25 meme",sprite}',0.0,'[0.010013299,-0.023753045,0.0106605925,0.028155547,-0.028760985,-0.053278632,-0.030186716,0.014993712,-0.0056528975,0.063189685,0.036170322,0.013743547,0.036421835,0.015411422,-0.024672246,0.026311828,-0.015633777,-0.021807063,-0.013526102,0.012971285,-0.01676811,-0.0037951756,-0.05569091,-0.040002745,-0.004176431,0.020814283,0.009793839,0.038004432,0.055736613,0.0097366255,-0.008412284,-0.010768824,0.0042447587,-0.053096168,-0.01990125,-0.013228955,0.027592404,-0.031126983,-0.027606143,-0.04129932,0.016553584,-0.034907244,0.031878505,-0.011422504,-0.02389111,-0.03856996,-0.035659783,-0.038880713,0.037067614,-0.016535224,-0.001671239,-0.025466733,0.015670154,-0.0025068598,-0.014091989,-0.012883302,-0.02488465,-0.0092217205,0.0062647066,0.029578438,0.012839745,-0.038806655,0.0021491426,-0.023353266,-0.021321934,-0.0071639162,-0.023617472,-0.02152922,-0.021764327,-0.020088391,-0.010251644,0.014461629,-0.015275421,-0.014252571,-0.040929984,0.027418623,0.0071219886,-0.031244414,-0.01941362,0.007809254,-0.008342617,0.050636724,-0.02666153,-0.008451068,-0.03764937,-0.033686794,0.05187881,0.033321604,0.016723389,-0.052417137,-0.004615947,0.064701244,-0.0025242367,0.025650926,0.028810585,0.06707153,-0.007081067,0.029860053,-0.0024212303,0.0009782572,0.006769036,0.021704268,-0.013899019,0.01804898,-0.02821999,0.0066100736,0.02689778,0.00019449857,-0.015916271,-0.04477747,-0.