	 ('10-Guy','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a young man with a distinctively uncomfortable or strained facial expression. The subject appears to be in an indoor setting, likely a bedroom or dorm room, with a plain light-colored wall visible in the background.

The young man has short, dark hair and is wearing a black shirt or tank top. His face is the central focus of the image, taking up most of the frame. His expression is what makes this image notable as a meme template - his eyes are slightly narrowed, his brow is somewhat furrowed, and he has an awkward, forced smile that doesn''t reach his eyes. This combination creates an air of discomfort, as if he''s trying to appear relaxed or happy but is actually experiencing some internal struggle or anxiety.

The lighting in the image is harsh, creating a slightly shiny or sweaty appearance on the subject''s face, which adds to the overall sense of discomfort or stress. There''s a hint of a blue object, possibly a bottle, visible at the bottom left corner of the frame.

This image has become known as the "10 Guy" or "Really High Guy" meme, often used to express confused or nonsensical thoughts, particularly those that might occur when someone is under the influence. The subject''s strained expression and slightly dazed look make it a perfect template for captions describing muddled thinking or absurd realizations.

The poor image quality, including slightly grainy texture and somewhat washed-out colors, adds to its authenticity as a candid, spontaneous photo that''s been widely shared online. This raw, unpolished quality contributes to its effectiveness as a relatable and humorous meme template.','/memes/10-Guy.jpg',2,'{}','{"Really High Guy","Stoner Stanley","Brainwashed Bob","stoned guy","ten guy","stoned buzzed high dude bro"}',0.0,'[0.04590981,-0.024141693,0.024481857,0.002537969,0.0051407916,-0.04613705,-0.0025723898,0.0030476043,-0.009653974,0.027232721,0.0049645016,-0.046024427,0.041233536,-0.004039915,-0.0017123832,0.013285734,-0.005950322,-0.015088673,-0.026856134,0.03610494,0.022305053,-0.005078221,-0.043358136,-0.0077631776,0.00076755765,0.045926597,-0.008343083,0.0142794745,0.04628742,0.019532016,-0.012460434,0.0030141564,-0.0026168732,-0.05090348,-0.005324674,0.0027669324,0.056210738,-0.05024122,-0.014514038,-0.0059498656,0.040007275,-0.011146337,0.022197455,-0.0103234835,-0.023365524,-0.036823925,-0.044013064,0.01449094,0.03351438,0.007262554,0.009688521,-0.035465926,0.03508976,0.02804315,-0.011859543,-0.010759534,-0.002390646,-0.0012003714,0.015520565,0.030329324,0.022043739,0.031326365,-0.0013591099,-0.0339198,-0.014292135,0.014287617,-0.024488417,-0.006754379,-0.014352773,-0.021191236,0.0057454547,-0.004994478,0.010810748,0.012946114,-0.039939377,0.00038903745,-0.06828848,-0.011115947,0.031100454,0.023969641,0.011017498,0.03552803,-0.006446342,-0.022562008,-0.03733823,-0.011702886,0.0074127135,0.01538091,0.011016762,-0.0312635,-0.025082905,0.05322537,0.0017607654,0.016348012,0.03321951,0.02394947,0.0009132896,0.03980564,0.008733269,0.014990874,0.008632133,0.036032066,-0.0126413405,0.040978506,-0.025347965,-0.0010845211,0.025655007,0.005922767,-0.058884118,-0.021229923,0.01146767,-0.043780196,-0.022108605,0.0016058271,-0.053871028,-0.0026692983,-0.021332728,0.069942236,-0.048601795,-0.012277199,-0.021846792,0.024282267,-0.0016549863,-0.01807164,-0.023925083,-0.