	 ('Bad-Pun-Dog','This meme template consists of three vertically stacked images featuring a Husky dog and a small stuffed animal, likely a wolf or another dog plush toy. The setting appears to be a cozy indoor environment, with the dog resting on what looks like a bed or couch covered in a light-colored blanket.

In the first panel, the Husky is shown in a calm, attentive pose. Its piercing blue eyes are focused on the small gray plush toy that it''s gently holding in its mouth. The dog''s expression is serene and curious.

The second panel captures a moment of joy and excitement. The Husky''s mouth is open in a happy pant, tongue visible, giving the impression of a doggy smile. The plush toy is now positioned slightly differently, as if the dog has just tossed it up or is playing with it.

The third and final panel shows the Husky in a state of high excitement or surprise. Its mouth is wide open, teeth visible, in what appears to be a playful bark or exclamation. The plush toy is now held at an angle that suggests rapid movement, as if the dog is vigorously shaking it.

Throughout the sequence, the background remains consistent, showing elements of a home interior including a wall-mounted shelf, some artwork, and the edge of a window with blinds. The progression of the dog''s expressions and interactions with the toy creates a narrative of escalating enthusiasm and playfulness.

This meme template is often used to represent a progression of emotions or reactions, typically starting with calm consideration, moving to dawning realization, and ending with an exuberant or shocked response. The Husky''s expressive face and the contrast with the small, inanimate toy make it a versatile format for various humorous or relatable scenarios.','/memes/Bad-Pun-Dog.jpg',2,'{}','{"joke dog","whisper joke dog","happy husky","joke telling husky","pun husky","bad joke dog","ifunny - punhusky watermarked"}',0.0,'[-0.0041794265,0.009312084,0.026257327,0.020548726,-0.031834245,-0.060501922,-0.026431615,0.028672246,-0.0034020292,0.03287569,-0.00072502845,0.044266492,-0.0040106783,0.022282528,-0.010670181,0.012054739,-0.019279236,-0.0312231,-0.062131077,0.026532214,-0.010990903,0.013877288,-0.08634266,-0.028640077,0.0051435702,0.07908691,0.006828907,-0.0068576196,0.06703757,0.017025996,0.011286284,0.019418301,0.044767283,-0.053257883,-0.010473135,-0.011014513,0.024754077,-0.014856256,-0.0096937325,-0.040953916,0.0406941,0.00015453917,0.04820876,-0.037085295,-0.03677072,-0.02583598,-0.019112092,0.0013121613,0.027692368,-0.041603804,0.02630791,0.007538278,-0.0035714912,-0.036276348,-0.01266838,-0.04475012,-0.0012310299,-0.03851294,0.0068214955,0.043843668,0.05607764,0.00029072302,0.009713907,-0.025360517,-0.025861267,0.010256486,-0.028013928,-0.025101341,-0.032216825,-0.0056083286,0.029255297,0.02359407,-0.022377692,-0.030911233,-0.01154643,-0.0037112297,-0.027571354,0.00935252,-0.009613445,0.017005652,0.051898915,0.040774133,0.016134527,-0.014911676,-0.011551375,-0.041599754,0.02898193,0.035083506,0.0009774965,-0.0055582,-0.031631414,0.036203176,-0.003451137,0.019404141,0.0013132803,0.022072641,0.016336542,0.024166811,-0.003968347,-0.001199529,-0.0038401983,0.013333204,0.005962214,0.029944876,-0.062898375,0.012576428,0.0162706,6.556993e-05,-0.03720339,-0.016514333,-0.024807373,-0.041555367,-0.0014329279,0.014341765,0.0024871684,0.023712844,-0.010865076,0.06413348,