	 ('First-World-Problems','This meme template features a close-up image of a woman in an emotionally distressed state. The focus is on the lower half of her face and one hand, creating a powerful and intimate portrayal of grief or anguish.

The woman''s face is partially obscured by her right hand, which is pressed against her forehead in a gesture commonly associated with distress, frustration, or intense emotion. Her eyes are closed, emphasizing the internal nature of her struggle. Tears are visible on her cheek, glistening in the light and adding to the raw, vulnerable atmosphere of the image.

The lighting in the photograph is soft and warm, coming from the side, which creates gentle shadows and highlights the contours of her face and hand. This lighting technique adds depth and emotion to the scene, making the tears and facial expression more prominent.

The woman has dark, slightly tousled hair that falls around her face, framing the visible portions and adding to the sense of dishevelment and emotional turmoil. Her skin appears smooth but marked by the tracks of tears, showing a mix of youth and profound emotion.

The background is out of focus and neutral in tone, keeping all attention on the subject''s expression and body language. This lack of context allows the image to be widely applicable to various situations involving sadness, regret, or overwhelming emotion.

This meme template is often used to convey feelings of intense sadness, disappointment, or emotional pain in a relatable and visually striking way. Its power lies in the universal nature of the expression and gesture, which can resonate with a wide audience across different contexts and cultures.','/memes/First-World-Problems.jpg',2,'{}','{fwp,"woman crying","crying woman","sad woman","crying lady"}',0.0,'[-0.0057916935,-0.036487237,-0.0074797086,0.016662829,-0.008220191,-0.07759604,-0.012413357,-0.021094333,-0.00050632155,0.042766385,-0.018335104,-0.015751101,0.0247087,-0.007029147,0.002749522,-0.009125087,0.035697278,-0.015077933,-0.028068688,0.017466761,-0.010792414,-0.004924457,-0.075141445,-0.033106916,0.00021311601,0.06429825,0.03407903,-0.008395898,0.03719217,0.020930111,-0.065168016,0.02901101,-0.013636757,-0.04051821,0.012505812,-0.030939033,0.011395083,-0.052720886,-0.032375276,-0.030206664,0.023797238,-0.02307239,0.04201147,-0.030947475,-0.022375816,-0.017531626,-0.0116561055,-0.008614424,0.040420823,-0.00033097522,-0.009374685,-0.03525619,0.013675246,0.0127300415,-0.013212391,-0.010515422,-0.00120748,-0.020846449,-0.009709304,0.0074064513,0.0611706,-0.014860638,-0.01039004,-0.039058253,-0.034330226,0.0033830132,-0.018357035,-0.005512478,-0.021730395,-0.041065294,-0.0004582855,-0.015987279,0.0077753537,-0.026845144,-0.042540547,-0.007692828,-0.016495751,-0.022422649,0.020102806,0.016741019,0.006665544,0.038021233,-0.009313667,0.015439825,0.0026259087,-0.014625801,-0.022537282,0.019775484,0.00030532564,-0.03648841,-0.019998373,0.05096747,-0.034021042,0.029833855,-0.00040823733,0.036493544,-0.0026579057,0.009278751,-0.010411316,0.0198056,-0.020466555,0.04342185,-0.0154519575,0.05032441,-0.032934822,-0.00071283744,0.032516196,0.010789428,-0.011565112,-0.060956564,0.010416459,-0.03449161,-0.031300932,-0.0017420751,-0.026557837,0.058513053,-0.01765716,0.04612696,-0.048446193,-0.020135542,-0.018976606,0.016872298,-0.0077563818,-0.028134456,0.02675245,0.00108169