	 ('Imagination-Spongebob','This meme template features the iconic cartoon character SpongeBob SquarePants, a cheerful yellow sea sponge with a wide, toothy grin. SpongeBob is shown from the chest up, wearing his signature white shirt, red tie, and square brown pants. His large blue eyes are wide open, giving him an excited and enthusiastic expression.

The most striking element of this image is the vibrant rainbow arching over SpongeBob''s head. The rainbow is composed of multiple colorful stripes - purple, blue, green, yellow, orange, and red - and is adorned with small white star-like sparkles. This rainbow creates a magical, whimsical atmosphere around the character.

SpongeBob''s arms are raised on either side of him, with his hands open in a gesture that suggests wonder, celebration, or presenting the rainbow above him. His posture and expression convey a sense of joy and amazement at the colorful spectacle.

The background behind SpongeBob and the rainbow is a muted olive green, which allows the bright colors of the character and rainbow to pop vividly. This contrast enhances the fantastical and surreal quality of the image.

This meme template is often used to express feelings of happiness, wonder, or childlike excitement. The combination of SpongeBob''s gleeful expression and the magical rainbow creates a perfect visual representation of unbridled enthusiasm or the celebration of something colorful and positive.','/memes/Imagination-Spongebob.jpg',2,'{}','{"spongebob rainbow","nobody cares","bob esponja tpm"}',0.0,'[0.034366783,-0.024556918,-0.014714048,-0.008481269,0.0036842711,-0.0122654885,0.015350208,-0.009508656,0.021386141,0.045193665,0.008960872,0.003977113,0.038471237,0.0007069599,-0.00977862,-0.04651057,-0.031212335,-0.05047935,-0.05557156,0.016667757,-0.008149526,0.0044143875,-0.03480205,-0.012748218,-0.017221732,0.058166802,0.0018024058,0.011327824,0.04795269,0.0049085496,0.028952323,0.013329049,-0.00078735256,-0.041408736,0.042812206,0.014326753,0.0065334463,-0.043604065,0.0064855353,-0.053233292,0.035235956,-0.033838566,0.00509958,-0.034072317,-0.03268918,-0.030855209,-0.02977479,-0.005785436,0.037332572,-0.013315857,0.02235924,-0.0025390114,0.03554096,0.023042174,-0.025430638,-0.03207396,-0.008508642,-0.007984591,0.021373754,0.0143860495,0.008027909,0.023158172,-0.027774587,-0.07960114,-0.038016167,-0.008541948,-0.003941541,-0.03568477,-0.020507121,-0.017361984,-0.00717816,0.03213266,0.00085142563,-0.038228877,-0.0380213,-0.017161157,-0.05003402,-0.020680131,-0.004610773,0.0137403235,0.033664174,0.026952384,0.013075511,-0.0130395675,-0.02901644,0.0066977087,0.032397777,0.03575364,0.01732469,-0.04665794,-0.045297578,0.0768247,0.013385095,0.034787215,0.0057758153,0.040027943,0.004065993,0.053103212,0.020493278,0.013206875,0.032556895,0.049718585,-0.013288219,0.034548126,-0.010642718,0.03567656,0.030872146,0.043733515,-0.026711889,-0.018597668,0.04809876,0.005158213,0.0377351,0.00028967235,0.012226557,0.02763369,0.0002986577,0.0810076,-0.05274447,-0.018370306,-0.044901118,0.007272499,-0.017336229,-0.009623741,0.019248256,0.011367369,-0.0050446475,0.051781148,-0.023859689,0.0