	 ('Be-Like-Bill','This meme template features a minimalist stick figure design set against a stark white background, creating a high-contrast, simplistic aesthetic. The stick figure is positioned slightly off-center to the right, drawn with thin black lines that form a basic human shape - a circular head, a straight vertical line for the body, and simple lines for arms and legs.

The stick figure''s face consists of two small black dots for eyes and a curved line forming a simple smile, giving it a cheerful, friendly expression. This basic emoticon-style face adds a touch of warmth and personality to the otherwise bare design.

What makes this image particularly noteworthy is the addition of a realistic, detailed winter hat perched atop the stick figure''s head. The hat is a light gray or beige color, likely made of wool or a similar material, with a folded brim. It''s topped with a contrasting dark red pom-pom, adding a pop of color to the otherwise monochromatic image.

The juxtaposition of the highly detailed, three-dimensional hat against the two-dimensional simplicity of the stick figure creates a visually striking and somewhat humorous effect. This contrast between realism and abstraction is often used in memes to highlight absurdity or to draw attention to a particular element.

The image is framed by a thin black border, further emphasizing its meme-ready, shareable format. The simplicity of the design allows for easy modification and the addition of text, making it a versatile template for various meme scenarios, particularly those involving winter themes, clothing choices, or the idea of being prepared or unprepared for different situations.','/memes/Be-Like-Bill.jpg',2,'{}','{"bill the stick figure with a hat","this is bill"}',0.0,'[-0.00029494183,-0.011987154,-0.0002795951,-0.027449975,0.026388193,-0.0444756,-0.0043727662,0.0078591155,-0.016211951,0.030351702,0.0121316,0.014035723,0.050242107,-0.015738789,-0.013114371,0.025349446,0.0015722766,-0.008200227,-0.0130717335,0.02048665,-0.024935786,-0.0009617391,-0.08211833,-0.04563675,-0.031389277,0.049535226,-0.01785154,-0.00054083153,0.068351865,0.026732823,0.0054670624,0.011998369,0.016209116,-0.08022932,-0.003464211,-0.022504844,0.00816345,-0.04101046,0.00472766,0.0032710081,0.056814775,-0.03380761,0.016773148,0.002656852,-0.009928701,-0.032263752,-0.0293681,0.0068580736,0.039270062,-0.025547948,0.031318154,-0.010095323,0.031949047,0.012387997,-0.009766714,-0.0067943633,-0.0028369944,-0.023745378,-0.005956313,0.013067803,0.04810643,0.010599357,0.032320805,-0.028138679,-0.051022917,0.0054397746,-0.011874754,-0.011496882,-0.025402574,-0.002858527,0.0072584874,0.0115757985,-0.0014634972,-0.021522414,-0.028332723,0.015553978,-0.035907906,-0.041230723,0.01426153,0.028244771,0.023260387,0.043238565,-0.017646799,-0.0015031272,-0.012604257,0.0072498233,-0.0051722955,0.02365689,0.029146073,-0.039682057,-0.008586895,0.037446264,-0.007980451,0.020215362,0.032113455,0.04603238,-0.015105125,0.052464794,-0.019706907,0.016226562,-0.021642162,0.06327732,-0.006101503,0.041602995,-0.027604403,-0.024099577,0.007039697,0.014570497,-0.044820435,-0.023251025,0.016005332,-0.003359624,-0.0028880872,0.012129257,-0.03131023,0.026536388,0.020104779,0.029788392,-0.04038689,-0.011072377,-0.039606888,-0.01038308,-0.