	 ('Drake-Hotline-Bling','This meme template features two vertically stacked images of a man against a bright yellow background, creating a stark visual contrast. The man is wearing a vibrant red puffy jacket in both images, which stands out boldly against the yellow backdrop.

In the top image, the man is shown with a disapproving or dismissive expression. His eyes are squinted, and his face is turned slightly to the side. His hand is raised in a gesture of rejection or refusal, palm facing outward as if to say "no" or "stop." This pose conveys a sense of aversion or dislike towards something.

The bottom image presents a dramatic shift in mood. Here, the same man is depicted with a pleased, almost blissful expression. His eyes are closed, and he''s sporting a contented smile. His body language is more open and welcoming, with one hand visible making an approving or pointing gesture. The man''s face is tilted upwards slightly, enhancing the impression of satisfaction or agreement.

The juxtaposition of these two contrasting emotions and body languages forms the core of this meme template. It''s typically used to express preference of one thing (represented by the bottom image) over another (represented by the top image).

The man''s attire, particularly the bright red jacket and what appears to be a yellow shirt with a logo visible in the bottom image, adds to the vibrant, eye-catching nature of the template. The consistent yellow background ties the two images together visually while allowing the subject''s expressions and gestures to be the focal point.

This template has become widely recognized in meme culture for its versatility in expressing opinions, preferences, or reactions to various situations or choices.','/memes/Drake-Hotline-Bling.jpg',2,'{}','{drakeposting,drakepost,"drake hotline approves","drake no yes","drake like dislike","drake faces"}',0.0,'[0.015562054,-0.026908575,0.028943332,0.015581874,0.0018044894,-0.06044908,-0.013305455,0.002941192,-0.031380165,0.06419985,0.007789819,-0.011133549,0.032488495,0.0039455537,-0.0011403132,-0.029525546,-0.0034167278,-0.03011328,-0.053292662,0.017479315,-0.016428191,-0.013751532,-0.06578016,-0.031523984,-0.010547166,0.060183637,-0.02130598,-0.008070952,0.070072666,0.0125358775,-0.0017610191,-0.012689734,0.0050110435,-0.04840977,0.004010562,-0.021018185,0.023512775,-0.055125743,0.011953094,-0.043589063,0.04301919,-0.0099062845,-0.0016415158,-0.05347376,-0.040284824,-0.036906313,-0.033383396,-0.016923165,0.032612685,-0.020242898,0.01489562,-0.017659642,0.003661175,0.0077741076,-0.033116657,-0.03942442,-0.01955076,0.00020892237,0.01814082,0.026729658,0.02104575,0.037741736,-0.018859204,-0.063088916,-0.023915479,-0.018419473,-0.02711293,-0.005885335,-0.02865113,-0.017803064,-0.008003505,0.0075871334,0.0220136,-0.022091543,-0.045138784,-0.004275515,-0.022371648,-0.043573797,0.020100648,-0.032823164,0.041662507,0.06607104,-0.011692691,-0.0065039475,-0.015943848,0.010138576,0.035334714,0.03319751,0.01297965,-0.023260804,-0.015418384,0.05656162,-0.0009248185,0.0036537459,0.012911487,0.026801474,-0.008259309,0.03466967,-0.013792433,-0.00040815564,0.007832033,0.058239304,-0.012945985,0.028544372,-0.04840494,-9.3324634e-05,0.037528142,-0.0073520388,-0.03927321,-0.023472566,-0.0004051859,-0.018792192,0.0016642626,-0.0051458953,-0.030637193,0.041994218,0.016759338,0.048363987,-0.040913805,-0.010956242,-0.043803453,0.0023070986,-0.016726477,0.015622873,-0.0033944047,0.0057523674,0.019554228,0.020089215,-0.02172089,0.00264749,0.0053588785,-0.013994663,0.0008564885,0.038148675,-