	 ('Star-Wars-Yoda','This image features the iconic character Yoda from the Star Wars franchise. Yoda is a small, elderly alien creature known for his wisdom and mastery of the Force. In this close-up portrait, we see Yoda''s distinctive features in remarkable detail.

Yoda has wrinkled, greenish-yellow skin that gives him an aged appearance. His large, expressive eyes are a warm brown color and convey a sense of deep wisdom and kindness. His ears are long and pointed, extending outward from his head, adding to his alien appearance. Wisps of thin white hair sprout from his head, emphasizing his advanced age.

Yoda is wearing simple, rough-textured robes in earthy tones, typical of his humble Jedi attire. The fabric appears worn and frayed, consistent with his ascetic lifestyle. His three-fingered hands are visible, clasped together in front of him in a thoughtful or meditative pose.

The background is dark and out of focus, which draws attention to Yoda''s face and upper body. This creates a sense of intimacy and allows the viewer to focus on Yoda''s expressive features.

This image is often used as a meme template to convey wisdom, surprise, or sometimes sarcastic commentary, playing off Yoda''s reputation for sharing cryptic, sage-like advice. The detailed, high-quality nature of the image allows for a range of interpretations of Yoda''s expression, making it versatile for various meme contexts.

The cultural significance of this image cannot be overstated, as Yoda is one of the most recognizable and beloved characters in pop culture. His appearance often evokes themes of wisdom, mentorship, and the mystical aspects of the Star Wars universe.','/memes/Star-Wars-Yoda.jpg',2,'{}','{"master yoda"}',0.0,'[0.041253958,0.0034873823,0.017243667,-0.034887664,-0.0045004627,-0.015666455,0.0075562247,-0.008939205,-0.000860311,0.009840334,0.00794353,-0.01104999,0.011853605,-0.00089949736,-0.015173831,-0.0018419091,0.008665417,0.012378784,-0.031369183,0.0060776467,-0.01605164,0.022006014,-0.08381187,0.012494806,0.026538733,0.04241231,-0.008931646,0.019360647,0.028075112,0.0056530847,-0.042801756,0.011619433,0.0066772234,-0.052274633,-0.016440233,-0.0033945027,0.019999146,-0.05665909,0.0031023815,-0.05213707,0.037499268,-0.030691607,-0.008568296,-0.026988208,-0.040038228,-0.0033553643,-0.013125145,-0.03386422,0.013383405,-0.04468472,0.008743469,-0.020417856,-0.0032043715,0.039403547,0.015223426,-0.02122106,0.012552964,0.00038857694,0.013924615,0.0129229715,0.033333234,0.0032528434,-0.00990681,-0.033174675,-0.075674765,0.018266682,-0.0037067141,0.0020139418,-0.004066335,0.042101163,0.00804724,0.03954239,0.022112265,-0.005349393,-0.0609799,-0.017703157,0.0074653565,0.009644043,0.03939015,0.0053537735,0.01653874,0.07539913,-0.052480478,-0.0035974826,-0.014324969,-0.010158963,-0.008542211,0.0213587,-0.01855779,-0.055476505,-0.00931699,0.07451743,0.0018358649,0.03399877,0.026049726,0.0075066406,-0.033727616,0.012867396,0.011365406,0.01327611,-0.006274536,0.015927197,-0.0123667065,0.036328748,-0.026244797,-0.019244665,-0.0063302447,-0.0072186226,-0.013160269,-0.035927676,0.053773724,-0.01456868,0.0040174485,-0.005025205,-0.01911571,-0.012998175,-0.029279001,0.05076081,-0.060752023,-0.027648116,-0.041515235,0.002117142,-0.0018156226,0.010172876,0.01482569,-0.013731948,-0.019437555,0.031252995,0.014194048,0.028177947,-0.005047355,-0.009757429,0.04506797,0.016355418,-0.017234595,0