	 ('One-Does-Not-Simply','This meme template features a close-up shot of a man with long, shoulder-length brown hair and a beard. He''s wearing a dark leather jacket over what appears to be a reddish shirt or tunic. The man has a distinctive facial expression - a knowing, slightly mischievous smile with his eyes narrowed, giving him an air of wisdom or inside knowledge.

The lighting in the image is warm and golden, suggesting an indoor setting, possibly near a window or fireplace. This creates a cozy, intimate atmosphere that contrasts with the man''s somewhat rugged appearance.

The man''s posture is relaxed, with one hand raised near his face in a gesture that implies he''s about to impart some information or wisdom. This pose, combined with his expression, gives the impression that he''s about to share a clever observation or witty remark.

