	 ('Batman-Slapping-Robin','This meme template is based on a classic comic book panel featuring Batman and Robin, iconic characters from DC Comics. The image has a vintage aesthetic with bold, flat colors characteristic of older comic printing techniques.

The panel is set against a vivid red background, creating a stark contrast with the characters. In the foreground, we see the back of Robin''s head, identifiable by his signature black hair and yellow cape or collar. Robin''s hand is raised, palm open, in a gesture that suggests he''s speaking or explaining something.

Facing Robin is Batman, instantly recognizable by his pointed-ear cowl and stern expression. Batman''s face is partially visible, showing his strong jaw and the white eyes of his mask. He''s wearing his classic gray and blue costume. Batman''s arm is outstretched, hand open, in a slapping motion directed at Robin''s face.

Above the characters are two large, empty speech bubbles. These bubbles are a key element of the meme format, as they invite users to fill in humorous or satirical dialogue that often subverts the expected interaction between these characters.

The composition creates a sense of tension and action, frozen in a moment that''s ripe for comedic interpretation. The exaggerated gestures and expressions, combined with the empty speech bubbles, make this image a versatile template for various jokes and commentary, often playing on the dynamic between a mentor figure (Batman) and a sidekick or subordinate (Robin).

This particular meme format has become known as the "Batman Slapping Robin" meme, and it''s frequently used to humorously depict scenarios where one person abruptly shuts down or rejects another''s statement or idea.','/memes/Batman-Slapping-Robin.jpg',2,'{}','{"batman and robin","shut up hater"}',0.0,'[0.018410027,-0.0039034018,0.027045239,0.0019236841,0.011708107,-0.08253627,-0.021844069,-0.039799232,-0.013279779,0.054345146,-0.018766189,0.029443052,0.030382536,-0.015651375,0.0055427216,-0.007360074,-0.017389853,-0.0023871507,-0.01704674,0.02482643,-0.005096432,0.009778961,-0.065520234,-0.047142196,-0.006387715,0.04370512,-0.0066395467,0.003704646,0.057703324,0.04034508,0.0028110393,-0.01754339,0.026100025,-0.04259151,-0.0014789335,-0.021764474,0.008557822,-0.04521748,-0.00024092139,-0.0038089857,0.031322505,-0.02785865,0.0010195067,-0.016180782,-0.026360368,0.0014474483,-0.0015247507,0.031462915,-0.014412436,-0.04042894,-0.011374633,-0.022776397,0.025162889,0.03261854,-0.03904342,-0.046119936,-0.047373936,-0.019159932,0.03229752,0.024201997,0.04914493,-0.026687456,0.021116132,-0.052522592,-0.0414764,-0.016630404,-0.034499414,0.015096524,-0.011060564,-0.0032994628,-0.0041532647,0.06037053,0.016415786,-0.021106174,-0.056250043,-0.018906038,-0.024654938,-0.034033906,-0.005951945,0.017934242,-0.004075097,0.07132564,-0.013084789,-0.015194729,-0.0019014851,-0.037704255,0.027730359,0.031506725,0.037329677,-0.055881307,0.009926789,0.06881717,0.007872886,0.055927277,0.0044755056,0.04036385,-0.037107814,0.0653171,-0.019349853,0.010449064,0.0069472576,0.08298963,-0.04602233,0.040386062,-0.006175144,-0.0120679,0.033259306,-0.032054678,-0.009800475,-0.016509864,0.01886705,0.011125873,0.004994771,-0.022311611,-0.0037079277,-0.0135408975,0.020299701,0.03691821,-0.016782368,-0.012460768,-0.009258201,-0.02336417,-0.039543025,-0.02186851,-0.026720172,-0.0097070895,-0.008481826,0.03143759,-0.015461369,0.026239777,0.039060257,-0.020625755,0.018020637,0.03421254,-0.029572517,0.034416