	 ('Captain-Picard-Facepalm','This meme template features a close-up shot of a man in what appears to be a futuristic or sci-fi setting, likely from a television series or film. The subject is seated and wearing a burgundy uniform top with a high collar, suggestive of a military or official capacity.

The most striking element of the image is the man''s posture and gesture. He is shown with his face buried in his hand, palm covering his eyes in a classic "facepalm" pose. This gesture universally conveys frustration, exasperation, or embarrassment. The baldness of the man''s head is prominently visible, adding to the dramatic effect of the pose.

The background is muted, with pale walls or panels visible, keeping the focus squarely on the subject''s reaction. The lighting is even, giving the scene a somewhat sterile or institutional feel, which contrasts with the emotional nature of the gesture.

This image has become an iconic representation of secondhand embarrassment, disbelief, or reaction to something incredibly frustrating or stupid. It''s often used in online discussions or social media to express similar sentiments without words, relying on the powerful visual shorthand of the facepalm.

The framing of the shot, cutting off at the man''s shoulders, emphasizes the gesture and facial expression (or lack thereof, given it''s hidden). This tight focus makes the template highly effective for conveying a strong emotional reaction in a succinct, immediately recognizable way.

Overall, this meme template captures a moment of pure, relatable human exasperation, making it a versatile and popular choice for expressing similar feelings across a wide range of contexts in internet culture.','/memes/Captain-Picard-Facepalm.jpg',2,'{}','{"star trek face palm",pickard}',0.0,'[0.024809176,-0.038679782,0.03357755,0.03688603,0.023579748,-0.058993686,-0.009543009,-0.038099315,-0.00453173,0.033672374,0.008342001,-0.023176653,0.02786277,-0.0033362221,-0.00037469875,-0.015355333,0.030643746,-0.019470766,-0.02502532,0.0056794,0.0067787864,-0.0123671405,-0.06464996,-0.0426737,-0.004098546,0.052509308,0.013100951,0.014706959,0.038358025,0.0325993,-0.008639704,-0.0024977857,-0.0036680715,-0.03693503,0.005104371,-0.009463711,0.02736672,-0.0626166,-0.037339587,-0.026931433,0.03720527,-0.021001967,0.023116743,-0.042879574,-0.01931264,-0.014627945,-0.002904459,0.0015715036,0.042817604,-0.002282724,-0.0003600736,-0.004267529,-0.01293269,0.037321072,-0.015938839,-0.041404705,-0.01543123,-0.0077149076,-0.0056040986,0.021636784,0.06767025,0.0016007203,-0.0063100453,-0.02366324,-0.020402389,0.0003594732,-0.0029379062,-0.008953708,-0.031151896,0.013754351,-0.0051530744,-0.026558172,0.033110805,-0.026678436,-0.023601515,-0.011941779,-0.02539712,-0.0003061799,0.0459876,-0.00326729,0.036063507,0.075396635,-0.0012833498,-0.020994779,0.008911559,-0.016497694,0.04940204,0.06599266,-0.007255741,-0.034394745,0.016760768,0.046122838,-0.01919934,0.013447069,-0.012400399,0.033892903,-0.018020846,0.054802816,-0.021253737,0.0004930136,-0.015857236,0.06523544,-0.035373457,0.05654475,-0.019731373,0.0120874,0.02215534,-0.0032559778,-0.014558634,-0.03662939,0.017700698,-0.007422927,-0.015166776,-0.019913869,-0.042866856,0.019659767,-0.01581973,0.023487963,-0.02104093,0.0071475194,-0.04480542,-0.023745697,0.008220179,-0.009733929,-0.019555654,-0.009914974,0.023441676,0.03641898,-0.029315455,0.0058824467,0.0060227877,-0.040394317,0.024344144,0.059572585,-0.02158052,-0.0026733526,0.03323