	 ('Grandma-Finds-The-Internet','This meme template features an elderly woman seated at a computer, peering intently at the screen with an expression of surprise or confusion. The image captures a moment of technological bewilderment that many can relate to, especially when considering the generational gap in computer literacy.

The woman has short, curly white hair and wears glasses, which she''s adjusting with her right hand as if struggling to see the screen clearly. Her mouth is slightly open, suggesting a mix of concentration and perhaps mild distress. She''s wearing a light blue blouse with a white collar, giving her a neat, grandmotherly appearance.

The setting appears to be a home office or living room, with a warm yellow wall visible in the background. A computer monitor takes up the lower right corner of the image, though we can''t see what''s on the screen. A computer mouse is visible on the desk, emphasizing the technological context.

The lighting in the image is soft, likely from a nearby window, which highlights the woman''s facial features and creates a warm, domestic atmosphere. This lighting contributes to the image''s relatability and homey feel.

This meme template is often used to humorously depict situations where older individuals struggle with modern technology, or more broadly, when anyone encounters something confusing or surprising online. It plays on the stereotype of older generations being less tech-savvy, but does so in a way that''s endearing rather than mocking.

The close-up framing of the woman''s face allows viewers to clearly see her expressive reaction, making it easy to project various scenarios onto the image. This versatility has made it a popular template for a wide range of internet-related jokes and observations.','/memes/Grandma-Finds-The-Internet.jpg',2,'{}','{}',0.0,'[0.023328464,-0.041020326,-0.010657108,0.02972238,0.007905231,-0.032137934,-0.004278542,0.0053161904,0.008466639,0.047814704,0.00556002,-0.015467235,0.04818979,0.016687248,0.005480587,-0.0018262316,0.005470558,0.009258474,-0.032613993,0.011878034,-0.0009437719,0.01491335,-0.07840504,-0.034361947,-0.04344845,0.053875864,0.0064625046,0.02304115,0.06284537,0.007485034,0.0054159067,0.000709679,-0.02232434,-0.0315854,-0.0003488037,-0.020656243,0.014927081,-0.027801968,-0.054208066,-0.051918082,0.023837822,-0.02543317,0.019292444,-0.02671886,-0.040846385,-0.038774084,0.009357543,0.001062183,0.049273696,-0.005012859,0.021433042,-0.022081448,-0.0055086855,0.004813485,-0.02153418,-0.03927173,-0.02377329,-0.013773009,-0.019031387,0.013240374,0.056902666,0.016489504,0.013728682,-0.045705196,-0.004081429,0.020182487,0.0075642914,-0.011443422,-0.03479567,0.016138926,0.018136756,0.013817047,-0.02078373,-0.036699485,-0.06274603,0.01758555,-0.023210377,0.025476735,-0.03101861,0.03730914,-0.0051894854,0.017591726,-0.026938466,-0.011966782,-0.0021625974,-0.035183404,0.016562536,0.042187985,-0.010578891,-0.027921855,-0.0024052246,0.03731151,-0.005622458,0.023443885,0.011645203,0.04994247,-0.008105919,0.026129661,0.011834249,0.02898682,-0.02171503,0.04333458,-0.013281411,0.06195761,-0.021139849,0.01118424,0.019648243,-0.008297384,-0.05479176,-0.033706035,-0.008041761,-0.026444834,-0.006664492,0.010201578,-0.026658358,0.03736937,-0.0041688806,0.048264686,-0.03836533,-0.0030605667,-0.072364055,-0.015976025,-0.027700301,-0.012977582,0.01442783,0.0038725778,-0.0012989155,0.023442904,-0.01735466,0.019431414,-0.0020300846,-0.027972247,0.004722192,0.004022515,-0.011966852,0.