	 ('The-Scroll-Of-Truth','This meme template is a four-panel comic strip featuring a small green alien-like character with a large brown hat. The art style is hand-drawn and colorful, with a whimsical, cartoonish quality.

In the first panel, the character is standing in a crystal-filled cave next to a red treasure chest in water. The background shows blue water, gray rock formations, and green crystals jutting out from the walls and ceiling.

The second panel depicts the character excitedly holding up a yellow scroll with a radiant effect around it. The character''s expression is jubilant, with a wide smile.

The third panel zooms in on the scroll, which is now unrolled and blank except for a small decorative flourish at the bottom. The green hands of the character are visible holding the scroll.

In the final panel, the character is shown running or leaping away through shallow water, with an annoyed or frustrated expression. The scroll is still in their hand, trailing behind them.

This comic template seems designed to set up expectations of a great discovery in the first two panels, only to subvert them with the blank scroll in the third, leading to the character''s comical disappointment in the fourth. It''s a classic structure for memes about anticlimax or thwarted expectations.

The artist''s signature "Robotatertotcomics" is visible in the first panel, indicating the original creator of this comic template.','/memes/The-Scroll-Of-Truth.jpg',2,'{}','{"I''ve finally found it... after 15 years",nyehhh}',0.0,'[0.01846019,-0.010615563,0.016050382,-0.01811137,0.012332414,-0.022077061,0.0073136482,0.024496535,-0.004362579,0.04692561,0.018094227,0.019045215,0.01511333,-0.009716966,-0.019882863,-0.013959353,0.0113618625,-0.0145137645,-0.008098157,0.01969251,-0.0009990293,-0.018006748,-0.05407076,-0.005966977,-0.0035678032,0.041669745,0.027661294,0.029389638,0.07338295,0.023841364,0.03216589,-0.0037683188,-0.006357324,-0.07225824,0.015824318,0.025750814,0.010557539,-0.015065619,-0.010020045,-0.048106905,0.006581419,-0.017433176,0.042992376,0.0047416873,-0.013058114,-0.008259294,-0.029833134,0.0051644947,0.014028454,-0.04235546,0.026161717,-0.016990347,-0.01072764,0.0047288574,-0.00995524,-0.01366755,-0.0018751217,-0.02666087,0.020113643,0.028340768,0.03373027,0.005827227,0.03506893,-0.027294619,0.008016649,0.043667432,-0.028795464,-0.025162391,-0.031764627,0.00713751,-0.044716593,0.0388925,0.031491328,-0.053546723,-0.06595495,0.000290987,-0.0032032256,-0.01664801,-0.011393396,0.029269481,0.025586557,0.021363497,-0.014098774,-0.027124792,0.0020635647,-0.037269738,0.01244442,0.04700311,-0.002599197,-0.06333313,0.011371958,0.058643695,0.014796232,-0.0069870166,0.04876664,0.020607803,-0.034084205,0.041492768,-0.009684134,0.004412637,-0.032188907,0.04124704,-0.053682588,0.022001745,-0.023824103,0.0070121307,0.028135054,-0.016080204,-0.03156086,-0.025600674,0.010861637,0.006539195,0.00892056,-0.012667682,-0.040944517,0.029392052,0.0014266347,0.020826431,-0.027273145,-0.0344777,-0.037504062,-0.02228125,-0.0443838,-0.017822085,-0.012598546,-0.048819788,-0.009773596,0.03658786,-0.010386932,0.025575433,0.0026078632,-0.011174473,-0.008208008,0.021511734,-0.0373859,0.022610452,0.0019201678,0.042570934,0.019926462,-0.022265043,0.007102978,0.009546051,0.004371090