	 ('Doge','This image depicts the iconic "Doge" meme, featuring a close-up portrait of a Shiba Inu dog. The Shiba Inu has a distinctive fox-like appearance with a golden-tan coat, pointy ears, and a white muzzle. The dog''s face is the central focus of the image, positioned slightly off-center to the right.

The Shiba Inu''s expression is what made this image go viral and become a widespread meme. Its eyes are wide and alert, giving an appearance of mild surprise or curiosity. The dog''s mouth is slightly open, creating what looks like a subtle, almost smug smile. This particular expression has been described by many as quizzical, knowing, or even slightly judgmental, which adds to its humor and versatility as a meme template.

The image has a soft, warm color palette dominated by shades of golden yellow and cream. The background is blurred, putting all the focus on the dog''s face. The lighting appears natural, highlighting the textures of the dog''s fur and creating a gentle shadow under its chin.

The image quality is clear but not overly sharp, giving it a slightly vintage or early digital camera feel, which adds to its charm and meme-ability. This particular shot has become one of the most recognizable animal memes on the internet, spawning countless variations and even influencing cryptocurrency (Dogecoin).

The Doge meme typically features colorful text in Comic Sans font scattered around the image with intentionally broken English phrases, though this template shows only the base image without any added text. Its simplicity and the dog''s expression make it highly adaptable for various humorous contexts, contributing to its enduring popularity in internet culture.','/memes/Doge.jpg',2,'{}','{"Shiba Inu","ironic doge"}',0.0,'[0.014147301,0.0070859725,0.012147443,-0.012196302,-0.0052112537,-0.0019766288,-0.0037015753,-0.0097539965,0.0090304585,0.05023742,-0.0023282748,0.03270983,0.02355937,0.037090957,-0.035987098,-0.00398063,7.031335e-05,-0.028486524,-0.050441865,-0.00028555503,-0.015982306,0.013089937,-0.07042412,-0.021060936,0.03885752,0.067085326,0.023756845,-0.00600151,0.066828914,0.011187786,0.008850201,0.044946607,0.012164758,-0.0413434,-0.010518124,-0.029422924,0.011811378,-0.008709365,-0.012446215,-0.047963087,0.051222667,-0.019509537,0.04127928,-0.027004743,-0.048586685,-0.016767617,-0.06399661,-0.022174729,0.011921205,-0.02167511,0.020166114,0.025260296,0.012583176,0.0048412685,-0.020244883,-0.03679706,-0.0074970797,-0.04539147,-0.02426618,-0.00094896473,0.03217698,0.0019512681,0.030195532,-0.037265427,-0.025802199,0.019071413,-0.023204828,-0.016220506,-0.020265216,0.005469083,0.015458715,0.010551611,-0.0323097,-0.02832434,-0.047992043,-0.015974972,-0.009339699,0.007645683,-0.015295383,-0.00074797776,0.0073540513,0.03392517,0.009999884,-0.0380648,-0.020757021,-0.0237751,0.03297355,0.030623347,0.011270362,-0.013021921,-0.033393733,0.060639564,-0.0009136172,0.022405077,-0.006807511,0.030663513,0.00774927,0.014273828,0.017354423,0.010853663,-0.01115518,0.029401952,-0.03489537,0.047304466,-0.028412476,-0.007944928,-0.008495004,-0.0022495694,-0.030776383,-0.0010067837,0.0019623705,-0.042347774,0.0031140593,0.007658707,-0.0102373175,-0.0036909631,-0.053608146,0.09856166,-0.038196195,-0.004558236,-0.067099206,-0.008421742,-0.020780882,0.009892332,-0.0074829706,-0.01