	 ('Am-I-The-Only-One-Around-Here','This meme template features a middle-aged to older man with a stern, intense expression. He has a thick beard and mustache, and is wearing aviator-style sunglasses that partially obscure his eyes. His hair is styled in a short, neat cut.

The man is dressed in a casual manner, wearing what appears to be a light-colored button-up shirt or bowling shirt, with the sleeves rolled up to his elbows. Over this, he has on a darker vest or sleeveless jacket.

The focal point of the image is the man''s raised right arm, which is prominently holding a handgun. His pose suggests he is either about to fire the weapon or has just finished doing so. His left hand is not visible in the frame.

The background of the image is somewhat blurry but appears to be an indoor setting, possibly a bar or bowling alley, given the dim lighting and reddish tones visible.

The man''s expression and body language convey a sense of frustration, anger, or intense determination. This image is often used in memes to express extreme annoyance, overreaction, or a readiness to take drastic action in response to a situation.

The composition of the image, with the man filling most of the frame and the gun prominently displayed, creates a sense of immediacy and drama. The slightly grainy quality of the photo suggests it''s a still from a film, adding to its cinematic feel.

This template has become iconic in meme culture, often used to humorously express disproportionate responses to minor inconveniences or frustrations in everyday life.','/memes/Am-I-The-Only-One-Around-Here.jpg',2,'{}','{"Angry Walter from The Big Lebowski","john goodman"}',0.0,'[0.039777502,-0.017275626,0.02252852,0.032284424,0.006596251,-0.04987931,-0.045556784,-0.0098713795,-0.013631531,0.05118176,0.018035622,-0.013904956,0.01836955,0.0018274968,0.02624472,0.025685454,0.003269568,0.0005012527,0.0013848282,0.030532388,0.00973538,-0.017922891,-0.05741951,-0.046577286,0.012128198,0.03700377,-0.020262161,0.028397975,0.042311065,0.036053218,0.0112811215,0.0010963259,-0.00080329366,-0.043664586,-0.009724656,-0.010099425,0.022310682,-0.06812934,-0.009428635,-0.024102671,0.032172047,-0.013190617,0.04433361,-0.0114246365,-0.015406077,-0.04658201,-0.026799152,-0.009334846,0.02677082,0.013409911,0.023315378,-0.024137897,0.023858586,0.02047836,-0.031471327,-0.03153137,-0.015167472,0.0033479037,0.025985293,0.020117298,0.050286204,-0.007974399,-0.032578103,-0.032693706,-0.032763682,0.013511101,-0.0089155985,0.014944373,-0.026131256,-0.017183091,0.0049746386,-0.01595179,0.014040532,0.0136496425,-0.04611861,0.0080807535,-0.04740395,-0.010198797,0.03422215,-0.005200503,0.007249282,0.038401328,-0.010274832,-0.02965936,-0.028457653,0.009434775,0.024909385,0.04998979,0.0031955647,-0.029515663,-0.0006551802,0.060675982,-0.020095875,0.014546848,0.029313987,0.047141127,0.009094453,0.053412087,0.0072349967,0.011977152,-0.029785743,0.047600616,-0.02780223,0.021474395,-0.05130641,0.01431618,0.037801728,-0.0063131773,-0.041395597,-0.027094107,0.038796566,-0.0072408323,0.015014452,0.012790115,-0.03337651,0.0153714055,-0.019235034,0.039376806,-0.03176086,0.0206984,-0.032161582,9.253489e-05,-0.0010730369,-0.02530198,-0.00078425114,-0.005512044,0.006927061,0.0450602,-0.0295792,0.026773354,0.009360186,-0.011132665,0.032327697,0.019639377,-0.041726105,0.011384184,0.031683236,0.044042937,0.0004624