	 ('And-everybody-loses-their-minds','This meme template features a striking close-up of a character dressed as a clown or jester, likely from a popular superhero film. The character''s face is painted white with exaggerated red lips extending into a grotesque smile, and dark makeup around the eyes. Their hair appears disheveled and green-tinged.

The character is wearing a white shirt or jacket and is captured in an intense, dramatic moment. Their hands are raised and blurred, suggesting rapid movement or gesticulation. The expression on their face is one of exasperation or frustration, with eyes tightly closed and brow furrowed, contrasting sharply with the painted smile.

The image has a cinematic quality, with a shallow depth of field focusing on the character''s face while the background is blurred. The lighting creates shadows that enhance the dramatic and slightly menacing atmosphere of the scene.

This particular frame seems to capture a moment of high emotion or a pivotal point in a dialogue, making it a potent template for memes that express frustration, sarcasm, or dramatic overreaction. The juxtaposition of the character''s clown makeup with their genuine expression of annoyance or disbelief adds layers of complexity that can be exploited for humorous or satirical purposes in meme culture.

The image''s high contrast and emotional intensity make it eye-catching and memorable, contributing to its effectiveness as a meme template. It taps into themes of chaos, madness, and the thin line between comedy and tragedy, which resonate with many internet users and can be applied to a wide range of situations for comedic effect.','/memes/And-everybody-loses-their-minds.jpg',2,'{}','{"Heath Ledger Joker from The Dark Knight","joker lose mind"}',0.0,'[0.025028978,-0.030676847,-0.008085235,-0.008632711,0.025549397,-0.06655131,-0.016834045,-0.023650609,-0.013562129,0.055991348,-0.0044669057,-0.014458709,0.054342892,-0.026207238,0.029282968,-0.012531816,-0.005072222,-0.045334306,-0.04031683,0.00860569,-0.026004786,0.009744766,-0.08147974,-0.063054316,-0.018165963,0.043306928,-0.0020284802,-0.0013634403,0.03399327,0.01692423,0.0048514334,-0.009941795,0.006784565,-0.056695342,0.021266608,-0.0023525134,0.028113918,-0.04807453,-0.006722754,-0.014738917,0.048149258,-0.017453982,0.014434384,-0.04136083,-0.024529435,-0.015204554,-0.025898369,0.007215297,0.0060880147,-0.03401642,-0.014605058,-0.026323996,0.005453637,0.016920108,-0.022565989,-0.04140784,0.0049038464,-0.00805216,0.0019759461,-0.0035828603,0.04877379,0.009637241,0.0058531277,-0.053302154,-0.03130341,0.014805294,-0.0071597523,0.0029789468,-0.033947688,-0.0005294254,-0.0009601608,0.026375478,0.0035892338,-0.005631434,-0.07556431,-0.019325992,-0.028572163,-0.047317103,0.032639932,-0.003390454,0.016721467,0.042980053,-0.018229127,-0.011611465,-0.038399663,-0.010794332,0.021495247,0.013106208,0.013673309,-0.04211764,0.0029309955,0.08000627,0.012913468,0.048269972,0.025793329,0.041311834,-0.01130103,0.033730187,-0.005192272,0.015316794,-0.0010597575,0.036894314,-0.051618833,0.04109726,-0.014645477,0.0004954331,0.015785884,-0.005114769,-0.037466113,-0.027869547,0.020462833,-0.042704042,0.03615865,-0.0055293785,-0.030811463,0.010275654,0.013888378,0.05782944,-0.053809956,-0.029391656,-0.024327576,-0.02648265,-0.0330407