	 ('Mocking-Spongebob','This meme template features a close-up of SpongeBob SquarePants, the iconic yellow sea sponge character from the eponymous animated TV series. The image captures SpongeBob in a moment of comical distress or confusion, which is typical of his exaggerated expressions in the show.

SpongeBob is depicted with his characteristic square shape and bright yellow color, covered in his trademark holes. His large, bulging blue eyes are wide open, giving him a startled or bewildered look. His mouth is agape, forming an oval shape that suggests he might be mid-exclamation or gasp.

Adding to the absurdity of the image, SpongeBob''s body is contorted in an unnatural pose. His left arm is raised awkwardly above his head, with his hand visible. His right arm appears to be reaching out to the side, though it''s partially out of frame. This posture contributes to the overall sense of chaos or panic in the scene.

One of the most striking and humorous elements of this image is that one of SpongeBob''s teeth seems to have popped out of his mouth and is hovering above his head. This floating tooth adds to the cartoon physics and slapstick humor that the show is known for.

The background of the image shows the familiar setting of SpongeBob''s pineapple house interior, with its wooden floorboards visible at the bottom and a hint of blue wall or water in the upper part of the frame.

This particular frame likely comes from a moment in the show where SpongeBob is reacting to something surprising or alarming, captured at the peak of his animated reaction. The exaggerated expression and bodily contortion make it a perfect template for memes expressing shock, confusion, or an over-the-top response to a situation.','/memes/Mocking-Spongebob.jpg',2,'{}','{"spongebob mock","spongebob chicken","retarded spongebob","sarcastic spongebob","spongebob stupid","spongebob derp","spongebob bird","spongebob mocking face"}',0.0,'[0.037430834,-0.01608636,-0.010383633,0.006710919,0.03001094,-0.017344205,0.005141902,-0.015641766,0.028209748,0.044302493,0.0321534,-0.01911003,0.03441541,0.01170855,-0.014437681,-0.021015784,-0.018864207,-0.0329924,-0.030145632,0.043663744,0.017671363,-0.029095225,-0.021465734,-0.02037871,-0.027626412,0.0492687,0.016153615,-0.006701697,0.03506807,0.012394268,0.015583863,0.0036925809,-0.0038121454,-0.029560026,0.024027983,0.020342454,0.038733747,-0.06962346,0.0143380035,-0.038298026,0.026075838,-0.031961158,0.015013619,-0.013471966,0.0054096305,-0.027783396,-0.014720102,0.010793881,0.028574163,-0.020826764,0.042667918,-0.011376119,0.025238814,0.02141894,-0.028659675,-0.05435074,-0.013430223,-0.004126669,0.0120290145,0.0092163505,0.009843106,0.014340444,-0.022389704,-0.05866349,-0.043201257,-0.0016149459,-0.011243018,-0.035256986,-0.016799482,0.012485948,-0.0069745346,0.023557654,0.023249818,-0.008511769,-0.058040336,0.0059954263,-0.054589164,-0.010527385,0.022186095,0.012690467,0.033396605,0.04803204,0.012848097,-0.04276184,-0.029484525,-0.0088978335,0.03269811,0.028451337,0.022109615,-0.042817753,-0.0361621,0.07790462,0.00011946042,0.035095632,0.012780909,0.025572341,0.004798524,0.036062263,0.027094275,0.00800201,0.009367738,0.06738589,0.0013390321,0.040775236,-0.00944515,0.025093533,0.019896176,0.03830764,-0.051032178,-0.028669782,0.03179567,0.0077631096,0.02278601,-0.018468255,-0.017814027,0.016970212,-0.01199691,0.07225433,-0.0459032