	 ('Sad-Pablo-Escobar','This meme template consists of three separate images arranged vertically, all featuring the same character in different contemplative or solitary poses. The images appear to be stills from a TV series or film set in a past era, likely the 1980s or early 1990s, based on the clothing and settings.

In the top image, we see a man with curly hair and a mustache, wearing a light blue short-sleeved shirt, sitting alone on a yellow swing or porch swing. The background shows a grassy area, suggesting an outdoor setting. His posture and expression convey a sense of thoughtfulness or melancholy.

The bottom left image shows the same character sitting alone at a small table in what appears to be a dimly lit kitchen or dining area. He''s wearing a light-colored t-shirt with green accents. The setting has a vintage feel with old-fashioned furniture and decor visible in the background. The lighting and composition create a moody, introspective atmosphere.

In the bottom right image, the man is standing alone beside an empty swimming pool. He''s dressed in a white polo shirt and blue jeans, hands at his sides, gazing off into the distance. The pool is visibly aged and possibly abandoned, with plants growing nearby, adding to the sense of isolation and reflection.

The combination of these three images creates a powerful visual narrative of loneliness, contemplation, and perhaps regret or nostalgia. The character''s consistent solitude across different settings emphasizes themes of isolation and introspection, making this template particularly suitable for memes about deep thoughts, loneliness, or the passage of time.','/memes/Sad-Pablo-Escobar.jpg',2,'{}','{"pablo escobar waiting","man waiting","waiting man","lonely man","narcos waiting","narcos bored","narcos alone","forever alone","coronavirus sports"}',0.0,'[0.017055001,-0.026054455,0.01238101,-0.0019250658,0.010335093,-0.06145409,-0.02217293,0.0042121266,0.016907144,0.02559124,0.019443493,-0.023345659,0.015094749,-0.005324029,-0.028074687,-0.014664454,0.0020954283,-0.010614121,-0.06118053,0.022879958,-0.0016395381,0.0034820903,-0.043938573,-0.02468808,0.016385835,0.047008093,-0.01811511,0.05028961,0.032580644,0.019583136,0.03584799,-0.024614831,-0.015976053,-0.04369158,0.0045372644,0.02179179,0.0103976745,-0.05736646,0.0027104295,-0.024074,0.0063882614,-0.0162407,0.033208527,-0.027770737,-0.012000682,-0.021989174,-0.0032700545,-0.0218879,0.03408249,-0.011779782,0.020629207,-0.03614686,0.037529655,0.019038308,0.009570185,-0.030675834,0.0077996,0.017888902,0.0070873913,0.0062404447,0.007297331,0.01242731,-0.011188563,-0.046398,-0.027771538,0.014462994,0.0095749665,0.019702679,0.00542885,-0.013685898,-0.011658577,-0.0033097663,0.013071724,0.0057432204,-0.022548027,-0.0007530255,-0.012543169,-0.009755434,0.026554052,0.0005361936,0.014775664,0.05593291,-0.01936561,-0.0021662759,-0.043469552,-0.07083458,-0.0034155475,0.04022503,0.0329763,-0.024805376,-0.026286807,0.063899286,-0.0038348245,0.005732598,0.004627352,0.024447894,0.008285525,0.022455314,0.0221843,0.009912335,0.011972914,0.025089726,-0.029644288,0.03161543,-0.038444504,-0.0010681676,0.01816645,-0.0067169075,-0.055595025,-0.03042731,0.0030235767,-0.0024770703,0.0014895354,0.03167455,-0.038305882,0.031111293,0.000483501