	 ('Uncle-Sam','This iconic image depicts the classic Uncle Sam character, a personification of the United States government. The figure is shown from the chest up, wearing a distinctive costume that includes a tall top hat with a blue band decorated with white stars, reminiscent of the American flag. The hat sits atop a head of disheveled gray hair.

The face is that of an older man with sharp, piercing eyes and a stern, authoritative expression. He has a goatee and sideburns, giving him a distinguished and somewhat intimidating appearance. His gaze is direct and intense, looking straight at the viewer.

Uncle Sam is wearing a white collared shirt with a red bow tie, and a dark blue jacket, again echoing the colors of the American flag. The most striking element of the pose is his outstretched arm and pointing finger, directed straight at the viewer. This gesture is commanding and engaging, creating a sense that he is singling out the person looking at the image.

The artwork style is reminiscent of early 20th-century propaganda posters, with bold lines and a slightly painterly quality. The colors are vibrant and patriotic, dominated by red, white, and blue. The background is plain, focusing all attention on the figure itself.

This image is famously used in recruitment posters with the text "I Want YOU for U.S. Army" (though no text is present in this version). It has become a powerful symbol of American patriotism and government authority, often repurposed in various contexts for both serious and humorous memes. The directness of the pointing gesture and the stern expression make it particularly effective for messages that demand action or attention from the viewer.','/memes/Uncle-Sam.jpg',2,'{}','{USA,murica,"i want you for us army!","we want you","i want you","thank you!","we need you","usa needs you","i need you","uncle sam pointing finger"}',0.0,'[0.028662512,-0.03336093,0.034882765,0.03047642,0.0008011154,-0.02484963,-0.019023575,0.014078187,-0.015090241,0.02498805,0.024654578,-0.030455818,0.013043845,0.025950173,0.008599012,0.026695028,-0.0026674136,0.0011185986,0.022160323,0.0061853505,-0.0025595953,-0.0021715576,-0.05165572,-0.043692164,0.00021769787,0.037864476,-0.0044964557,0.021761391,0.039160706,0.020612946,-0.017050795,-0.009677513,-0.0130763035,-0.076323934,-0.006324278,-0.009473515,0.041854255,-0.096483156,0.02775239,-0.04570889,0.03631641,-0.002480791,-0.023022283,-0.00343529,-0.03892044,-0.03637336,-0.04531443,-0.06335421,0.023814842,-0.011947948,-0.010917303,-0.006753513,-0.0027069466,0.035324685,0.0054674707,-0.023454962,0.006001383,-0.03666082,0.0008593758,0.036848627,0.035466928,-0.012737416,0.0053203637,-0.043784317,-0.04723691,-0.007150263,-0.0020963345,0.033942044,0.008427981,0.040565692,0.014025663,0.01042956,0.027335512,-0.015913289,-0.019867439,0.012185529,-0.017171938,-0.020766862,0.0048258305,0.014886934,0.005975715,0.017894419,-0.021466447,-0.02523921,0.013930176,0.04806391,0.008845746,0.032768503,0.01825973,-0.033134673,-0.008352508,0.038681116,-0.048410118,-0.0094957,0.013446722,0.02380102,-0.020599548,0.019357208,0.029958736,-0.010144014,-0.0009294177,0.03042264,0.0053108535,0.026320925,-0.027223505,0.009075512,0.0013925023,-0.029607302,-0.010623851,-0.05