	 ('Back-In-My-Day','This meme template features a close-up portrait of an elderly man with a stern, admonishing expression. He is dressed formally in a dark suit with a white shirt and dark tie, topped with a black bowler hat, giving him an old-fashioned, distinguished appearance.

The man''s face is the focal point of the image, showing deeply etched wrinkles and a ruddy complexion that suggests advanced age. His eyes are narrowed behind small, round glasses perched low on his nose, adding to his scrutinizing look. His mouth is slightly open, forming what appears to be a scowl or a look of disapproval.

Most notably, the man is raising his right hand with his index finger extended, pointing upward in a gesture that is commonly associated with lecturing, warning, or making an emphatic point. This pointing gesture, combined with his facial expression, conveys a sense of authority, criticism, or possibly giving unwanted advice.

The background is a plain, neutral color, likely beige or light brown, which keeps the focus entirely on the man and his expressive pose.

This image is often used in memes to represent an older generation criticizing younger people, to mock outdated or conservative viewpoints, or to humorously portray someone giving unsolicited advice or complaints. The exaggerated, almost caricature-like quality of the man''s expression and gesture makes it a versatile template for various humorous or satirical contexts.','/memes/Back-In-My-Day.jpg',2,'{}','{"grumpy old man pointing"}',0.0,'[0.027690481,-0.028555414,0.009543567,0.020423785,0.015479392,-0.015219113,-0.021196615,-0.008643259,-0.01113847,0.048343625,0.020718092,-0.039441664,0.05672547,-0.010038641,0.0072870697,-0.009235738,0.0020966455,0.0044425637,0.010773882,0.010992322,0.01582082,0.0004286015,-0.049248897,-0.060352158,-0.00053664384,0.061420515,-0.025937084,0.043383807,0.051394485,-0.001509686,-0.00067698205,0.011072248,-0.021533666,-0.05529777,-0.015905662,-0.037422087,0.031114437,-0.07414006,2.6109044e-05,-0.026579592,0.030554619,-0.041596774,0.02240182,0.00090182567,-0.034249235,-0.025014976,-0.025628166,-0.002135221,0.007103994,-0.008309337,0.023201551,-0.012332776,0.01425754,0.04441485,-0.006646835,-0.028285326,-0.031649653,-0.00820228,-0.008910715,-0.004057493,0.0399202,-0.018889723,-0.0018836189,-0.048647262,-0.047928512,0.013291735,-0.015749393,-0.00034432655,-0.018174956,-0.009943211,-0.013835682,-0.0010386584,0.03755974,0.021456013,-0.053734805,0.021887597,-0.03695788,0.0015724511,0.017803274,-0.0015302101,0.026075244,0.022948446,0.00070106273,-0.025207773,-0.011295374,0.014898297,0.025101595,0.049338344,0.0018581578,-0.030614644,-0.007893309,0.056552507,-0.025249481,0.019903375,0.01761151,0.04085558,0.0046048667,0.058331758,0.015874704,-0.0046977843,-0.027277902,0.05587398,-0.0053174803,0.026965793,-0.03208147,0.013294655,0.015111006,0.00869722,-0.042825356,-0.02253806,0.040486936,-0.020003058,-0.008149648,-0.04100395,-0.061179113,0.036570836,-0.023573555,0.022509165,-0.045922272,0.01585629,-0.033529427,-0.0007442338,0.0033553767,-0.003112