	 ('Skeptical-Baby','This meme template features a close-up portrait of a baby with a distinctively skeptical and slightly disapproving expression. The infant has a round face with chubby cheeks, typical of a young baby. Their eyes are wide and alert, peering directly at the camera with an intensity that seems beyond their years. The baby''s mouth is slightly pursed, contributing to the overall look of doubt or mild contempt.

The baby appears to be wearing a brown or tan colored outfit, possibly a sweater or onesie, visible at the bottom of the frame. The background is soft and out of focus, suggesting an indoor setting, possibly near a window due to the gentle lighting.

What makes this image particularly meme-worthy is the baby''s facial expression, which seems to convey a sense of judgment, skepticism, or disbelief. It''s as if the infant is critically evaluating something they''ve just heard or seen, despite being far too young to actually do so. This incongruity between the baby''s age and their seemingly mature expression is what gives the image its humorous and versatile quality as a meme template.

The image is cropped closely around the baby''s face, emphasizing the expression and allowing it to dominate the frame. The clarity and quality of the photo make the baby''s features and expression very distinct, which is crucial for its effectiveness as a meme.

This template is often used to express doubt, skepticism, or a judgmental reaction to statements or situations, playing on the idea of even a baby finding something unbelievable or worthy of criticism.','/memes/Skeptical-Baby.jpg',2,'{}','{"sceptical boy"}',0.0,'[0.0072637787,-0.032814868,0.020420078,-0.0029968603,0.034149274,-0.040171184,-0.0040531666,-0.014906068,-0.0002835816,0.04580382,0.005028399,-0.020603606,0.04781213,0.010036363,0.004390603,0.010499514,0.0064207152,-0.01509876,-0.00029624443,0.00096967403,-0.012394783,0.008913405,-0.09213861,-0.027062511,0.006142165,0.036371425,0.02247735,-0.002516106,0.06736895,0.013944427,-0.03347924,-0.008398266,0.0063491073,-0.0048391623,-0.0012521076,-0.007825971,0.04735553,-0.004035603,0.0065354155,-0.034239873,0.023886569,-0.0038078704,0.036440037,-0.021588275,-0.028308641,-0.05411025,-0.015606429,0.0044887997,0.045202713,0.0076611876,0.02885238,-0.022629634,0.015488634,-0.0053169196,-0.026104376,-0.03667467,0.017879184,0.0040196814,-0.013248905,0.025377985,0.029998116,0.012627667,0.009913245,-0.040491935,-0.038484424,-0.015916498,-0.035569012,-0.0006754587,-0.008802116,-0.03494644,0.0326591,0.025551936,-0.0097542675,0.0044159982,-0.036878068,0.0059295828,-0.031894274,-0.019962812,0.0061130896,0.009755067,0.026441887,0.008870601,0.027306888,-0.020781564,-0.0005900774,-0.023375034,0.024514388,0.045519017,-0.004592392,-0.025808705,0.008323693,0.06238571,-0.00813844,-0.0003069447,0.0386822,0.033394843,-0.010594878,0.038373087,0.0008924052,-0.0019504852,0.0027186512,0.023832435,0.019840358,0.032773387,-0.041524492,-0.0014569279,0.010151914,-0.009953876,-0.05758018,-0.028927142,0.00391088,-0.033873457,-0.007037022,-0.002217778,-0.026800005,0.026604405,-0.008832837,0.07262571,-0.07277833,-0.05473794,-0.052962806,0.022598935,-0.021033792,0.0072468044,0.019105742,-0.0015228068,-0.00907511,0.051403612,-0.029086472,0.018204236,-0.030789386,-0.042395547,0.0033549953,0.060513344,-0.013181045,-0.0002953674,0.01821823,-0.0067163627