	 ('Say-That-Again-I-Dare-You','This meme template features a striking image from a well-known 1994 crime film. The scene captures a tense moment with a man in a classic black suit and white shirt, portraying an intimidating character.

The focal point is the man''s intense facial expression - his eyes are wide and piercing, conveying a mix of anger and determination. His mouth is slightly open, as if he''s in mid-speech or about to deliver a forceful line. He has a distinctive afro hairstyle that stands out against the lighter background.

The man is holding a handgun, pointing it directly at the viewer, which creates an immediate sense of confrontation and danger. His other hand is raised, palm open, in a gesture that could be interpreted as a warning or a sign to stop.

The setting appears to be indoors, with a plain wall visible behind the character. The lighting is harsh, creating strong shadows that emphasize the dramatic nature of the scene.

This image has become iconic in meme culture, often used to represent moments of extreme frustration, threats, or intense questioning. The character''s authoritative stance and the direct eye contact with the viewer make it a powerful template for conveying strong emotions or reactions in a humorous or exaggerated context.

The composition of the shot, with the character filling most of the frame and the gun prominently displayed, gives the image a forceful, in-your-face quality that translates well to meme format. It''s a versatile template that can be adapted to various situations where one wants to express confrontation, incredulity, or a no-nonsense attitude.','/memes/Say-That-Again-I-Dare-You.jpg',2,'{}','{"Samuel L Jackson","pulp fiction"}',0.0,'[0.04897974,-0.0015064809,0.0134786805,0.03941164,-0.0055125384,-0.06915545,-0.058833923,-0.015519998,-0.014870132,0.050340716,0.010085745,0.00015357237,0.02721626,-0.004280476,0.03780866,0.05061291,-0.0020412314,-0.011559977,0.0030159727,0.027051967,0.009309917,-0.027978454,-0.08614202,-0.0785101,0.00047891898,0.044331923,-0.011314506,0.011337436,0.039073512,0.03189144,0.00820521,0.00095259544,0.0102697285,-0.036576748,-0.006289344,-9.9910314e-05,0.060743675,-0.063981354,-0.011836185,-0.003137581,0.027019812,0.0044590863,0.039652947,-0.005863774,-0.04428571,-0.028853899,-0.024244877,0.009960082,0.0019469558,-0.008072816,0.008951735,-0.015408072,0.028068244,0.034421403,-0.04591172,-0.032324348,-0.03152711,-0.015405065,0.016337393,0.02228438,0.043459818,-0.009833503,-0.012840872,-0.03026419,-0.040570162,0.020941595,-0.012872811,0.004184306,-0.02919172,-0.024200745,0.0033398084,0.015933705,0.028339263,0.052023962,-0.040360354,-0.0019545055,-0.03951524,-0.037760224,0.03745301,-0.019577783,0.0026039472,0.028380243,-0.006991095,-0.037280917,-0.030544272,-0.004841861,0.02312343,-0.009705145,0.03496502,-0.038440302,0.01978096,0.07515655,-0.0504029,0.001239687,0.010939959,0.046316564,-0.0027422549,0.023684174,0.0051535084,0.036681242,-0.037343133,0.056518126,-0.039015908,0.030510869,-0.028920522,0.015574271,0.032839384,-0.009539859,-0.018015504,-0.029453253,0.032016408,-0.019918997,0.011507039,-0.008737233,-0.0469405,0.020564778,0.0012739025,0.052546203,-0.028068274,0.013619508,-0.035852768,-0.0022825813,0.014305946,-0.036436025,-0.00036970893,-0