	 ('Philosoraptor','This meme template features the iconic "Philosoraptor" image, a stylized depiction of a Velociraptor dinosaur head with a contemplative expression. The image is rendered in a high-contrast, two-tone style primarily using shades of green against a lighter green background.

The raptor''s head is shown in profile, facing left. Its eye is prominent and alert, with a piercing gaze that suggests deep thought or consideration. The dinosaur''s mouth is slightly open, giving it an almost quizzical or pondering look. The textured, scaly skin of the dinosaur is represented through intricate line work, creating a detailed and somewhat realistic appearance despite the simplified color palette.

Below the head, a single clawed hand of the raptor is visible, curled inward in a gesture that further emphasizes the thoughtful pose. This hand adds to the meme''s philosophical connotation, as if the dinosaur is stroking its chin while pondering life''s great questions.

The background is divided into four triangular sections of varying shades of green, creating a subtle geometric pattern that draws focus to the central raptor image. This design choice gives the meme a modern, graphic quality while maintaining its prehistoric subject matter.

The "Philosoraptor" meme is typically used to pose paradoxical questions or humorous logical conundrums, playing on the juxtaposition of a predatory dinosaur engaged in deep philosophical thought. The image''s composition and style make it instantly recognizable and versatile for a wide range of contemplative or ironic captions.

This particular rendition of the meme stands out for its green monochromatic color scheme, which may be a nod to the popular imagination of dinosaurs as primarily green creatures, or could be interpreted as a reference to the color of contemplation and growth.','/memes/Philosoraptor.jpg',2,'{}','{"green dinosaur","dinosaur wondering","philosiraptor meme","dinosaur ponder"}',0.0,'[0.010173631,-0.008222677,0.024050126,0.019670984,0.005295652,-0.023090597,-0.033509597,0.024018455,-0.0027723399,0.04110634,-0.015355814,-0.04404196,0.011379694,0.02601265,0.011112863,0.008211202,0.031953447,-0.0015415829,-0.046318028,0.015011504,-0.029297808,0.016212564,-0.057097234,-0.042658694,0.0052943677,0.046653822,0.026326202,0.01923636,0.08154676,0.0142646935,-0.022968313,0.023985406,-0.002624673,-0.06853082,-0.0024087608,-0.017091202,-0.005528338,-0.036718532,-0.025103364,-0.018722005,0.03820882,-0.023629762,0.024783142,0.0006232497,-0.030723093,-0.03588687,-0.030757096,-0.031144042,-0.0116967335,-0.033682838,0.034551233,-0.012055771,-0.0019310985,-0.028585987,-0.035714455,-0.018565932,0.012486037,-0.005324082,-0.0072159367,0.029757239,0.051184792,0.006477242,0.005082602,-0.027373843,-0.031008514,0.00059576373,0.0027981803,0.009183648,-0.016073566,-0.015859457,-0.015267593,0.013649579,0.024927778,-0.008718943,-0.03397934,0.009449135,-0.00060129305,-0.026883343,0.025488961,0.01656136,0.038406897,0.0473514,-0.04571987,0.008256126,-0.015688967,-0.011619214,0.0011696249,0.051813617,-0.0056610773,-0.049170762,-0.016916545,0.08099464,0.019239258,0.030284993,0.033793703,0.031471513,-0.028716246,0.038613565,-0.0112832505,-0.00345887,-0.0147824325,0.019370234,-0.021973064,0.035027836,-0.039003212,0.015877556,-0.007351519,-0.02554631,-0.00865621,-0.045834057,0.019861687,-0.009037317,-0.009100314,-0.0197769,-0.032882497,0.025678672,-0.00040245865,0.027203472,-0.039275926,-0.043035496,-0.06590972,-0.022248227,-0.025560211,0.032904692,-0.035003915,-0.036222976,-0.015570577,0.006529659,-0.006491